    hi "二人ともいつからそこにいたんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1647
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_833e9f3c:

    # mi "I think you need more practice."
    mi "もっと練習したほうがいいね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1652
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_d048f6dd:

    # "Shizune draws a few sharp signs in the air between herself and Misha."
    "静音がミーシャとのあいだの空間にいくつかの手話を鋭く描く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1657
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_1a0b7e51:

    # mi "Shicchan agrees."
    mi "しっちゃんもそういってるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1659
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_329b6481:

    # "Rin said the exact same thing yesterday, but why did it sound less condescending?"
    "琳も昨日、まさに同じことを言っていたけど、どうしてあっちは馬鹿にした感じがしなかったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1661
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_ed28d547:

    # hi "You shouldn't judge before I'm finished."
    hi "終わってもないのに判断するなよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1663
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_1d5c4068:

    # hi "Besides, don't you know it's bad luck to see an unfinished piece of work?"
    hi "それに、作りかけのものに口を出すのは縁起が悪いって知ってるか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1668
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_6b435cf7:

    # "Misha cracks in exuberant laughter."
    "ミーシャはあふれんばかりの笑い声をあげる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1673
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_6b3efc73:

    # mi "What? Don't be silly~! There's no way that could be true."
    mi "え～？　なにいってるの～！　そんなわけないじゃん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1675
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_fac8e03d:

    # hi "Whatever."
    hi "そうかよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1680
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_a962787d:

    # "Shizune's eyebrows furrow dangerously, and the movements of her hands become abrupt, like the slashing of a knife."
    "静音の眉毛が危険なほどしわを寄せ、手の動きもナイフをふるっているかのように険悪なものになる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1685
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_ef2b123c_4:

