    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1690
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_fd5941ef:

    # mi "You should learn to take constructive criticism better."
    mi "建設的な批評はもっと前向きに受け止めるべきよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1692
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_cccccb6a:

    # hi "I would if you'd actually offer some."
    hi "ちゃんと批評してくれるならな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1694
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_5570e1f6:

    # "I know I'm getting too defensive and that Shizune is taking advantage of it, but I can't help it."
    "受け身になってるのはわかってるし、そこを静音に利用されているのもわかってる。でもどうしようもない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1696
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_65aaa2c6:

    # hi "What are you two doing here, anyway?"
    hi "それで、二人ともそこで何やってるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1701
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1703
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_e7924e02:

    # "Misha wags her finger admonishingly at my nose."
    "ミーシャが俺の鼻に向かって諭すように指を振る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1708
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_53ae0812:

    # mi "Tsk, tsk, Hicchan. Were you not listening to the teacher at all?"
    mi "ちっちっち、ひっちゃん。先生の話、ぜんぜん聞いてなかったの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1713
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1718
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_7c9efb99:

    # mi "We have a group assignment, now."
    mi "わたしたち、グループ課題をやるんだよ、今から"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1720
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_0eb31ceb:

    # "I nod bleakly, and let them take the lead."
    "俺はどんよりとうなずくと、二人に舵取りを任せる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1725
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_60d7d137:

    # mi "So, what do you think of the lesson for today?"
    mi "それで、今日の授業はどう思う？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1727
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_fd65c7b1:

    # hi "Not much of anything… I didn't listen to a word of it."
    hi "なんとも言えないな……一言も聞いてなかったし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1732
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_5cbced6e:

    # "Misha slaps her forehead and shakes her head theatrically."
    "ミーシャは自分のひたいを叩くと、わざとらしく頭を振る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1734
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_55f29ce1:

    # mi "What are we going to do with you, Hicchan?"
    mi "もう、ひっちゃんてばどうしようもないね！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1736
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_fec493d4:

    # "Luckily, Shizune and Misha together are more effective than three or four normal people, so I can mostly slack on the assignment."
    "幸い静音とミーシャが組むと普通の人３、４人よりも有能なので、俺はほとんど課題には関わらずに済む。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1738
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_d38e5d84:

    # "I try my best to offer at least some assistance, but I end up being mostly useless."
    "多少の手伝いくらいは頑張ったけど、結局俺はほとんど役立たずで終わる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1747
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_38f23db9:

    # "The teacher keeps us in class five minutes past the lunch bells, but eventually lets us off the hook."
    "先生には昼休みのチャイムが鳴ってから５分過ぎても教室に足止めされたけど、やがて解放してくれる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1749
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_21db04c3:

    # "I quickly stuff my books into my bag while Shizune and Misha carry their chairs back to their own seats."
    "静音とミーシャが椅子を自分の席に戻している間に、俺はさっさと教科書をかばんに詰め込む。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1751
translate jp a2_rin_self_study_7bfebd10:

    # "The failure of a bird-drawing ends up crumpled and stuffed in my pocket as I hurry outside."
    "失敗した鳥のスケッチは結局、外へと急ぐ間にくしゃくしゃにしてポケットに押し込んだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1767
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_b44219f6:

    # "After that morning class, and throughout the week, I keep bumping into Rin."
    "あの午前の授業以来、その週はずっと琳に出くわし続けた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1776
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "やあ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1780
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1785
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_7dca636a:

    # n "{vspace=60}This is somewhat natural, as our classrooms are adjacent. But rather than just cross paths in the hallway like people regularly do, we seem to pause at the sight of each other."
    n "\n\nまあ俺たちの教室は隣りあってるから、当たり前か。でも他のみんなのように廊下ですれ違うというより、俺たちはお互いを目にした瞬間に足を止めたかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1787
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_bf100a98:

    # n "We invariably end up talking a little bit, or just silently hanging out together."
    n "俺たちはいつも通りに少し話をするか、でなければ黙って一緒にぼうっとするだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1789
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_ec57484b:

    # n "I think I'm getting used to being quiet in Rin's company, as it doesn't feel as awkward, any more. I am, by nature, somewhat introverted like her, so we fit together well."
    n "琳と一緒にいながら、ただ黙っていることに慣れてきたような気がする。もう以前ほど気まずい気持ちにはならない。俺は生まれつき、琳のように内向的なところがあるから、お互いそりが合うんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1791
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_4c2b04e1:

    # n "I think it's actually an anomaly for someone in this school to be so quiet. Most people here seem to love socializing."
    n "たぶん、この学校でそんなにおとなしくしているのは変なんだろうな。ここにいる人はみんな人付き合いが好きでたまらないって感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1793
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_0d1d1345:

    # n "{vspace=30}It's something that I've noticed already, even though I haven't been here very long: people here talk a lot, and they talk all the time."
    n "\nまだここに来て長いわけではないけど、そのことにはもう気づいていた。みんな大いにおしゃべりをしている。しかも四六時中だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1795
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_68133e62:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}It's a rare case when I see someone sitting alone, just spacing out or whatever. Obviously there are people like that here, too; that Hanako girl and myself, just to name two from my own class. But overall, they are a minority."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n誰かがぽつんと一人ぼっちでぼんやりしているなんてことはほとんどない。もちろん、そういうやつだっているけど。俺のクラスでも俺自身や、あの華子って女子がそれに当てはまる。でも全体からすれば、少数派だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1799
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_ee61753d:

    # n "At any rate, I wouldn't exactly call what Rin and I do 'socializing,' either, but it's something, at least."
    n "ともあれ、俺と琳が『付き合ってる』なんていうつもりはないけど、少なくとも何かは起きているわけで。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1801
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_991e73af:

    # n "These occurrences themselves don't bother me, but the fact that they happen at all does."
    n "こういうめぐり会い自体は気にならない。でもそういうことが起きているという事実そのものが気になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1803
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_fcb60e28:

    # n "I'd hesitate to say that we are drawn together by something, but we certainly act as if we were."
    n "お互いにどこか気を惹かれていると言うのはためらわれるけど、でも俺たちは確かにそうであるかのようにふるまっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1805
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_33809380:

    # n "{vspace=60}However, this sense of a budding friendship is completely wrecked every time Rin opens her mouth."
    n "\n\nでもこの友情が芽生えてくる感覚は、琳が口を開くたびに完全にぶっ壊されてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1808
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1816
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_06d21fa2:

    # rin "Can I listen to your heartbeat?"
    rin "君の心臓の音、聞かせてくれない？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1822
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_8475a565:

    # "She says this, or something else about as outrageous, and I have to fend off whatever nonsense her mind has cooked up during the preceding class of a subject that she is not interested in."
    "琳はこんなことや、これと同じくらいとんでもないことを言う。琳が何の興味も持っていない前の時間の授業で考えついたわけの分からない話をしてきて、俺はそれを受け流すはめになる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1824
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_f8e8e791:

    # "It seems Rin has taken a shine to my heart condition as some kind of an extension of her interest in the odder disabilities that people here have, and the consequences of said afflictions."
    "琳はここの生徒たちが持つ珍しい障害や、その影響に興味を持っていたけど、その延長で俺の心臓のことを大いに気に入ってしまったらしい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1826
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_4b9954cf:

    # "As I stand in front of her for a second too long, looking as flummoxed as I am, she concludes it is necessary to further clarify her request."
    "俺が琳の前になおも立ちつくしていると、向こうも俺と同じように戸惑ったのか、そのリクエストについてもっとはっきりさせる必要があると思ったようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1831
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_f2bff420:

    # rin "I know I can, but I mean, will you let me?"
    rin "耳は聞こえるから大丈夫。というか、私に聞かせてくれる？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1833
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_7df9d21b:

    # hi "Why?"
    hi "どうして？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1838
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_104727a1:

    # rin "Do I need a reason? I'm usually pretty bad with reasons."
    rin "理由がいる？　理由をつけるのは得意じゃないんだけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1840
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_0895310e:

    # hi "Not per se, but if you want to do it, you probably do have a reason."
    hi "別にいいけどさ。でもそうしたいからには、なにか理由があるんじゃないのか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1845
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_b3f96c03:

    # rin "That's kinda clever. You are smarter than you look."
    rin "なんか鋭いね。君って見かけによらず冴えてる"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1847
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_321cb82a:

    # hi "Also, I'd rather you not. I think these things should be private."
    hi "それと、お前には聞かせたくないな。こういうことはプライベートにしておくべきだと思うし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1852
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_17d35a41:

    # rin "Private. I get it."
    rin "プライベートね。わかったよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1854
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_68a76165:

    # hi "I can tell you something though, if it amuses you. I'm pretty sure it will. My heartbeat does sound very weird. Because of the… you know, condition."
    hi "まあでも、一つ教えてやるよ、お前の好きそうな話だ。保証する。実際、俺の心臓の音はすげえ変なんだ。なんでかっていうと……その、病気のせいだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1856
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_08c5ffba:

    # hi "And I hear it. All the time."
    hi "で、俺にはそれが聞こえてる。ずっとな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1861
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_0e59666c:

    # rin "So you're paranoid."
    rin "それじゃ君って心臓マニアなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1863
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_91b3f78f:

    # "It's not a question, it's a statement."
    "これは質問じゃない、意見だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1865
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_0d8daf8b:

    # hi "No, I'm not paranoid. The doctors said that abnormal attention to heartbeat is a common symptom of my… condition."
    hi "違う、俺は心臓マニアじゃない。医者が言ったんだ、心臓の音を異常なほど意識するっていうのは、一般的な症状だって。この……病気の"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1870
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_39b98077:

    # rin "So, for you, it's normal to be paranoid."
    rin "ってことは、君にとって、心臓マニアなのは普通なんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1872
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_a65d9cdb:

    # "It's not a question either."
    "これも質問じゃない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1874
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_b33003cd:

    # hi "One could also say that me being like this in the first place isn't normal, either, but what the heck."
    hi "そもそも俺がこんなふうになってる時点で普通じゃないとも言えるだろ。でもそれがどうしたってんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1876
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_9b51be72:

    # hi "Paranoia fits me fine."
    hi "俺には心臓マニアがお似合いなんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1881
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_64a46f96:

    # rin "I don't think it's something that actually can fit anyone or anywhere."
    rin "誰かとか、どこかに似合うようなものだとは思わないけどな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1886
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_2b6298a3:

    # rin "You know, I ate an orange today for breakfast."
    rin "ところでさ、朝ごはんにオレンジ、食べたんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1888
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_be6f36e4:

    # hi "How was it?"
    hi "うまかったか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1890
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_e556ebfe:

    # "I'm vaguely proud of myself, managing to keep up with Rin's sudden change of topic."
    "琳が突然話題を変えたことになんとかついていっている自分を地味に誇りに思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1895
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_043a3f54:

    # rin "Excellent. I don't remember when I last ate an orange. Because it's annoying to peel one."
    rin "すっごくね。最後にオレンジを食べたのがいつだったか覚えてないんだ。皮をむくの面倒なんだもん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1900
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_f454173a:

    # rin "It's on the list of things I want to learn properly."
    rin "もっとちゃんとできるようにしたいことリストに入ってるんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1902
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_2529a1f7:

    # hi "How come you ate one, then?"
    hi "じゃあ今日はどうやって食べたんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1907
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_3899d286:

    # rin "Emi had some, so she peeled one for me."
    rin "笑美が持ってたんだ。だから笑美がむいてくれたよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1909
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_7d3eb37a:

    # hi "Good for you."
    hi "そりゃよかったな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1916
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_cb50cf13:

    # "Rin stretches her back and yawns, and says nothing further."
    "琳は背伸びをしながらあくびすると、それ以上なにも言わなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1918
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_04793935:

    # "She throws me a glance from the corner of her eye while she watches people pass by, but I couldn't say why."
    "行きかう生徒たちを見ながら、目尻で俺にチラッと視線を送るけど、その理由は俺には分からなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1920
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_4220db58:

    # "I realize, though, that this is the first time I've talked naturally about my condition with anyone. In a way."
    "だけど、誰かと心臓のことについて自然に話すのは初めてだったと気づく。ある意味では。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1924
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_7de8baa1:

    # "A group of boys walk past us to Rin's classroom, but she doesn't pay them any mind. They pay none to her, either. My mind wanders off, spurred by the silence."
    "男子たちのグループが俺たちとすれ違って琳の教室のほうへ歩いていくけど、琳は気にもとめないし、彼らも琳になんの注意も払わない。その沈黙に押されて、俺の意識はあてもなく漂い出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1926
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1932
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_2e79ac04:

    # n "{vspace=90}Maybe I should've let her listen to my heart. It's not like it matters. Nothing really matters that much, at the end of the day."
    n "\n\n\n琳に心臓の音を聞かせてやれば良かったのかもしれない。別に大したことじゃないし。どんなことだって、最終的には大したことじゃないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1934
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_c04fd35a:

    # n "I start feeling depressed for no reason, again. It's like a tidal wave out of nowhere rolling over my consciousness, submerging me underwater."
    n "また理由もなく気持ちが沈み始めるのがわかる。どこからともなく押し寄せる高波が意識の上で渦を巻いて、俺を水中に沈めてしまうかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1936
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_abec4bf4:

    # n "I feel a sigh coming out of my mouth, and I turn away from Rin, pretending to read a poster on the wall. It's an advertisement for the school festival, promoting an event almost a week past."
    n "口からため息が漏れたのを感じて、俺は琳に背を向け、壁のポスターを見るふりをする。ポスターは学園祭の告知で、宣伝しているイベントはもう１週間も前のものだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1938
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_c178d82d:

    # n "The difference between me and Rin is that I'll be more likely than not dead before turning thirty, while she can't eat oranges without help."
    n "俺と琳の違いは、俺は３０になるまでにはたぶん死んでいるだろうけど、琳は人の助けなしにはオレンジを食べられないということだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1940
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_f6d0c724:

    # n "{vspace=60}I can't decide which one of us is worse off."
    n "\n\nどっちの方がつらいと言えるのか、俺にはわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1943
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1950
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_920047c4:

    # n "{vspace=90}I try to grasp the passing of time, but it seems hard. I'm still used to the rhythm of the hospital, where trivialities such as the day of the week or time of day didn't really matter."
    n "\n\n\nどれくらい時間がたったのか把握しようとするけど、なんだか難しい。俺はいまだに病院での生活リズムに引きずられている。あそこでは曜日や時刻といった些細なことは大して重要じゃなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1952
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_68eb9731:

    # n "Everything was the same, no matter what."
    n "何が起きようと、何もかもが同じだった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1954
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_ac33c6f8:

    # n "Rediscovering the significance of time is an oddly disorienting experience, and I find myself enjoying the fact that I can categorize events in this fashion."
    n "時間の大切さを再確認するということは、妙に混乱させられる経験で、俺はものごとをこうやってそれぞれに分類できることを楽しんでいる自分に気づく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1961
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_a19b90d0:

    # n "The relevancy of a ticking clock is surprisingly delightful, and I decide to start wearing an analog wristwatch, something I didn't use to do before."
    n "時計が時を刻む音の有意義さが驚くほど心地よくて、俺は以前はしようと思わなかったアナログの腕時計をつけようと決める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1963
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_f975fe21:

    # n "{vspace=30}When I finally ask Rin on Thursday about something that's been bothering me for the entire week, it's already lunch time."
    n "\n木曜になって、この１週間ずっと気がかりになっていたことについて琳にようやく聞いたときには、すでに昼休みになっていた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1967
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1974
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_ab0a3a09:

    # "The time is somewhere between 11:06 and 11:07, as my watch doesn't have a hand to show seconds. It's the old-fashioned kind with a black leather strap and titanium casing."
    "今の時間は１１時６分と１１時７分の間のどこかだ。俺の時計には秒針がついてないので正確にはわからない。黒い革のベルトとチタンのフレームがついた古風な型のものだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1976
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_4ea1b1d2:

    # "It doesn't look flashy, but a wristwatch doesn't need to."
    "派手には見えないけど、腕時計は派手じゃなくてもかまわない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1990
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_20a67d9a:

    # hi "Hey."
    hi "なあ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1995
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_1860319c:

    # hi "Remember that sketch you made of me? How you said I looked grim and gloomy or something?"
    hi "お前が描いた俺のスケッチ、覚えてるか？　俺が不機嫌で憂鬱に見えるとか言ってたやつ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:1997
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_a913aaa7:

    # hi "I'd like to know what you meant by that."
    hi "あれ、どういう意味だったのか知りたくてさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2002
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_679f7134:

    # "She gives me a weird look and tilts her head a few degrees to the left, but doesn't say anything for a while."
    "琳は俺に奇妙な視線を投げかけ、頭をやや左に傾けるけど、しばらくの間なにも言わない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2004
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_8b0635d8:

    # rin "Well, you see…"
    rin "えっと、ほら……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2012
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_03d13291:

    # rin "We've known each other for two weeks and I haven't seen you smile even once."
    rin "私たちが知り合ってからもう２週間になるけど、君が笑ってるとこ、一度も見たことないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2014
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_a12b9df8:

    # "Her striking observation gives me pause."
    "琳の鋭い観察眼が俺を固まらせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2016
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2019
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_c072d50f:

    # n "{vspace=90}Have I stopped smiling?"
    n "\n\n\n俺は笑わなくなってしまったのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2021
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_d3a072ac:

    # n "{vspace=30}I have to take what she says as truth. She has no reason to lie."
    n "\nこれは事実として受け止めないといけない。琳には嘘をつく理由がない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2023
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_2661e674:

    # n "Something about the way she puts it annoys me. I frown at Rin, then try to correct my expression to look less depressed."
    n "琳のその言い方がなんだか気に入らない。俺はしかめ面を琳に向け、そして落ち込んでいる様子を和らげようとして表情を直す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2025
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_77540516:

    # n "I haven't been in the cheeriest of moods during the past few months or so, this is true."
    n "確かに、この数ヶ月かそこらの間、俺の気分は最高に明るいというわけじゃなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2027
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_6e82529f:

    # n "Does it show so much that someone like Rin can tell, after so little contact with me?"
    n "琳みたいにほとんど付き合いがなかった相手でもわかるくらい、そんなにはっきりと表情に出ているのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2029
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_1cd31177:

    # n "Should I try to smile more at Rin? Maybe she could appreciate it, having such a neutral face herself almost all the time."
    n "もっと琳に微笑みかけてみようか？　きっと琳なら面白がるだろうな、こいつだってほとんどいつも無表情だし。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2031
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_b9ec8dd7:

    # n "{vspace=30}Have I really stopped smiling?"
    n "\n俺は本当に笑わなくなったんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2034
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76b2fe88_6:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2038
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2040
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_2cf75b91:

    # hi "Should I smile more?"
    hi "もっと笑ったほうがいいのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2045
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_5bcd1692:

    # rin "I don't mind either way. Be as you are; you can't help being Hisao anyway."
    rin "どっちでも気にしないよ。君らしくしてなよ、君が久夫なのはどうしようもないんだから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2047
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_c6ecd42f:

    # hi "But it bothers you?"
    hi "でも嫌なんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2052
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_5497647d:

    # rin "I just noticed it, that's all."
    rin "気づいたってだけだよ、それだけ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2065
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_cccab5e2:

    # "Emi skips along the hallway, jumps to a sharp stop when she reaches us, and lightly pats Rin's shoulder."
    "笑美が廊下をスキップしてくると、俺たちのところで急停止して、琳の肩を軽く叩く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2070
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_e487c830:

    # emi "Ready for lunch?"
    emi "お昼、いこ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2075
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_6e5a4cbe:

    # rin "Depends on what lunch is today. Remember that stew from March? Never again, that."
    rin "メニューによるかなあ。３月のあのシチュー覚えてる？　あれは二度とごめんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2080
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_39d7834c:

    # emi "Let's go anyway. I'm starving!"
    emi "とにかくいこうよ。お腹ペコペコだよ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2086
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_7cffe0dc:

    # "As they are about to depart, Emi turns from her friend to me, seemingly as an afterthought, and smiles charmingly."
    "二人が出発しようとしたとき、笑美は琳の方から、思いついたようにこっちに向き直って、可愛らしく微笑む。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2091
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_8a3ee00c:

    # emi "By the way, Hisao…"
    emi "ところでさ、久夫くん……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2093
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_f4f8bf6c:

    # "Her tone is way too sweet and soft to be sincere. I can sense the trap about to be sprung upon me by this miniature health-devil."
    "本心からと言うには、その声は甘すぎで、柔らかすぎだ。このミニチュア健康悪魔が俺の頭上に仕掛けた罠が今にも発動しそうなのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2095
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_639abd09:

    # "I know what she's about to say even before she continues, because I've been trying to avoid her all week."
    "笑美が何を言おうとしているのかは、続きを聞かなくてもわかる。なんせこの１週間、ずっと笑美を避けつづけてきたからな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2100
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_b40265ac:

    # emi "I still haven't seen you at the track this entire week."
    emi "今週ずっと、運動場に来てないよね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2102
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_57474d95:

    # hi "Maybe I've been there when you haven't."
    hi "お前がいないときに行ってたかもしれないだろ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2107
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_4d65e589:

    # emi "That's impossible. I'm there all the time."
    emi "そんなのありえないよ。あたし、いつもいるもん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2109
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_76c20356:

    # hi "But you sleep and go to class."
    hi "でも、授業とか、寝たりもするだろ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2114
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_7efd5e7d:

    # emi "I do those at the same time as you do."
    emi "それは同時にやってるから。久夫くんみたいに"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2116
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_16af0b8c:

    # hi "Yeah, I know, I know. I just… haven't been able to pick myself up."
    hi "わかったわかった。俺はただ……まだ調子が戻ってなくってさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2118
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_4ddabfe3:

    # hi "Don't rat me out to the nurse, okay?"
    hi "このこと、ナースにチクるなよ、いいか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2120
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_fd143a63:

    # hi "Running just isn't my thing, and I haven't come up with a good alternative."
    hi "走るのは苦手なんだよ。ほかに代わりになりそうなことも見つからなくてさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2125
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_93000d78:

    # emi "Why don't you come to the track meet this weekend? Maybe you'll get inspired."
    emi "それなら週末に陸上部の競技会に来てよ。やる気が出るかもしれないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2127
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_eb77460f:

    # hi "Track meet?"
    hi "競技会？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2132
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_085324f5:

    # emi "Yeah! People from a few other schools come here for some friendly track and field action. It's on Sunday afternoon."
    emi "そうだよ！　ほかの学校の人も来て、みんなで陸上の友好試合するの。日曜日の午後だよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2134
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_30cd2dae:

    # "I can't think of any reason not to go."
    "行かない理由は思いつかないな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2136
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_40e42382:

    # hi "Sure. I'll come and cheer for you. I guess you'll be running?"
    hi "わかった。応援に行くよ。お前も走るんだろ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2141
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_b6ef75aa:

    # emi "Of course! You'll get to see me beat them all!"
    emi "もちろん！　あたしが一番になるところ、見られるよ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2146
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_9e1b9902:

    # emi "But bye now! If I don't get something to eat, I'll die."
    emi "もう行かなくちゃ！　なにか食べないと死んじゃう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2148
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_181ad1e9:

    # hi "See you later."
    hi "またな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2155
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_ba0e269e:

    # hi "Bye Rin. I promise I'll smile next time."
    hi "じゃあな、琳。次は笑って見せるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2157
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_21b8d79d:

    # "I call after her, as a bit of an afterthought. Afterward, I feel embarrassed about it, and wonder why I said anything at all."
    "やや思いつきで、琳の背中にも声をかける。その後でなんだか恥ずかしくなる。別に何も言わなくても良かったのに。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2164
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_dd47099a:

    # "That night, when I'm doubly certain that Kenji won't be barging in the bathroom, I look in the mirror and smile at my reflection."
    "その夜、健二がシャワー室に乱入してこないことを十二分に確認してから、鏡をのぞき込んで自分の姿に笑いかけてみる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2166
translate jp a2_rin_hisaos_smile_800c16d8:

    # "The me in the mirror smiling at the me in the bathroom looks awfully fake."
    "俺に笑いかけている鏡の中の俺は、偽物に見えてしかたがなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2182
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_3a7727cf:

    # "Having exhausted the books Kenji lent me in just a few nights, I go back to the library, deeming it a safer alternative for getting my reading fix."
    "数夜で健二が貸してくれた本を読みきってしまったので、俺は図書室に足を運ぶ。次の本を確保するならそっちの方が安全だろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2184
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_595f3a5a:

    # "I return the books he had stolen while I'm at it, to Yuuko's delight. I don't tell her where I got them, though."
    "ついでに健二が盗んできた本を返すと、優子さんがとても喜んでくれる。どこでその本を手に入れたかは言わないでおくけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2189
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_76f72518:

    # yu "Wow, you sure read a lot, don't you?"
    yu "わあ、たくさん読んでるんだね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2191
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_66604769:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess I do."
    hi "ええ、まあ、たぶん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2193
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_3cdbceda:

    # hi "I mean, I do. Even I think it's weird. I think I might have a reading problem. Maybe I'm a junkie."
    hi "というか、確かに読んでますね。自分でも変だと思います。もしかしたら病気かもしれないですね。読書中毒なのかも"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2198
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_83f1980f:

    # yu "No no, I didn't mean it that way. It's not weird at all, and being addicted to reading is a lot better than being addicted to… to something else."
    yu "もう、そんな意味でいったんじゃないのに。ちっとも変じゃないし、読書に夢中になるならぜんぜんマシよ……ほかのことに夢中になるより"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2200
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_8f05fb00:

    # hi "Yeah, I know. It was a joke."
    hi "わかってますよ。冗談です"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2202
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_043deca1:

    # "I smile at her reassuringly and drop the books on the counter so Yuuko can check them out. I feel tired, so I sit down in the vacant chair in front of her desk."
    "俺は安心させるように笑って、優子さんが貸し出し手続きができるよう、本をカウンターの上に置く。なんだか疲れを感じて、デスクの前にある空いた席に腰を下ろす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2207
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_a2f2925a:

    # "While Yuuko goes through the modest pile of reading material I found, I let my gaze wander around the library."
    "優子さんが俺の持ってきたささやかな書籍の山を処理する間、俺はぼんやりと辺りを見回す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2212
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_465a417d:

    # "At the tables, a pair of girls is chattering in hushed tones rather than working on their homework."
    "テーブルのほうでは、２人の女の子が宿題を放り出して、静かな声で雑談している。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2214
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_a35ccc8a:

    # "The short-haired one notices me looking in their direction and waves at me. When I raise my hand back, they glance at each other and giggle in unison."
    "俺が見ていることに気づいて、ショートヘアの子がこっちに手を振る。俺が手を振りかえそうとすると、２人はお互いに向き合って、そろってくすくすと笑う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2216
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_75c978bd:

    # "I'm not sure how I should feel about that, so I decide it's a good thing. The one who waved at me has a horrible case of epilepsy."
    "それをどう受け止めればいいのかわからなかったけど、よかったと思うことにする。俺に手を振った子は重いてんかんを患っている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2218
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_49430e73:

    # "I saw her having an attack a few days ago. It was one of the most disturbing and scary things I've seen in a very long time."
    "何日か前に発作を起こしているのを見た。ここ何年かで目にした、いちばん衝撃的で恐ろしい出来事の一つだった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2220
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_9627ceff:

    # "Yet, there she is, happily chirping away about whatever, as if she doesn't have a care in the world."
    "それでも、彼女はなんの不安もないかのように、楽しそうにおしゃべりしている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2222
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_1e5c25f5:

    # hi "You know, this school is really something else."
    hi "ほんとに、この学校ってどこか違いますね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2227
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_0c511a47:

    # "Yuuko raises her eyes from the books she was going through, slightly startled. She adjusts her glasses and puts on a nervous, confused smile."
    "優子さんはわずかに驚いて、処理している本から視線を上げる。眼鏡を直すと、不安そうな、困ったような笑顔を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2232
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_f5c41094:

    # yu "What do you mean?"
    yu "どういうこと？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2234
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_d804cb90:

    # hi "I don't really know how to explain it. It's just that everyone's so… active, or …how should I put it?"
    hi "うまくは言えないんですけど。ただみんな……活発だなあっていうか……なんて言えばいいんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2236
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_2208347c:

    # hi "It's not just the festival thing, I think, even though I haven't been here that long, but it's everything."
    hi "ここに来てまだ日も浅いですけど、でも学園祭の時期だからってわけじゃなくて、何でもそうだと思うんです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2238
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_6f955c0c:

    # hi "People talk more, work harder and just… are… more than in any other school I've seen before."
    hi "いままで俺が見てきたどの学校よりも、みんなよくしゃべるし、なにかと頑張るし、とにかく……その……どんなことでも多くやってるんです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2240
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_7cdc27e9:

    # "I'm struggling for words, but it feels like I'm speaking honestly."
    "言葉を探すのに四苦八苦するけど、正直に話している気はする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2244
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_3ab94033:

    # hi "This school feels so alive." nointeract
    hi "この学校は本当に活気がありますよね" nointeract

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2259
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_6b872460:

    # yu "I don't think that's a bad thing."
    yu "でもそれっていいことだと思うな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2261
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_25847cfa:

    # hi "Yeah, me neither."
    hi "ええ、俺もですよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2263
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_191f2258:

    # "Suddenly I realize that I've just been babbling my thoughts to Yuuko, out of the blue. She's a bit of a jumpy person, so I fear I might've made a bad impression."
    "突然、俺は脈絡なく優子さんに妙な考えを口走っていたことに気づく。優子さんはちょっと驚きやすい人だから、悪い印象を与えてしまったかと不安になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2265
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_9113fdf3:

    # "She's looking at me with what I hope is curiosity rather than horror, so I figure she's all right."
    "恐ろしそうに、というよりは物珍しそうにこっちを見ているので、大丈夫だと思いたい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2267
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_3c7b4c80:

    # hi "Sorry for suddenly talking about weird stuff like this. I didn't mean to trouble you."
    hi "すみません、急に変なこと言って。困らせるつもりはなかったんですけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2272
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_503f82eb:

    # yu "Oh no, it's not troubling. I'm happy to listen if you feel like talking."
    yu "あらら、別に困ってないわよ。あなたが話したい気分だったなら、聞けてよかったわ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2277
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_9126fc4c:

    # yu "It makes me feel a little reliable, too."
    yu "私もなんだか頼もしくなったものね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2279
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_2a0a33ca:

    # "Yuuko smiles sweetly and a little bit ironically at that. I respond with a thankful smile of my own."
    "優子さんは愛想よく、少し皮肉っぽく微笑む。俺も感謝の笑顔で応える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2281
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_ded80923:

    # "As she pushes the neat stack of books across the counter, I stand up and gather them in my arms."
    "優子さんがきれいに積み上げられた本をカウンター越しに押しやると、俺は立ち上がってそれを腕に抱える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2286
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_fd4feeea:

    # yu "Here you are."
    yu "はい、どうぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2288
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_85879fae:

    # hi "Thank you."
    hi "ありがと"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2293
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_75d58af0:

    # yu "I guess we'll be meeting each other again. Please come here anytime."
    yu "またこうやってお話することになりそうね。いつでも来てね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2295
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_2d84fca9:

    # "Yuuko's kindness is heartwarming."
    "優子さんのやさしさには心温まる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2297
translate jp a2_rin_things_you_like_55375500:

    # hi "You can count on it. See you later."
    hi "もちろんです。じゃあまた"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2315
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8050bdb1:

    # "The morning of the track meet greets me with a brilliant sunshine from a crystal blue sky."
    "陸上部の競技会の日の朝が、透き通るような青空からのきらめく日差しで俺を出迎える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2317
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_7c66b7a7:

    # "While I leisurely stroll towards the track, I decide this is a good sign. Of what, I'm not sure; this event isn't as exciting for me as it seems to be for a large portion of the student body."
    "のんびりと運動場へ足を運びながら、これをいい兆しだということにする。何の兆しかはよくわからない。俺にはこのイベントが、ほかの多くの生徒たちが思っているほど面白そうなものには見えない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2319
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_f6e03850:

    # "I'm even less interested in watching sports than I am in participating, but cheering for Emi is a good cause."
    "自分で参加するならともかく、スポーツを見るというのはなおさら興味がわかない。でも笑美の応援をするというのは立派な理由になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2321
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_12f47cc2:

    # "I'm not expecting this to be any sort of amazing and spectacular experience, but it can't hurt. I'd probably be spending the time reading while cooped up in my room, otherwise."
    "これが驚くような見物になるなんて期待はしてないけど、別に困ることじゃない。そうでなければきっと部屋に引きこもって本でも読んで時間を過ごしていただろうな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2328
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_4c07ada2:

    # "When I approach the bleachers, I spot Rin emerging from the crowd right before she spots me."
    "観覧席に近づくと、人ごみのなかから琳が出てくるのを、向こうが俺に気づく直前に見つける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2333
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8e24cda9:

    # rin "You came."
    rin "来たんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2335
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_128022b9:

    # hi "Of course. I said I would, didn't I?"
    hi "当然。行くって言ったよな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2340
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_909aa193:

    # rin "That doesn't necessarily imply that you had to follow through."
    rin "だからって、必ずそうしなきゃいけないとは限らないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2345
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_ad62fba4:

    # rin "Lots of people say things and don't mean them."
    rin "思ってもいないことを言う人、いっぱいいるから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2347
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_fb2dd3f8:

    # hi "Well, I don't."
    hi "いや、俺は言わないぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2354
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_6507a2c2:

    # "Rin shrugs. Seemingly bored with our conversation, she turns on her heel and heads back toward the stands."
    "琳は肩をすくめる。話をするのに飽きたみたいで、きびすを返して観覧席のほうへ戻る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2356
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e4991f5a:

    # hi "So, are you excited about this?"
    hi "それで、今日は楽しみにしてるのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2361
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_4d44250e:

    # rin "Not really."
    rin "やめとく"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2363
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_7391fc15:

    # hi "Me neither."
    hi "俺もだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2368
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_67c79eef:

    # rin "Then why did you come?"
    rin "じゃあ、なんで来たの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2370
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_6f47fb8a:

    # hi "Why did you?"
    hi "お前はどうなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2372
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_403dba80:

    # "She doesn't reply at all, so I decide not to, either."
    "琳は何も答えないので、俺も答えないことにする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2374
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_6f256d6f:

    # "We enter the bleachers, and Rin nods upwards."
    "観覧席に入ると、琳はあごで上のほうを指す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2379
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_7662434f:

    # rin "Up there."
    rin "あそこ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2384
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_3f0787e5:

    # "Rin leads the way, and soon we've settled down on an almost-empty bench."
    "琳に連れられて、俺たちはほとんど空っぽのベンチに腰を下ろす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2400
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_7a6f9b84:

    # "There's an older woman sitting next to Rin - someone's mother, I assume."
    "年上の女の人が琳の隣に座っている――誰かのお母さん、だろうな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2402
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_2e0de5c3:

    # "She's got rather long hair done up in a braid. On seeing Rin, she gives her an oddly familiar-seeming grin."
    "その人はいくぶん長い髪を三つ編みにまとめている。琳を見て、妙に見覚えのある感じで笑いかける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2407
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_283b7902:

    # emm_ "Well, this is surprising."
    emm_ "まあ、驚いた"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2412
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8c864ddc:

    # emm_ "I thought you went to get a snack, not a boy."
    emm_ "てっきりおやつでも探しに行ったのかと思ったら、男の子と帰ってくるなんて"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2414
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2419
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e69a7036:

    # rin "This is no good?"
    rin "それって良くないの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2425
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8a099328:

    # "The woman laughs at Rin and shakes her head, apparently unable to find a comeback for that. I know the feeling."
    "女性は琳に向かって笑い声を上げ、頭を振る。返事が思いつかないんだろう。俺もその気持ちはわかる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2430
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_61b02c3e:

    # emm_ "Well, I suppose you've always been one to go out for one thing and bring back another."
    emm_ "そうねえ、あなたっていつもなにかを取ってくるって言って出かけて、別のものを持って帰ってくる子だから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2432
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_ff7e3f96:

    # emm_ "But I'm being rude! I haven't introduced myself."
    emm_ "って、やだ！　私、自己紹介もしてないじゃない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2434
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e3fdbe52:

    # emm_ "I'm Meiko Ibarazaki. I'm sure that if you know this girl, you've at least met my daughter, too."
    emm_ "茨崎芽衣子です。この子を知ってるなら、私の娘にもきっと会ったことくらいはあるでしょう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2439
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_d482a825:

    # emm "Pleased to meet you."
    emm "よろしくね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2441
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_61af10dc:

    # "Well, that explains it. She's like a taller, older, more motherly Emi."
    "ああ、なるほど。この人は背が高くて、年上で、もっと母親っぽい笑美みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2443
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e33a9bda:

    # "Apart from her hair being somewhat darker than her daughter's, there's really no mistaking the resemblance."
    "笑美よりも濃い色合いの髪を別にすれば、本当によく似ている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2449
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_7055e23d:

    # hi "Sorry, I'm Hisao. Hisao Nakai. Nice to meet you."
    hi "すみません、久夫です。中井久夫。はじめまして"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2454
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_4adf2880:

    # rin "I'm Rin Tezuka."
    rin "手塚琳です"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2460
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8ac7a1e7:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki laughs again - she really does resemble her offspring - and then leans back a little on her seat and raises an eyebrow."
    "芽衣子さんはもう一度笑うと――本当に笑美にそっくりだ――少し席に寄りかかって、眉をつり上げる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2469
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_ede3064a:

    # emm "So, now that we all know each other, how long have you and Rin been dating?"
    emm "さて、お互い顔見知りになったところで、いつから２人はお付き合いしてるのかしら？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2471
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_873079cb:

    # "My response consists of silence as my brain suddenly lurches into gear. But just before I can begin to utter a hastily babbled explanation, Emi's mother bursts into laughter again."
    "いきなり調子を狂わされて何も言えなくなる。でも、俺があわててべらべらと説明し始める前に、芽衣子さんはまたドッと笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2479
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_35442e7c:

    # emm "Ha! You're a blusher, aren't you?"
    emm "あはは！　久夫くん、すぐ赤くなるほうなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2481
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_14a3feb0:

    # "I don't know if there's any way to keep my dignity in this situation, so I settle for a mumbled response."
    "この状況でどうやったら自分の尊厳を保てるのかわからなくて、とりあえずブツブツ言うことにする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2487
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_f8696b5c:

    # hi "We're not—"
    hi "別に俺たちは――"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2493
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_4565795e:

    # emm "I know, but it's funny to watch you squirm."
    emm "わかってるわ。でもあなたがもじもじしてるところを見るの、面白くて"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2498
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_2fbc3b45:

    # emm "I'm sorry. Forgive an old woman her amusements."
    emm "ごめんなさいね。おばさんの楽しみなの、許してちょうだい"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2500
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8670f0b2:

    # "She chuckles again to herself."
    "また自分でクスクスと笑う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2502
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_d567d04b:

    # "Old woman?"
    "おばさん？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2504
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_ef81889d:

    # "She sure doesn't look that old to me."
    "ぜんぜんそうは見えないけどなあ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2509
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_928dae43:

    # hi "I suppose I can let it go."
    hi "別に気にしてませんよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2515
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_f2fcf1c8:

    # emm "How kind of you."
    emm "ありがとう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2522
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_34cc1882:

    # rin "It's starting."
    rin "始まるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2531
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_fdd4654b:

    # "I direct my attention to the track, where they're preparing for the first sprint."
    "トラックに目をやると、選手たちが最初の短距離走に備えている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2533
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_214fba4d:

    # "It looks like the 400 meter dash."
    "４００メートル走みたいだな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2535
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_ad8eb1ef:

    # "My eyes scan the runners, before finding Emi."
    "笑美を探す前に、ランナーたちを見渡す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2540
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_33e08575:

    # "She's smiling, with an almost cocky look on her face."
    "笑美はほとんど自信過剰なくらいの笑顔を浮かべている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2548
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_356375bd:

    # "The starter raises his pistol."
    "スターターがピストルをかかげる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2564
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_62075404:

    # "Emi explodes off the block, disappearing from the starting line in a blur."
    "笑美はスターティングブロックから飛び出すと、残像を残してスタートラインから消える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2566
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_94fa712c:

    # "It's amazing. Even as the other sprinters converge on the lanes closest to the inside line, Emi surges to the front of the pack."
    "すごい。他の選手がレーンの内側ぎりぎりを走っているときでも、笑美は先頭へと躍り出る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2568
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_6c5a18b2:

    # "By the time she rounds the final turn, a few of the other runners have caught up with her."
    "最後のコーナーを曲がるころになって、何人かのランナーが笑美に追いつく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2570
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_a6466607:

    # "But she puts on a final burst of speed that leaves them at least a half second behind."
    "それでも笑美の爆発的なラストスパートで、他の選手は少なくとも０．５秒は離される。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2578
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_9647ba32:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki whoops and shouts, applauding wildly, and generally looking like any other parent cheering on their child."
    "芽衣子さんはきゃあきゃあ叫んで拍手喝采する。子供を応援する他の普通の親みたいに。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2580
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_42d67943:

    # "Emi bounds off the track, looking pleased with herself."
    "笑美はトラックから跳び出る。自分に満足したみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2589
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_927c7898:

    # "I cheer right along with the rest of them."
    "俺もみんなといっしょに喝采を続ける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2591
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_f5f2273f:

    # "The announcer (sounding suspiciously like Misha) gleefully gives the results."
    "アナウンサー（どうもミーシャのように聞こえる）が大喜びで結果を伝える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2597
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_49aa6f79:

    # emm "I think she's gotten faster since the last time."
    emm "この前より速くなったと思うわ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2602
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_7a658918:

    # hi "That was incredible."
    hi "すごかったですね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2608
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_6e0f28f0:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki grins proudly."
    "芽衣子さんは誇らしげに笑う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2610
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_24acd1f9:

    # emm "Emi's a heck of a runner."
    emm "笑美はすごいランナーなのよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2615
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_d3235c2d:

    # "We fall silent as the next event prepares to start."
    "次の種目の準備が進むあいだ、俺たちは黙り込む。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2617
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_b628005f:

    # "I'm surprised to see Emi striding out onto the track again."
    "笑美がまたトラックに大股で入っていくのを見て驚く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2622
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_a262c76c:

    # hi "Wait, didn't she just run?"
    hi "え、いま走ったばっかりですよね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2624
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e8c4686e:

    # "Emi's mother nods."
    "芽衣子さんはうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2629
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_c130b458:

    # emm "Yes, but she runs multiple events for the team. Especially the sprints."
    emm "ええ、でも笑美はほかの種目も走るの。特に短距離走ね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2634
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_c19ab472:

    # emm "It's a lot of running, but Emi can handle it."
    emm "いっぱい走ることになるけど、でもあの子なら大丈夫よ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2636
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_6fcd9d17:

    # "From the looks of things, she's right."
    "様子を見てると、どうもその通りみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2638
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_c4a6384b:

    # "Emi doesn't appear to be tired, as if she hadn't run the previous event at all."
    "笑美に疲れの気配は見えない。まるで前の競技にそもそも出ていなかったかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2640
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_64ea2cbf:

    # "If not for the sweat visible on her shirt, you'd never know."
    "もしシャツが汗ばんでいるのが見えなければ、気づきようもないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2645
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_1bee6ed0:

    # hi "Which event is this?"
    hi "今度の競技は？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2651
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_7d1676cf:

    # emm "It's the 200 meter dash."
    emm "２００メートル走ね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2653
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_a9c47c5a:

    # emm "She'll do this one, the 100-meter, and the relay."
    emm "あと１００メートル走とリレーもやることになってるの"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2658
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2666
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_0de8c5d6:

    # "Once again the pistol sounds, and once again Emi flies off the block."
    "ピストルがもう一度鳴り響くと、笑美ももう一度スターティングブロックから飛び出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2668
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_2417e5b8:

    # "A thumping sound draws my attention away from the race."
    "ドシンという音が俺の意識をレースから引き離す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2670
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_ebb65b2c:

    # "It's Rin's foot."
    "琳の足だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2672
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_801e329d:

    # "She seems completely absorbed in the race."
    "琳はすっかりレースに夢中みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2680
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_f49b9658:

    # "Emi's mother cheers again, and I assume that the race is over."
    "芽衣子さんがまた声を上げ始めて、レースが終わったんだなと思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2682
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_941ecf11:

    # "Sprints don't seem to me like they'd take very long to complete."
    "短距離走はそんなに長いこと走らないだろうし。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2684
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_c382c6c8:

    # hi "Your foot."
    hi "お前の足"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2690
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e9686c2a:

    # rin "Hmm?"
    rin "んー？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2692
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_2cb216d6:

    # hi "Your foot was bouncing on the bleachers."
    hi "お前の足、席の上で跳ねてたぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2697
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8cf3c02d:

    # rin "Oh."
    rin "ああ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2699
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_efaf4785:

    # hi "You seem pretty into this stuff. I'm surprised; I thought you said this wouldn't be exciting."
    hi "なんだかのめり込んでるみたいだな。楽しみじゃないなんて言ってたから、驚いたよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2704
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_de550c0c:

    # rin "Hmm, I suppose you're right."
    rin "うーん、君の言う通りだね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2706
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_056a211c:

    # rin "It's not that interesting."
    rin "そんなに面白くはないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2711
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_555d1430:

    # rin "But I'm watching Emi, not the sport."
    rin "でも私は笑美を見てるから、競技じゃなくて"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2713
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_ed15e901:

    # hi "I don't follow."
    hi "なんだそれ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2718
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_fe9a74c4:

    # rin "Emi's the most Emi when she runs."
    rin "笑美は走ってるときがいちばん笑美なんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2720
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_9fcc19fb:

    # rin "You don't get to see Emi at her Emiest very often."
    rin "笑美が最笑美状態なのを見られるチャンスはそうそうないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2725
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_3ae9d7f7:

    # rin "But here, you can. See?"
    rin "でもここなら見えるよ。ほらね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2727
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_3fc268c5:

    # "She directs my attention toward the track again, where the 100-meter dash is about to start."
    "琳が俺の注意をもう一度、１００メートル走が始まろうとしているトラックのほうに向ける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2735
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_4b886958:

    # "I watch Emi closely."
    "俺は笑美をしっかりと見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2737
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_befbd79a:

    # "As she gets onto the starter blocks, her whole body seems to relax, but it's a false relaxation."
    "スターティングブロックに乗りかかると、体全体がリラックスしているように見えるけど、それは見せかけのリラックス状態だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2739
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_dedaa01b:

    # "I can see that she's actually like a coiled spring."
    "笑美の体が本当にバネのように見える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2744
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_2ed0b4eb:

    # "As the starter tells everyone to get set, her head snaps up, and her eyes narrow slightly."
    "スターターが位置につくよう声をかけると、頭がピシッと上がり、目はほんの少し細くなる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2746
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_1ab7f00a:

    # "Her mouth curls upward in what could be a grin and could be a growl."
    "口が上向きに曲がり、笑いとも唸りともとれそうな形になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2760
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_3dbe4dc8:

    # "When the pistol goes off, it's as if she's been unleashed from a cage, like she was always moving at this blinding speed, but we couldn't see it happening until the starter's pistol dispelled the illusion of motionlessness."
    "ピストルが鳴り響いたとき、笑美は檻から解き放たれたかのように、常にこんな目にも止まらぬ速さで動いていたかのように走り出す。 でも、すべてが静止していたかのような錯覚をスターターのピストルが吹き飛ばすまで、俺たちにはそれがわからなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2765
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_684ddac6:

    # "As soon as she crossed the finish line, the fierce look was replaced by her normal grin."
    "笑美がゴールラインを横切るやいなや、いつもの笑顔が険しい表情にとって代わる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2767
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e0805e23:

    # "The conquering general returning to his farm."
    "一仕事終えて、普段の姿に戻ったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2769
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_6ca17858:

    # hi "Amazing."
    hi "すごいです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2771
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_f59443ce:

    # hi "She's really amazing. I've never seen someone move that fast."
    hi "ほんとにすごい。あんなに速く走る人は見たことないですよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2778
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_e245860a:

    # emm "Well, don't look at me, I'm far too relaxed to run that fast."
    emm "あら、私を見られてもなあ。私はあんなに速く走るにはのんびりしすぎてるから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2786
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_5a6f12a2:

    # emm "No, I think Emi's prowess all came from her father's side."
    emm "ううん、笑美の才能はみんな父親から受け継いだんだと思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2788
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_3a556b49:

    # "At the mention of Emi's father, Mrs. Ibarazaki looks wistful, almost sad."
    "笑美の父親の話になると、芽衣子さんは寂しげな、悲しそうな顔をする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2790
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_3c9c175b:

    # emm "He got her into running, you know."
    emm "彼が笑美にランニングを教え込んだのよね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:2795
translate jp a2_rin_target_audience_8ec26ed9:

    # hi "Ah, really? I didn't know that."
    hi "ああ、そうなんですか？　それは知りませんでした"

