translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_cf16a595:

    # "Today's art club meeting is currently on hold while everyone waits for Nomiya to show up. I take this time to try and explain my theory about Yamaku to Rin."
    "今日の美術部の活動は、今のところ野宮先生が現れるまで保留となっている。この時間を使って、琳に俺の山久学園論を説明しようとする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3208
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_27da292e:

    # "I've tried to figure out what exactly about the school feels so special to me; that concept I unsuccessfully tried to explain to Yuuko the other day."
    "俺は前の日に優子さんにうまく説明できなかったこと、つまり、この学校がこんなにも特別だと感じさせるものが何なのかを突き止めようとした。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3210
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_1e61d842:

    # "It's still difficult, but the track meet and the time I've spent observing my fellow students have helped my ideas mature a little."
    "今でもそれは難しいけど、でも競技会のことや同級生たちを観察しながら過ごしたことが、俺の考えを多少なりともまとめるのに役立った。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3215
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_e2e4c47a:

    # hi "Have you noticed that people talk all the time?"
    hi "お前はみんなが年がら年中、しゃべってるって気づいてたか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3217
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_4b6799df:

    # hi "I can't really explain it, but…"
    hi "ちゃんとは説明できないけど、ただ……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3219
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_fc9b9a7b:

    # "Once again, as I try to explain my observation, I'm struggling for words."
    "俺の観察結果を説明しようとするけど、またしても言葉がうまく出てこない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3221
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_e12e6fd6:

    # "The student body is heavily cliqued, and I'm only now beginning to make sense of the intricate grouping and popularity networks. And yet, the feeling of being a part of a group is stronger here than I remember it being in my old schools."
    "あらゆる生徒が濃密な集団を作っている。俺は最近になってようやく、その複雑なグループ分けや、人同士のつながりを理解し始めたばかりだ。 それでもなお、自分がそんなグループの一員だという感覚は、前の学校にいたときよりも強く感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3223
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_241b5e77:

    # hi "I'm trying to say that this school isn't like other schools. Or at least, the students aren't, even after discounting the obvious."
    hi "この学校はほかの学校とはどこか違うってことを言いたいんだ。少なくとも生徒は違う。わかりきった部分を除いたとしても"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3225
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_c4a9b5a6:

    # hi "…Do you know what I mean?"
    hi "……言ってること、わかるか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3230
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_9c5b7e02:

    # rin "I don't know what you mean."
    rin "いってること、わかんない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3232
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_8d05c90b:

    # hi "Oh, well… whatever, then."
    hi "ああ、えーと……まあいいや"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3234
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_4f1a17f0:

    # "I want to pursue the issue, but at that point, Nomiya arrives."
    "話を続けたかったけど、そのときになって野宮先生が到着する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3247
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_aa98f9c8:

    # "The teacher is wiping sweat from his forehead with a handkerchief and breathing rather heavily. He quickly glances over the room, then settles down a bit."
    "先生はひたいの汗をハンカチで拭い、息を荒くしている。教室内をざっと見渡すと、少し落ち着く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3252
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_1e1d5080:

    # no "Hello, hello; apologies for being late."
    no "やあやあ、遅くなってすまない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3257
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_aab81076:

    # no "Is everyone present? Good!"
    no "みんな揃ってるな？　よろしい！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3259
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_617fd25a:

    # no "I must confess, I haven't really planned anything for today as I have been extremely busy, lately. But I'm sure we can come up with something entertaining."
    no "実は、ここのところとても忙しくて、今日の活動内容をなにも考えてなくてな。だが心配ない、なにか面白いことを思いつけるだろう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3264
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_44489504:

    # no "Anyone have any suggestions? I was thinking we could have a discussion circle since we haven't had one in a while. I, at least, found the last one magnificently enjoyable."
    no "なにか提案はないかな？　グループ討論はどうだろうと思っていたんだが。しばらくやっていなかったからな。前にやったときは、少なくとも私は大変に楽しかったぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3266
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_17df4ad5:

    # "There are some murmurs here and there, but nobody raises their voice in support of or against Nomiya."
    "つぶやき声がちらほら聞こえてくるけど、先生に対して賛成なり反対なり、声を上げる生徒は一人もいない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3271
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_25f193c9:

    # no "We could delve into various movements of art. Or does someone have a good topic in mind?"
    no "美術界のさまざまな動向について掘り下げるのもいいな。それとも、誰かほかに議題の案はあるかね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3273
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_8fe877b6:

    # no "Come on, throw it out there. It doesn't matter if it's silly or odd, we can always cook up something interesting!"
    no "さあさあ、案があるなら言ってみなさい。くだらなくても妙ちきりんでも関係ない、どんな話題でも興味深い議論に発展できるからな！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3275
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_1e129e48:

    # "Nobody seems to be brave enough to make such a suggestion."
    "誰もなにか提案できるほどの勇気はないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3277
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_099aa443:

    # "As the awkward silence refuses to be broken, I lift my hand in the air."
    "気まずい沈黙が頑として居座るなか、俺は手を宙に上げる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3282
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_3f2b443b:

    # no "Oho? Our newest friend seems to have something on his mind. Speak up, my boy, speak up!"
    no "ほほう？　新入り君には何か考えがあるようだ。さあ言ってごらん、言ってごらん！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3284
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_99b735dd:

    # hi "Um, well… I don't know about anyone else, but I've always wondered why art exists in the first place."
    hi "ああ、ええと……ほかの人がどうかはわかりませんけど、そもそもどうして芸術ってものが存在するのか、いつも不思議に思ってたんです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3288
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_5033daa3:

    # "My voice trails off. A silence sets in the room, and nobody makes a followup on my meek suggestion."
    "俺の声はだんだん小さくなる。沈黙が教室に満ち、誰も俺の情けない提案をフォローしてくれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3290
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_c51be6b0:

    # "Then, the teacher bursts in laughter."
    "そのとき、先生がどっと笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3295
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_cfe3e0f5:

    # no "Hohoho, excellent!"
    no "ほほう、すばらしい！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3297
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_2a2af37d:

    # no "Very good, very good indeed. Right out of the gate with the big one, huh?"
    no "実にいい、まったく、実にいいぞ。しょっぱなから大きなものを持ってきたものだ、なあ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3299
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_c136f4b9:

    # no "Fabulous!"
    no "いやあ、見事だ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3301
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_230507ee:

    # "Chuckling, he shifts some papers around on his desk for a few moments. When he's done, he appears to have made some sort of decision."
    "くすくす笑うと、先生は少しのあいだ机の上の紙を何枚か動かす。それが終わると、なにやら決断したようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3306
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_e92cb623:

    # no "Very well, then. Let us run with this and see where it gets us, shall we?"
    no "よろしい。ではこれをテーマに話し合ってみよう、いいかな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3311
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_40ba4105:

    # no "Oh my, even an old fogey like me gets excited when such delicious enthusiasm is present. Oh my, indeed."
    no "おっと、こういった興味深いことに出会うと私のような年寄りさえつい興奮してしまってな。いやまったく"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3316
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_90a551be:

    # no "Let me gather my thoughts a moment so I can figure out a good starting point for everyone."
    no "みんなが始めやすいポイントを見つけたい、ちょっと考えさせてくれ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3318
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_821b006b:

    # "For some reason the teacher seems to be almost literally bursting with excitement. He scribbles a few things down on a loose sheet of paper, then cleans his glasses with the handkerchief."
    "どういうわけか先生は文字通り爆発しそうなほど興奮している。ルーズリーフになにやら殴り書きして、ハンカチで眼鏡を拭う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3323
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_36f33948:

    # "He strikes a pose, then freezes for an overtly dramatic, artistic pause that spans what must be half a minute."
    "今度はあからさまに芝居がかった、芸術家然としたポーズをとったまま３０秒ぐらい固まる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3325
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_b8ff0b19:

    # "It's so quiet I could hear a pin drop."
    "まわりは水を打ったように静まりかえっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3332
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_76ca357a:

    # no "First, let's come up with a few questions that we want answered, such as 'What is art?' and 'Why does art exist?'"
    no "まず、いくつかはっきりさせたいことを洗い出しておこう。『芸術とはなにか？』、『なぜ芸術が存在するのか？』といったことをな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3337
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_99837b98:

    # no "Anyone have any questions that might be related?"
    no "ほかに関係のありそうな疑問はあるかな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3339
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_14905bda:

    # "The boy with sunglasses pipes up almost immediately. His voice is soft and quiet, and I have a hard time making out what he says."
    "サングラスをかけた男子が、ほとんど間髪を入れずになにか甲高い声でいう。その声はやわらかく静かで、なんて言っているのか聞きわけるのが難しい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3341
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_a981b5fa:

    # "Sunglasses boy" "What defines an artist?"
    "サングラスをかけた男子" "芸術家の定義はなんですか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3343
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_47f0da3c:

    # "After him, another question comes up."
    "彼に続いて、別の質問が挙がる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3345
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_55ea3ef6:

    # "Student" "If I fill a cardboard box with water and call it art, is it art?"
    "生徒" "段ボールの箱を水でいっぱいにして、それを芸術だっていったら、それは芸術ですか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3350
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_efd1d38e:

    # "Everyone laughs at that, even the teacher."
    "みんなそれに笑う。先生もだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3352
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_6ae7cc02:

    # no "Great! Wonderful, all of these!"
    no "すばらしい！　どれも見事なものだ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3357
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_0c941482:

    # no "Let me start by saying that this is not a clear-cut issue by any means, and as such, I'm not going to give any answers to you. I'm only going to speak from my own perspective."
    no "まず始めに、こう言っておこう。これはいかなる意味でもはっきりとした問題ではないから、私からみんなに答えを教えるようなことはしない。私は私自身の観点だけから話させてもらう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3359
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_3e781d62:

    # no "Scholars have argued about these sorts of questions since time immemorial, and there has never really been a broadly applicable consensus reached."
    no "はるか昔から学者たちはこうした質問について議論してきたが、広く認められる合意が得られたことは、実際のところ一度もない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3364
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_a700bec3:

    # no "There are, however, some qualities that most tend to generally agree upon. Hopefully, you all should find these acceptable as well."
    no "しかし、多くの人がおおむね同意するような性質もいくつかはある。おそらく、諸君もそれには納得するだろう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3369
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_5f832f51:

    # no "In short, art defines itself. It simply cannot be contained to a definition from the outside, since the boundaries of art expand and contract from forces within."
    no "端的にいうと、芸術とはそれそのものを定義するものだ。単に外部からの定義の中におさまるものではない。なぜなら芸術の境界は内側からの力で伸び縮みするからだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3374
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_99aef550:

    # no "Every day, someone somewhere comes up with something completely outrageous that challenges any and all preconceptions."
    no "毎日、どこかで誰かが全くもって常識外れな、あらゆる既成の概念に挑むようななにかを生み出している"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3379
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_30c1f671:

    # no "The core reason for this is that rather than the rational side of the mind, art appeals to the intuition, the instinct, the primal. You would find it very hard to explain why exactly it is that you enjoy some particular style or piece, no?"
    no "その核心的な理由は、精神の合理的な部分から来るものではない。むしろ芸術は直感、本能、原始的なものに訴えるんだ 君たちも、ある様式や作品が好きだと思う理由を説明するのが難しいと感じたことがあるだろう、違うかな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3381
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_564d7c01:

    # "He doesn't wait for a response before continuing."
    "先生は続ける前に反応を待ったりはしない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3386
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_a0ae0cd7:

    # no "This is exactly why."
    no "これこそが理由だ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3391
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_d3a74919:

    # no "So, art is this sort of wild, uncontrollable thing that lurks somewhere deep in our subconscious. Now, why does it exist?"
    no "そう、芸術とはある種野生的なもので、潜在意識の底をうろつきまわる、コントロールできないものなんだよ。さて、なぜそれが存在するのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3393
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_0d865976:

    # "Nomiya apparently expects someone to pipe up with a guess, but as nobody dares to interrupt his inspired speech, he continues."
    "どうも野宮先生は誰かが推論を述べるのを期待したみたいだけど、誰も先生の見事なスピーチに割り込む勇気はなかったので、先生は続ける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3398
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_8cb82e5d:

    # no "It was a trick question! You see, art also validates itself."
    no "今のは引っかけだ！　つまりだな、芸術とはそれ自身を正当化するものでもあるんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3403
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_174c2046:

    # no "Generally speaking, you might say that art exists for no other purpose than itself. It's something that exists merely to leave a mark in history."
    no "一般的には、芸術の存在意義とは芸術そのもの以外にないと言えるかもしれない。単に歴史にその跡を残すためだけの存在だと"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3408
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_ba71dc73:

    # no "It's the defiance of a mortal against the face of darkness, as was once said. Art is truly the proof of our existence. You all should know that human culture and civilization are tightly tied to the existence of art."
    no "かつて言われたように、これは闇に立ち向かう、人間の果敢な挑戦なのだ。芸術とはまさに我々の存在の証明だ。人類の文化や文明と、芸術の存在が固く結びついていることは、諸君も知っておかねばならん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3413
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_ebfa51a2:

    # no "Then, what about artists? What drives a man to dedicate his life to a thing so fickle and mysterious that it even defies definition?"
    no "さて、芸術家たちはどうだ？　それ自身の定義を否定することさえある、あまりに移ろいやすく謎めいたものに対して、自分の生涯を捧げるほど人間を駆り立てるものとは一体なんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3418
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_3e7fcfba:

    # no "There are as many answers for this as there are artists, but if I had to put it into words… an artist doesn't make art because he can, but because he must."
    no "芸術家の数だけ答えが存在するが、あえて私が答えるとすれば……芸術家が作品を作るのは、それができるからではない、そうせずにはいられないからなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3420
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_d1c20d8c:

    # "Nomiya takes a pause, and his gaze sweeps over his audience, eyes flaring with passion."
    "野宮先生は一息つくと、情熱に輝く目で聴衆に視線を走らせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3425
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_f4ce15d6:

    # no "It is obvious that art touches the very soul of each and every human being in one way or another. So, if you were given a chance to connect with your fellow man in such a fundamental way, how could you not?"
    no "芸術が、あらゆる人間の心に何らかの感動を与えるのは明らかだ。そこでもし諸君が、他の人々とそんな根源的なつながりを得る機会を与えられたなら、それを活用しない手はあるまい？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3430
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_c91b16e9:

    # no "There is a poem I'm very much fond of, and I shall recite the most well-known part of it to you now. I feel that, for me personally, of all possible things it captures best the essence of what it means to be an artist."
    no "私のとても好きな詩があってな、一番よく知られている部分をみんなにも聞いてもらおう。私個人としては、この詩はあらゆるものの中で、芸術家であることの本質をもっともよく捉えていると思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3434
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_8c5e830e:

    # "Nomiya leans against the desk as he clears his throat in preparation."
    "野宮先生は準備の咳払いをしながら机に寄りかかる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3436
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_21b978ad:

    # "Looking at some distant place, he utters the words in the heavy afternoon air with his soft basso voice."
    "どこか遠く離れた場所を見つめながら、先生は重い午後の空気のなかに、やわらかな低い声で言葉を並べる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3443
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_ea234abd:

    # no "To see a world in a grain of sand"
    no "一粒の砂に世界を見、"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3445
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_3bd0996d:

    # extend "\nAnd a heaven in a wild flower,"
    extend "\n一輪の花に天国を見るために、"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3447
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_9233a1f4:

    # no "Hold infinity in the palm of your hand"
    no "そのたなごころに無限をつかめ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3449
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_83447599:

    # extend "\nAnd eternity in an hour."
    extend "\nそしてひとときのうちに永遠を"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3451
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_12e73d27:

    # "There is a solemn and unbelievably awkward silence after he finishes reciting the short fragment. Nobody dares speak a word."
    "先生が詩の一片を暗唱し終えると、重苦しく、信じられないほど気まずい沈黙が訪れる。みんな一言たりとも口を開こうとはしない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3453
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_211fa5b2:

    # "Nomiya clears his throat again."
    "先生はもう一度咳払いする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3458
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_0032536e:

    # no "To be an artist is to see the world in a grain of sand."
    no "芸術家であるということは、一粒の砂から世界を見出すことなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3463
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_fe9714f7:

    # no "You see, dear children, without art, there would not be much to live for in this world. It is a most profound thing."
    no "わかるかね、諸君。芸術がなかったら、この世界に生きがいはほとんどなくなってしまう。それは実に深遠なものなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3465
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_2136d65a:

    # "He is clearly touched by this notion. I almost expect to see a lone tear rolling down his rough cheek, but it never comes."
    "先生は明らかにこの考え方に心酔している。そのしわっぽい頬に、今にも涙が一粒転がり落ちそうだと思ったけど、そうはならなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3478
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_83eaf9fe:

    # "I turn to Rin and whisper to her."
    "俺は琳のほうを向いてささやく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3480
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_ef034d91:

    # hi "So how is this a discussion circle?"
    hi "で、これのどこがグループ討論なんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3482
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_94da5dae:

    # "She shrugs nonchalantly back at me."
    "琳は無頓着に肩をすくめて見せる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3487
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_92eeef56:

    # rin "The previous ones were the same."
    rin "前もこんな感じだったよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3489
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_fa5fd262:

    # "To his credit, Nomiya does try to get some debate going, but the club seems to be reluctant to comply."
    "先生の名誉のためにいっておくと、先生はなんとか討論を促そうとするけど、美術部の面々は気乗りがしないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3491
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_d4aaa999:

    # "I feel a bit guilty about opening my mouth. Maybe we would've been spared from this."
    "あの時口出しをしてしまったことをちょっと後ろめたく思う。こんなことにはならずに済んだかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3500
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_fe334dac:

    # "As the meeting comes to a close, I realize we haven't once touched any paint or pens today, and I feel somewhat disappointed."
    "部活が終わりに近づくころ、今日はただの一度もペンや絵の具に触れていないことに気づいて、少しがっかりする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3505
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_766f22b8:

    # "Nomiya suddenly appears next to us. He seems to be still fired up from the speech he delivered."
    "先生が突然、俺たちの横に現れる。まださっきの熱演の興奮が冷めていないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3507
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_d71c0543:

    # "His cologne smells musky and saccharine at the same time, giving me an instant headache, even though I'm not sensitive to perfumes. He is looking at Rin like a hungry wolf."
    "コロンがジャコウと砂糖の匂いをいっぺんに放って、香水に敏感でない俺でも一瞬で頭痛をもよおす。先生は腹をすかした狼のように琳を見据えている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3512
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_4b0d3a51:

    # no "Tezuka, do you remember Mrs. Saionji, who visited us at the festival?"
    no "手塚、学園祭のときに会った西園寺さんを覚えているか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3517
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_a3f20c4c:

    # rin "I think so."
    rin "たぶん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3522
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_5ba91c98:

    # no "I'm going to tell you something amazing."
    no "すばらしい話があるんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3527
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_ce328141:

    # no "The thing is, she's a very well-known gallerist around here. It turns out I might be able to get her to consider having some of your work put on display."
    no "実は、彼女はこの辺りではよく知られた美術商でな。お前の作品を展示してもらえないか掛け合うことができるかもしれないぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3529
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_4de5ab33:

    # "He ends his sentence with a dramatic gesture. It seems he's expecting Rin to show some sort of joyous, shocked reaction at such grand news, but she just stares at him blankly."
    "先生は壮大な手振りで言葉を終える。どうも琳がすばらしい知らせを聞いて、歓喜と驚きのリアクションを見せてくれると期待しているみたいだけど、琳はぼんやりと先生を見つめるだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3534
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_be02d23f:

    # no "Magnificent, isn't it? This could be a real chance for us to get ahead, girl."
    no "最高の話じゃないか？　私たちが成功できる、絶好のチャンスだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3539
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_0b20d50d:

    # rin "But…"
    rin "だけど……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3544
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_f97527e3:

    # no "Now now, I know what you're about to say. Yes, it wouldn't be a simple affair, but I think this is an absolutely fantastic opportunity."
    no "まあまあ、何が言いたいかはわかるぞ。確かに、簡単なことではないだろう、だがこれは間違いなくすばらしいチャンスだと思うぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3546
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_52718c55:

    # no "Frankly, I wouldn't be surprised at all if we even made it big! This could be the first step! And then, when the word is out, we strike while the iron is hot! Right, Nakai?"
    no "率直にいって、私はこれが成功を収めたとしてもまったく驚かないぞ！これが最初のステップになるかも知れないんだ！　そして評判が広まったなら、鉄は熱いうちに打てということだ！　そうだろう、中井？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3548
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_25930518:

    # hi "Er, yeah, it does sound pretty great. If you're into that kind of thing."
    hi "え、ええ。なんだかすごそうですね。もしそういうことに興味があるなら"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3553
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_b18a30e4:

    # no "See? We should definitely not let this one pass, am I right?"
    no "そうだろう？　なんとしてもこの機会を逃すわけにはいかない、そう思わんか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3558
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_1300a0a9:

    # rin "I don't… really."
    rin "思いません……あんまり"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3562
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_1a45ab2d:

    # "Rin seems to be troubled for some reason. I can't figure out why. What Nomiya is saying does indeed sound like a possibly great thing."
    "琳はどういうわけか困惑しているようだ。理由はわからない。野宮先生の言っていることは本当にすばらしいことのように聞こえるけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3564
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_4b00488a:

    # "She looks pretty down though, and confused. I've never seen her like this."
    "でも琳はひどく落ち込んで、困惑しているみたいだ。琳のこんな姿は見たことがない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3569
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_9362a39e:

    # no "So, what do you think?"
    no "それで、どう思うかね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3571
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_92211dd8:

    # "Rin looks up to her teacher's glowing face, then back down at her desk."
    "琳は先生のほてった顔を見上げると、自分の机に引き下がる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3576
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_5452cdaa:

    # rin "I'll think about it."
    rin "考えます"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3578
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_9359308f:

    # "Nomiya is at last taken slightly aback by Rin's lack of superlative delight. Then he smiles widely at her and gently pats her head."
    "野宮先生はようやく琳が大喜びしていないことに少し面食らう。そして大きく笑みを見せ、穏やかに琳の頭をぽんと叩く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3583
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_f323091d:

    # no "Good girl."
    no "よしよし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3589
translate jp a2_rin_eternity_in_an_hour_aa837bdc:

    # "The club meeting is finally over, and as I lazily collect my things and help clean up, I start feeling exhausted, for some reason. There isn't much to do, however, so it's over quickly."
    "部活動がやっと終わり、だらだらと用具を集めて掃除を手伝っていると、なぜだか疲れきった気分になる。でもやることはあまりなかったので、すぐに終わってしまった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3599
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_55ca0ab2:

    # "I catch up to Rin who left the club room just a moment earlier, so we're walking down the stairs to the ground floor while I try to go over Nomiya's passionate speech about art, and Rin seems to be lost in thought."
    "俺より一足早く美術室を出ていった琳に追いつくと、野宮先生の芸術に関する情熱的なスピーチを振り返りながら、いっしょに一階まで降りていく。琳は物思いに沈んでいるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3601
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_6456332b:

    # "Not an unusual state for her, I've learned, but something about her expression makes me feel uneasy."
    "琳には珍しくないことなのはわかってる、でもその表情はどこか俺を不安にさせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3603
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_3ac19fb9:

    # hi "Penny for your thoughts."
    hi "お前の考えてることに１０円かけてやるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3608
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_78f89dba:

    # rin "That'd be too cheap."
    rin "安すぎるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3610
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_05767acd:

    # hi "You're just overpricing your thoughts."
    hi "高く見積もりすぎてるだけだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3615
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d9fa5684:

    # rin "I wouldn't be able to sell them anyway. I'm not sure what I'm thinking yet. That'd be fraud too, like stealing a candy from a baby."
    rin "どっちにしろその賭けには乗れないよ。まだなに考えてるかわかんないし。これじゃ詐欺になっちゃうね、赤ちゃんからお菓子を盗んじゃうみたいにさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3617
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_0574cbb9:

    # hi "That's theft, not fraud."
    hi "それは窃盗だろ、詐欺じゃない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3622
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_1e910d38:

    # rin "I have to think about what I think."
    rin "なにを考えるのか考えなきゃ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3624
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_27afa9c7:

    # hi "Is this about what the teacher said? Getting your work put on display and all that?"
    hi "先生が言ってたことか？　お前の絵を展示するとかって？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3629
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_1717dcfa:

    # "She doesn't answer, but stops in her tracks as we reach the lobby."
    "琳は答えずに、ロビーについたところで足を止める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3631
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d3bf30d4:

    # "We're the only people around, so it's very quiet. Footsteps echo from a few floors up as someone hurries along a hallway."
    "周りには誰もいなくて、とても静かだ。誰かが廊下を駆けると、足音が上の階から響いてくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3636
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_fa15ff7c:

    # rin "I think I'm going to go somewhere elsewhere."
    rin "どこかここじゃないとこに行こうと思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3638
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b6d89494:

    # "I think she really is troubled."
    "本当に混乱してるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3640
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_c626855c:

    # hi "Want company?"
    hi "一緒に行こうか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3642
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_0373c276:

    # hi "I can't promise much help with the thinking, but it's not like I have much else to do, and I'm supposed to do some light exercise."
    hi "琳の考えごとの役に立てるって保証はないけど、でも他にやることがあるわけじゃないし、軽い運動もしないといけないし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3647
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_51dd9351:

    # rin "If you like."
    rin "ご自由に"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3654
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d6a8ab53:

    # "Rin leads me outside, to the wall behind the dormitories. There is a small back gate there, made from the same wrought iron as the main gate. It leads to the shadowy woodland park behind the school."
    "琳は俺を寮の裏の壁のところまで連れ出す。そこには正門と同じ鍛鉄でできた小さな裏門がある。その先は学校の向こうにある暗い森まで続いている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3656
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_dfe29ccc:

    # "The gate is rusty, as if it hasn't seen much use. However, it sits open, so we pass through. It's not forbidden for students to leave the grounds, but somehow I feel a little uneasy."
    "門は錆びついていて、あまり使われていないかのようだ。でも開きっぱなしだったので、通り抜ける。学校を抜け出すことは禁止されていないけれど、なんだか不安になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3661
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_6fedf770:

    # "A path leads deeper into the forest. Tall zelkova and maple trees rustle in the wind, their canopies creating patches of chill air hanging in the places where the shadows fall."
    "通り道は森の奥深くまで続いている。高いケヤキとカエデの木が風に揺られてカサカサと音を立て、林冠の影の落ちたところに冷たい空気が漂っている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3663
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_f8ea4e28:

    # "The forest smells strongly of earth. I almost feel cold, even though the midsummer day is as hot as ever."
    "森は強い土の匂いがする。例年通りの暑い真夏の日なのに、俺は肌寒いとさえ感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3665
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_308895cd:

    # "Rin trudges ahead like a sleepwalker, surefooted but with no apparent destination in mind. Her thoughts seem to be somewhere else. I follow a few steps behind, taking more care to watch where my feet land."
    "琳は夢遊病者のようにとぼとぼと前へ進む。足取りは確かだけど、特に行き先は考えてなさそうに見える。心ここにあらずという感じだ。俺は足の着く場所によりいっそう注意しながら、その数歩後ろをついていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3667
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8bd4bda0:

    # "The path follows the land uphill at a low angle, sometimes making little detours downhill before climbing back upward. The muted brown and gray trunks line the path on both sides, peppered with ferns and other undergrowth."
    "道はゆったりとした上り坂で、時折回り道をするかのようにちょっと下り坂になると、また上りになったりする。通り道の両脇には落ち着いた茶色や灰色の幹が並んでいて、シダと下生えにびっしり覆われている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3672
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_fbbdc337:

    # "After a little while, I start getting worried. The path is still wide and clear, so there's no chance of getting lost, but it doesn't look like we have any particular destination."
    "少ししてから、俺は心配になり始める。通り道はいまだに広く見通しがよくて、道に迷う可能性はないけど、その終わりに何かがあるようには見えない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3674
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_487bbb76:

    # "There's nothing wrong with a bit of aimless wandering around, but I don't want to go so far that I get too tired to walk back."
    "少し当てもなく辺りをふらつくぐらいなら何の問題もないけど、疲れすぎて戻れなくなるほど遠くまでは行きたくない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3679
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e6e7b548:

    # "I'm starting to get a little winded and my legs feel heavy. I want to stop and get a chance to catch my breath and rest my legs, but Rin keeps on going."
    "少し息切れし始めてきて、足も重くなってくる。息を整えて足を休めるために立ち止まりたくなるけど、琳は進みつづける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3681
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8f0d09e4:

    # hi "Where are we going? Or are we going anywhere at all?"
    hi "どこに行くんだよ？　っていうか、そもそもどこかに向かってるのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3686
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_63a7ec81:

    # rin "Worry Tree."
    rin "心配の木だよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3688
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3690
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e4481879:

    # hi "So what exactly is the Worry Tree?"
    hi "なんだよ、心配の木って"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3695
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_cd1eb3e1:

    # rin "It's just a tree. Like this."
    rin "木は木だよ。こういうの"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3697
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8ddb09b9:

    # "She stops in front of a particularly large maple that might or might not be the Worry Tree. Its lush green leaves sway lightly in the breeze blowing through the small clearing we entered."
    "琳はとりわけ大きいカエデの木、心配の木のようなそうでないような木の前で止まる。緑の豊かな葉が、俺たちの分け入った小さな空間を吹き抜けるそよ風に小さく揺れ動いている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3699
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d5d1e4a4:

    # hi "I guessed as much."
    hi "そのくらいはわかるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3704
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_88e3a193:

    # rin "There are people who believe that you must come here to wallow in misery, if you are miserable, only by 'people' I mean me, and the tree isn't really called anything."
    rin "悲しいときはここに来て悲しみに浸らなきゃいけない、って考える人たちがいるんだ。といっても『人たち』ってのは私のことなんだけど。あと、この木は実際には名前なんて付いてないから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3706
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_40a7e2f8:

    # hi "So… if you're miserable, you talk to a tree about it?"
    hi "じゃあ……お前は悲しいときは木にそのことを話すのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3711
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_6cb662e5:

    # rin "No. What? You can't talk to trees. What do you think I am, crazy?"
    rin "ううん。なにそれ？　木とは話せないでしょ。私のこと、なんだと思ってるの。頭おかしいって思った？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3713
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_f0e285df:

    # hi "No… I didn't mean it like that."
    hi "いや……そういう意味じゃなくってさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3718
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ca776f1b:

    # rin "Or maybe you talk to trees? I'm sorry, I didn't mean to say that you are crazy. Even though you probably are if you talk to trees."
    rin "それとも君は木と話してるの？　ごめんね、君が頭おかしいって言いたいんじゃないんだ。本当に木と話してるならたぶんそうだと思うけどね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3723
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ed2ed07c:

    # rin "I wouldn't recommend it in either case. People will think you are a weird person."
    rin "どっちにしてもおすすめはしないよ。変な人だと思われるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3725
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_6f5e3c64:

    # hi "No, I… just forget it."
    hi "違う、俺は……いいや、忘れてくれ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3727
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b061861d:

    # "She looks mildly confused, for which I don't blame her at all. She tilts her head a little to the side, expression melting back to her usual one."
    "琳は少し混乱してるみたいだ。無理もないけど。琳はわずかに首をかしげると、ゆっくりといつもの表情に戻っていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3732
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_f9660359:

    # rin "All right. I'm good at forgetting things."
    rin "いいよ。忘れるのは得意なんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3734
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_acec14c1:

    # hi "So why are we here? Are you miserable then?"
    hi "それで、なんで俺たちはここにいるんだ？　なにか悲しいのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3736
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_6062c6aa:

    # "I can't read the expression she makes. I hate how bad I am at interpreting Rin's mood."
    "琳の表情からはなにも読み取れない。琳の気分をまるで察することができない自分が嫌になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3741
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_dda2fe5b:

    # "She doesn't answer right away, as if she herself isn't quite certain of her own mood. The blank stare changes into a more difficult expression as she shuffles her weight around."
    "自分の気持ちを自分でもはっきり理解できていないかのように、琳はすぐには答えない。すり足で辺りを歩き回っているうちに、その虚ろな視線がさらに難しい表情に変わる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3746
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_2b5cfa9d:

    # "Finally, coming to a conclusion, Rin shrugs her shoulders. I've grown to seriously dislike that gesture. It doesn't mean anything."
    "ようやく結論にたどりついて、琳は肩をすくめる。俺はそのしぐさが本気で疎ましくなってくる。なんの意味もない動作だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3751
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e7b33cbb:

    # rin "Maybe. I just feel kind of like I'm sinking underwater. I don't know what I should do."
    rin "そうかも。水の中に沈んでいってるような感じがする。どうしたらいいのかわかんないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3756
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_dfebcc5e:

    # rin "I don't know where I should go, that's all. Maybe it's not a big deal but I thought walking might help. Kind of like, if I go somewhere I would know where I should go. I don't really know if it did."
    rin "どこに行けばいいのかわからない、それだけなんだ。大したことじゃないんだろうけどさ、でも歩きに行けばわかるかもと思って どこかに行けば、どこに行くべきなのかわかるんじゃないかって思ってたんだ。役に立ったかどうかはなんとも言えないけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3761
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_15ae8b9b:

    # rin "It really would've made sense if walking had helped to decide where to go."
    rin "歩いたことがどこに行くべきかを決めるのに役立ったのなら、すごく納得がいくんだけどね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3763
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_058a3bfe:

    # hi "So you don't want to try to get an exhibition? Or rather, you don't know if you do? Can't decide?"
    hi "それじゃ作品の展示はしたくないのか？　っていうより、自分がそうしたいかどうかわからないのか？　決められないのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3765
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_56092fb0:

    # "Rin doesn't say anything for a while, arranging her thoughts in silence. The quiet is broken by birdsong from somewhere in the treetops, followed by rustling leaves as the bird takes flight."
    "琳はしばらくなにも言わず、黙って考えをまとめている。どこか木の上から聞こえてくる小鳥のさえずりで静けさが破られると、それに続いて小鳥が飛び立ち、葉がかさかさと音を立てる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3770
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8e5cc23a:

    # rin "Maybe. I'm not sure if I can have a thing like that. So far I've only painted for myself."
    rin "たぶん。そんなこと私がしていいのかどうかわかんないんだ。いままで自分のためにしか描いてこなかったし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3775
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_015a513e:

    # rin "I don't think I could have my things on display the way I am now. This me couldn't do it."
    rin "今の私じゃ、展示できるようなものを作れるとは思えないんだ。この私じゃできないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3777
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_2b01448f:

    # "Her reason sounds like a weak excuse. I make my trademark frown but she doesn't notice it."
    "琳の理由は言い訳に聞こえる。俺は得意のしかめ面をして見せるけど、琳は気づかない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3779
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d2b7b0d6:

    # hi "I don't get it. The teacher certainly thinks you could. I don't think he'd suggest it otherwise. Sounds like he's calling in favors from his friends, too."
    hi "わからないな。絶対先生はできると思ってるだろ。そうでもないのにこんなこと提案するとは思わないけど。先生の友達にも頼みごとをしてるみたいだったし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3784
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8d4ce0e4:

    # rin "I know. He's really done a lot for me. But this might be too much."
    rin "わかってる。先生は本当にいろんな世話をしてくれたよ。でも今度はちょっとやりすぎかも"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3789
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8da25209:

    # rin "Becoming someone who can do it might be pretty hard. Maybe I couldn't do it at all. He can't do it for me and if I let him try, I'd just sink deeper and deeper."
    rin "こんなことができるような人になるのは大変そうだよ。私、全然できないかもしれない。私のために先生にこんなことしてほしくない、でもこのまま話を進められたら、私はもっと深いところに沈んじゃう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3791
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_4928910f:

    # "Rin stands in front of the large maple and turns away from me. I want to close the few feet of distance between us and… I don't know. My irritation is suddenly gone, and I start feeling sympathetic to her."
    "琳は大きなカエデの木の前に立って、俺に背を向ける。俺との間の数歩の距離を縮めたいと思う。それと……なんだろう。とつぜん俺のいらだちは消え失せ、琳に共感を覚え始めている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3793
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_180d9838:

    # hi "I know exactly how you feel."
    hi "その気持ち、よくわかるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3795
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_3e2c7ed3:

    # hi "Well, maybe I don't, but still."
    hi "まあ、わかってないかもしれないけど、それでもさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3797
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8353cf25:

    # hi "I think I haven't felt like I was actually in control of my own life this whole year. I'm just helplessly going along with the flow."
    hi "俺は今年の間ずっと、自分の生き方を自分でコントロールできてるって気がしなかった。なすすべもなく流されてるだけだった"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3799
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_f635c2b8:

    # hi "Like coming here to this school. I didn't really choose it myself. And I certainly didn't choose this time of my life to learn that I have… this condition."
    hi "この学校に来ることとかさ。自分で選んだわけじゃなかった。絶対に人生のこの時期なんて選ぶわけがない、自分がこんな……病気だって知るなんて"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3801
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e26040b8:

    # "I still can't casually say the word aloud."
    "俺はいまだにその言葉を気軽に口にできない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3803
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e4ab1c42:

    # hi "It's like… yeah, it's exactly like being underwater. Like I can't even breathe."
    hi "なんていうかこう……そうだ、まさに水の中なんだよ。息もできないみたいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3808
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_29674058:

    # "Rin turns to face me again, a sad expression on her face."
    "琳はまた俺のほうを向く、その顔は悲しい表情をしている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3810
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b74efa90:

    # rin "Is that why you look so sad all the time? I don't want to look sad like you. Do I look to you like you look to me?"
    rin "だから君はいつもそんな悲しそうなの？　私、君みたいに悲しそうな顔したくない。君が見てる私は、私が見てる君みたいに見えてるの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3812
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_61eefbcf:

    # hi "I don't look sad all the time."
    hi "別に四六時中悲しそうに見えたりはしてないだろ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3814
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_6e6f03cc:

    # hi "I just… don't know what I should be feeling. What kind of face I should be making."
    hi "俺はただ……自分がどう感じればいいのかわからないんだ。どんな顔をすればいいのか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3819
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ff4b0f7c:

    # rin "Me neither. Do I look sad now?"
    rin "私もだよ。私、悲しそうに見えてる？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3821
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_1dcb52cc:

    # hi "Not really. You look like you always do, I think."
    hi "いいや。いつも通りに見えてると思うぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3826
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e6421df2:

    # rin "But I'm sinking."
    rin "でも私、沈んでる"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3831
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_55ffe3c4:

    # rin "I should try to float. Up, like a rubber duck. Quack quack all yellow and creepy."
    rin "浮き上がってみなきゃいけないね。ゴムのあひるみたいにさ。ガーガーいって黄色くて気味悪いの"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3833
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_22af5774:

    # "I have to think for a few seconds about which direction I should pursue in this conversation, then I realize that it doesn't matter."
    "この会話をどの方向に追っていけばいいのかしばらく考えないといけなかったけど、別にどうでもいいことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3835
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_248b15b9:

    # hi "You think rubber ducks are creepy?"
    hi "ゴムのあひるって気味悪いか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3840
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_0cf29910:

    # rin "You don't? I think they look very creepy. Everything that has eyes but isn't alive is very disturbing. Like rubber ducks and reflections in mirrors."
    rin "そう思わないの？　すっごい不気味だと思うよ。目がついてるけど生きてないものは全部気味が悪くてしかたないよ。ゴムのあひるとか、鏡に映った自分とか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3851
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_12528d94:

    # "She plops down on the forest bed, leaning on the maple she named the Worry Tree. After wondering what to do for a minute, I sit down too, three feet apart from her."
    "琳は積もった葉の上にどすんと腰を下ろし、心配の木と自分で名付けたカエデの木にもたれかかる。どうしようか少し迷ったあと、琳から１メートルほど離れたところに俺も座る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3861
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e32a673b:

    # "The forest envelops us in its embrace, and its stillness falls upon the two of us."
    "森の抱擁が俺たちを包み込み、静寂が二人の上に覆い被さる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3863
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_c7cfb25e:

    # "We sit there without speaking for a long while. I can literally feel the time passing."
    "俺たちはしばらくのあいだ、話しもせずに座り込む。時間が流れていくのが文字通り肌で感じられる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3865
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_35219f52:

    # "Patches of sunlight litter the small clearing in a pattern that echoes the maple canopies. One of them falls directly on me, warming me all the way to the bone."
    "小さな空き地のところどころに陽光が差し込み、頭上を覆うカエデの木々の形と同じ模様を描く。そのうちのひとつが俺に直接降り注いできて、俺は体の芯まで暖まる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3867
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_17909459:

    # "I wonder what I could do for myself, and maybe for Rin. For now, I just keep watching her from this distance."
    "俺は自分自身に何ができるだろう。そして琳にも。今はただ、この距離から琳を見守り続けている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3869
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_005b75b5:

    # "Sometimes she cranes her neck all the way back, so much that it looks almost painful, and stares up at the small patch of sky visible past the canopy of the Worry Tree."
    "ときどき琳は首を思い切り後ろに伸ばす。痛そうに見えるくらい、すごい角度だ。そして心配の木の枝葉の向こうに見える小さな空の切れ端を見上げる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3871
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_4933485c:

    # "Sometimes she just stares blankly ahead, as if seeing something just beyond her reach. She keeps whispering to herself but so quietly that I can't hear her, even though I'm sitting right next to her."
    "時折、あと少しで手の届かない何かを見ているかのように、琳はただ虚ろに前を見つめる。なにか独り言をささやき続けているけど声が小さすぎて、すぐ隣に座っているのに俺には聞くことができない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3873
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_c684f6a0:

    # "I only see her lips moving, like she was in the middle of a distant dream."
    "琳がおぼろな夢を見ているかのように、そのくちびるだけが動いているのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3875
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_f4a63bcf:

    # "I realize that right now, I no longer feel any of the intense loneliness I feel at night, just before falling asleep."
    "夜になって眠りに落ちる直前に感じるような強烈な孤独感を、俺はもう全然感じていないことにたったいま気づく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3877
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_0e82fdc2:

    # "I might be more like Rin than I thought."
    "思っていた以上に琳に似てきたんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3879
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_0987d927:

    # "I can either give up and stay submerged under the weight of all the crap in my life, or try to change myself for the better."
    "俺は諦めてすべてのくだらないことの重みを受けて沈んでいくこともできるし、もっと自分を良くしようと努力することもできる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3881
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_6e0ca6f2:

    # "Her decision is different, yet the same."
    "琳の決断は違うけど、でも同じことだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3883
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_c0a85e27:

    # "And unlike her, I know for sure that I can't stay like this forever."
    "それに琳とは違って、いつまでもこのままでいられるわけがないことを俺はわかっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3898
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_035b3b76:

    # "It makes me feel a little bit better too, and I lean back against the tree, breathing out deeply as if for the first time in a long time."
    "そう考えると、俺も少し気分が良くなる。俺は木にもたれかかって、久しぶりにそうするかのように深く息をつく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3906
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_904c3ca2:

    # "We stay that way in the small clearing until the angle of sun changes and the chilly shadows deepen. No longer warm where we sit, we leave the forest, returning along the same path we took coming in."
    "太陽が傾いて、ひんやりとした影が濃くなるまで、俺たちはその小さい空間に居続ける。座っている場所はもう暖かくなく、俺たちは森を出て、もと来た道を戻っていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3912
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_914b75f2:

    # "It doesn't seem like Rin has come to a decision."
    "琳はまだ決心がついていないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3914
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_54ca5f71:

    # hi "I wonder if it was a bad idea for me to come along."
    hi "俺が一緒に来たのはまずかったかな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3919
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8300ae51:

    # rin "It's all right. I don't mind. I'm sure the trees and dirt and rocks won't mind either. Did you mind?"
    rin "そんなことないよ。気にしてない。木も土も岩も気にしないはずだよ。君は気にしてたの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3921
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e08dabae:

    # hi "No, not at all. I think it helped me too."
    hi "いや、全然。俺にも役に立ったと思うよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3927
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_7c03f9d0:

    # "While we walk back towards the dormitories, the sky is changing to a deep ultramarine. The first summer stars twinkle softly from between spots in the canopy, barely visible like tiny fireflies."
    "寮に向かって歩いていると、空が群青色に変わっていく。林冠の隙間にわずかに見える、小さな蛍のような最初の夏の星が、やわらかく瞬いている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3929
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ae426c4d:

    # "I become very self-conscious about Rin's presence."
    "琳がいることに、俺はやけに照れくさくなる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3931
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3936
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_83a6b97f:

    # n "{vspace=120}I haven't thought much about girls since things fell apart with Iwanako."
    n "\n\n\n\n岩魚子との関係がだめになってから、女の子のことはあまり考えてこなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3938
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e0b09e72:

    # n "This is kind of the same situation as then, but to be honest I don't think it really counts for much. Not with Rin."
    n "あのときのシチュエーションとある意味では同じだけど、でも正直なところ、これはノーカンだろうと思う。琳はそういうのとは違う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3940
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_827f9bb0:

    # n "And yet… it feels good walking next to her, even if it isn't anything more than this."
    n "それなのに……それだけでしかないとしても、琳と並んで歩くのはいい気分がする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3942
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_a24885ee:

    # n "At first, I think Rin agitated me quite a bit with her unpredictable behavior. But recently, I feel I haven't had to be on my toes so much."
    n "最初のころは、琳の気まぐれな行動にはかなりイライラさせられた。でも最近は、そんなに身構える必要もなくなったように感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3944
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_56c501ed:

    # n "I've managed to let myself go a little. It makes me feel satisfied, even though ultimately I think it's more thanks to Rin than myself."
    n "少しはリラックスできるようになった。その点は満足している。突き詰めると俺自身というより琳のおかげだと思うけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3946
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_0fbf19d2:

    # n "She seems to be disinterested in a huge number of things, but something in her makes me try harder than I normally would."
    n "琳はそれこそほとんどのことに無関心なようだけど、琳の中にあるなにかが、俺を普段よりも努力するように駆り立てる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3948
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b68c7331:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=90}It's not that I want to impress her; I think that truly impressing Rin would take near-superhuman effort just because of how she is. Instead, it's because there is this relentless feeling inside of me that I shouldn't let Rin down."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n別に琳にかっこいいとこを見せたいわけじゃない。人間離れした能力の持ち主である琳に本当に好印象を与えようとしたら、超人的な努力が必要になるだろう。そうじゃなくて、琳を落胆させちゃいけないという強い気持ちが俺の心の中にあるんだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3952
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ef339d92:

    # n "It's really weird. I wonder why I started thinking like that. I don't even know what sort of expectations she has about pretty much anything."
    n "ほんとうに妙な話だ。なんでそんなことを考え始めてるんだろう。それがどんなことであれ、琳がどんな期待を抱いているのか、俺にはさっぱりわからないのに。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3954
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_7839c7f1:

    # n "So how could I let her down? Rin has this unassuming air around her, and she doesn't really talk about stuff very often. Even today's confession of her self-doubt caught me a little bit off guard."
    n "じゃあ俺のせいで琳が落胆することなんてことがありえるか？　琳はいつも控えめな態度で、どんなことでもあまり多くを語らない。自信をなくしているという今日の告白だって、俺にはちょっと予想外だった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3956
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_4970dbc1:

    # n "I feel like I want to talk more with her."
    n "もっと琳と話をしたい気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3958
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_c9c42da6:

    # n "The realization suddenly dawns on me that Rin is basically the only person I talk to nowadays, apart from whatever I have to endure from Shizune, Misha or Kenji. I feel slightly depressed."
    n "必然的に会話せざるを得ない静音、ミーシャ、健二を除けば、最近の俺はほとんど琳一人としか話をしていない、という事実に突然思い至る。少し気が滅入る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3960
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3970
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_5d0f5756:

    # "In front of the dormitories, as if summoned by my dark thoughts, we run into Kenji himself."
    "寮の前までくると、俺の暗い考えに呼び寄せられたかのように、健二と鉢合わせする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3976
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_2caaf123:

    # "It feels very odd seeing him outside, breathing fresh outdoor air. At least it's already dusk; I partially expect Kenji would disintegrate upon direct exposure to the sun."
    "新鮮な外の空気を吸いながら健二の姿を見るのはすごく妙な気分だ。一応夕暮れ時ではあるけど。直接太陽の光に体をさらしたら、健二は崩れ去ってしまうんじゃないか、となんとなく思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3978
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_01686d04:

    # "Kenji himself seems very insecure as well, standing around looking like he's waiting for something, but doesn't know himself what it might be."
    "当の本人はとても不安そうにしている。なにかを待っているかのように突っ立って辺りを見回しているけど、それがなんなのか自分でもわかってないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3980
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ea83fe0a:

    # hi "Hey, Kenji. What're you doing?"
    hi "よう健二。なにやってるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:3992
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "やあ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4000
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b2ed8184:

    # ke "Who're you?"
    ke "誰だお前ら？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4007
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ede2449a:

    # hi "It's me, Hisao. Umm… I'm not sure if you know Tezuka from class 3-4?"
    hi "俺だよ、久夫。うーん……４組の手塚のことは知ってるっけ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4012
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d162d306:

    # "From his face I can see that not only he doesn't know Rin, he also can't see her from this short distance."
    "健二の顔を見れば、琳のことを知らないだけでなくて、この近さでも琳のことが見えていないのがわかる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4020
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_a5e576a5:

    # ke "Oh, sup dudes?"
    ke "そうか、よろしくな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4025
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_a70886f4:

    # "Kenji sticks his hand enthusiastically forward, almost straight into Rin's stomach."
    "健二は琳のお腹のほぼ手前に向けて、熱っぽく手を突き出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4030
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8b162ef9:

    # "Rin looks at his outstretched hand in confusion until Kenji clears his throat and retracts the hand."
    "琳は伸ばされた健二の手を困惑したように見ている。やがて健二は咳払いをして手を引っ込める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4035
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d12ee81b:

    # "There is something almost cool that he manages to do with social awkwardness. It's not like I'm the most suave man on the planet, but I don't think I'll ever be able to even approach Kenji's level."
    "こうやって健二が自分の社会不適合と折り合いをつけているのは、すごいと言ってもいいくらいだ。 俺は別に地球上でいちばん人当たりがいい男ってわけじゃないけど、健二ほどのレベルには近づくことさえできないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4037
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_9efa1797:

    # "I think I respect Kenji a little bit more."
    "少し健二を見直した。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4042
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_2e80be82:

    # hi "So you're waiting for someone?"
    hi "それで、誰か待ってるのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4047
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_2f67cc15:

    # "He leans closer and lowers his voice to an agitated whisper. I see his facial muscles twitching."
    "健二は俺のほうに身を寄せてきて、声をひそめて取り乱したようにささやく。顔の筋肉が引きつっているのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4049
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_0305cd74:

    # ke "Come on man, you know I can't talk about stuff here in public. They might be listening."
    ke "なに言ってんだお前、そんなこと人前じゃ話せないって分かってんだろ。奴らが聞いてるかも知れないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4051
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b45963a5:

    # ke "I'm going to have to go pick up some stuff from somewhere, and I don't want those snooping student council hags to get on my case."
    ke "ある場所から取ってこなきゃいけないブツがあってな、あのあちこち嗅ぎまわってる生徒会のババアどもに邪魔されたくないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4053
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_9556e336:

    # ke "Also, I don't trust your friend. Nothing personal. Are you sure he's trustworthy?"
    ke "それに、お前の連れも信じられない。別に悪気はないんだ。そいつは信用できるのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4055
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_1c930ba4:

    # "I briefly consider telling Kenji about Rin's gender, but as it might end up badly for one or both of them, I decide against it."
    "琳の性別を教えてやるかどうかしばらく考えるけど、どちらか、あるいは両方にとって悪い結果になりそうなので、やめておく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4057
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_5d785560:

    # hi "Yeah, I'm sure."
    hi "ああ、もちろん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4063
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_41e367da:

    # "He turns from me to Rin, and I immediately get the feeling that I have to prevent them from talking to each other with whatever means necessary. However, there is little I can do now, apart from physical violence."
    "健二が俺から琳のほうを向くと、瞬間的に二人がしゃべるのをなにがなんでも止めなきゃいけない気がする。でも俺が今できることは、肉体的な暴力はさておいて、ほとんどない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4068
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_ba56f1c3:

    # ke "In that case, would you be interested in knowing about the worst threat to mankind since they invented vegetarianism?"
    ke "それなら、菜食主義が考え出されて以来の、人類最大の脅威について興味はないか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4070
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_e5320a8c:

    # "He sounds like a vacuum cleaner salesman."
    "掃除機のセールスマンみたいな口ぶりだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4075
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_15a9c748:

    # rin "I thought it was Sunday."
    rin "それって、日曜日のことじゃないの"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4081
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_c55f6e4f:

    # ke "I see you're not in the know. Yeah man, I'm talking about man-eating cows here. Very few people know what I know, so I'm not surprised."
    ke "事情を知らないみたいだな。いいか、俺は人食い牛の話をしてるんだ。これを知ってる人間はほとんどいないから、無理もないけどな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4086
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b20e0456:

    # ke "We can't talk here, but if you'd like a pamphlet, come to my room after curfew on Mondays or Wednesdays."
    ke "ここじゃ話せないが、もしパンフレットが欲しければ、月曜か水曜の消灯時間が過ぎてから俺の部屋に来い"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4088
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_7964be6e:

    # "He suddenly reaches to his pocket and draws out a ballpoint pen and what looks like a convenience store receipt."
    "健二はとつぜんポケットに手を突っ込むと、ボールペンとコンビニのレシートのようなものを取り出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4090
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_4bb763ce:

    # "Kenji furiously scribbles on the scrap of paper and then thrusts it towards Rin."
    "紙切れに乱暴になにか殴り書きすると、それを琳に押しつける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4095
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_1611bc00:

    # ke "Here's the password. Memorize it and then eradicate any trace of this document. Eat it, burn it, dissolve in acid, whatever."
    ke "これが合い言葉だ。覚えたら、この書類はいっさい証拠を残さずに処分しろ。食べるなり、焼くなり、酸で溶かすなりしてくれ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4097
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b0f92ec9:

    # "I take the receipt from Kenji as Rin is unable to do so, and glance at it. It's indeed a receipt, apparently for two rice balls and five boxes of matches. I hope he is not planning to burn anything down."
    "琳は受け取れないので、俺が健二からレシートを取って、ちらっと目を通す。おにぎり２つと、マッチ５箱を買ったレシートだ。なにかに放火する気じゃないだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4099
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_3a1ab798:

    # "On the other side is written just one word."
    "裏には一言だけ書いてある。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4106
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_4784949f:

    # "I show it to Rin too, but she shows no reaction."
    "琳にも見せるけど、なんのリアクションも見せない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4111
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_2393106c:

    # rin "Thank you."
    rin "ありがと"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4116
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_3ef9daaf:

    # ke "Yo, Hisao. You still in that club? The club of dark arts?"
    ke "なあ、久夫。まだ部活やってるのか？　闇の魔術部だっけか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4121
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_c937c358:

    # hi "Fine art. Anyway yeah, actually just had a meeting today."
    hi "美術だよ。まあとにかく、ちょうど今日部活があったよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4127
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_85284389:

    # ke "Still got your wits about you? No shady mind tricks going on? Nothing personal man, but I have to be on top of things."
    ke "油断してないだろうな？　怪しいペテンに引っかかってないか？　悪く思わないでくれ、でも俺はどんなことでも把握しておかないといけないからな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4132
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_847a906f:

    # ke "Can't get caught with my pants down. Speaking of which, you should really take showers a bit later. Gotta respect that personal space. Nothing personal."
    ke "ズボンを下ろしたとこを不意打ちされるわけにはいかないんだよ。ちなみに、シャワー浴びるときは少し時間をあとにしろよな。プライベートな空間には気を使うもんだ。気を悪くするなよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4134
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_79d6830c:

    # "Kenji looks around as if he heard something and then straightens his jacket."
    "健二はなにかを聞きつけたかのように辺りを見回すと、上着を整える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4139
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_970c34f5:

    # ke "Okay, I gotta scoot now before it gets too late. Later dudes. Good luck."
    ke "よし、手遅れになる前に先へ行くぜ。また後でな、幸運を祈る"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4150
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_69c5f45a:

    # "Kenji takes off rapidly towards the main gate. Rin looks after him, frowning."
    "健二はすばやく正門に向かって進みだす。琳はしかめ面をしながらその後ろ姿を見ている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4152
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_8beccee6:

    # "We watch after Kenji's diminishing figure in silence."
    "俺たちは言葉もなく、健二の姿が小さくなっていくのを見つめる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4157
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d7c94855:

    # rin "What's wrong with him?"
    rin "あの人はなんなの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4159
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_b7adfa97:

    # hi "Technically speaking, I think he's legally blind."
    hi "厳密にいうと、法的盲ってやつだと思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4164
translate jp a2_rin_underwater_and_maple_d10d767d:

    # rin "Oh. I see."
    rin "ああ。なるほどね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4180
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_2ca1a556:

    # "I can immediately tell from the envelope that it's not about official matters of any sort. Someone actually wrote me an old-fashioned, hand-written paper letter."
    "その封筒を見てすぐに、これがなにかの公的な代物ではないとわかる。誰かが実際に、手書きという昔ながらのやり方で手紙を送ってきたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4182
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_b4d9e490:

    # "Who bothers doing something like that in this day and age, anyway? Yet, as unlikely as the prospect of receiving one sounds, there is definitely a letter lying on my desk."
    "いまどき誰がこんな面倒なことをするっていうんだ？　でも、どんなにその可能性が低いように聞こえたとしても、間違いなく俺の机の上には手紙が置かれている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4187
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_7f6487e7:

    # "The classes for the day are over. Still feeling pretty full from the big lunch that I had unexpectedly eaten at the cafeteria, I returned to my dorm, planning on finishing my homework and probably skipping dinner, or at least just eating light."
    "今日の授業は終わった。食堂で食べた昼食が予想外に多く、まだ腹が張っていて、宿題を片付けて夕食は抜くか、あるいは軽めにしておくか、と考えながら寮に戻った。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4189
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_db2c1b23:

    # "I feel like I need to eat less than I used to. Maybe I don't use that much energy, now that I don't do much beyond reading."
    "以前よりも食べる量を減らしたほうがいい気がする。今は本を読む以上のことはあまりしないから、そんなにエネルギーを使っていないのかもな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4191
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_398d09a6:

    # "However, the letter on my desk has naturally caught my interest."
    "でも、机の上に置かれた手紙は、自然に俺の興味を引いた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4199
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_d21c5bd8:

    # "It's the first piece of mail I've received here at Yamaku, so it'd feel special even if it wasn't something as rare as a handwritten letter."
    "山久学園に来てから受け取った最初の手紙だから、仮に手書きの手紙という珍しいものでなかったとしても、格別な気分がしただろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4201
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_2beb101c:

    # "What causes me even more trepidation is the name of the sender, written neatly on the back of the envelope."
    "さらに俺を不安にさせたのは、封筒の裏に丁寧に書かれた差出人の名前だった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4203
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_8549b9ff:

    # "Iwanako."
    "岩魚子。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4205
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_799ef6f3:

    # "I have no idea why she would write to me. I haven't been in contact with anyone from my old school since I transferred, and Iwanako is the last person I'd expect to want to write me a letter."
    "どうして岩魚子が俺に手紙を書いたのかまったくわからない。転校してきてから前の学校にいた連中とは誰とも連絡はとっていないし、岩魚子はいちばん俺に手紙を寄越しそうにない人間だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4207
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4213
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_2101c589:

    # n "{vspace=90}The last time I saw Iwanako was terribly awkward; embarrassingly so. She came to my hospital room, peeled me an apple out of courtesy and then we practically sat in silence for half an hour."
    n "\n\n\n最後に岩魚子と会ったときは、恐ろしく気まずかった。恥ずかしいくらいだった。俺の病室に来ると義理っぽくりんごの皮をむいてくれて、その後は３０分間、二人とも黙って座っているだけだった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4215
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_a36a2027:

    # n "She said 'goodbye' and didn't look me in the eye when she closed the door."
    n "そして、俺には目もくれずに『さよなら』と言って出て行った。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4217
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_0051aa8c:

    # n "It might've been a natural end to the series of visits that were probably pretty painful for both of us."
    n "彼女の一連のお見舞いは多分俺たち両方にとって苦痛だったと思う。その終わり方としては自然なものだったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4219
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_1bb53473:

    # n "Every time she visited me in the hospital I wanted to talk to her, but something stopped me every time. Every time that I didn't speak made the next time even harder."
    n "病院の俺を訪ねてくるたび、俺は話をしたかったけど、いつもなにかが歯止めをかけていた。毎回なにも話さずにいると、次のときには余計に話すのが難しくなった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4221
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_65d39431:

    # n "Iwanako always had this aura of fragility around her, as if she'd shatter into pieces at the slightest disturbance. Initially I think it might've been that delicacy that attracted me to her, but after what happened back then, it felt as if she really had shattered."
    n "岩魚子はいつもわずかな動揺で崩れ落ちてしまいそうな、繊細な雰囲気をかもしていた。最初は、俺はそんな繊細さに魅了されているんだと思っていた。でもあの出来事のあと、岩魚子は本当に粉々になってしまったかのようだった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4223
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_79f3a644:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=150}She looked so sad that I didn't want to say anything that might upset her, and I never could figure out the right words to say."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n\n岩魚子はあまりに悲しそうにしていたので、彼女を動揺させるようなことは一切口にしたくなかった。何を言えば良かったのか、俺にはまったく見当がつかなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4227
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_7f8abf22:

    # n "I told her that it wasn't her fault, she nodded and I really think she understood that if it hadn't been that, then sooner or later something else would've made my heart give out."
    n "岩魚子は悪くないんだと俺は言って、彼女もうなずいた。あの時のことがなくたって、遅かれ早かれ別の何かのせいで俺の心臓はやられてしまっていただろう、そう理解してくれたと本気で思っていた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4229
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_ade77ce8:

    # n "Yet she looked so hopelessly sad every time she opened that door and entered my room."
    n "それでも岩魚子は病室のドアを開けて入ってくるたび、どうしようもないほど悲しそうだった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4231
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_c8fc7c4a:

    # n "So I never managed to say the things I wanted to say. In the end, that might've hurt her even more."
    n "だから俺は、言いたいと思っていたことを一つも言うことができなかった。結局、それがなおさら岩魚子を傷つけていたのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4236
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4241
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_ad45b62a:

    # "Carefully, I open the envelope and draw out the folded letter from within."
    "慎重に封筒を開けて、中から折りたたまれた手紙を取り出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4264
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_bd3e586f:

    # "After finishing reading the letter I fold it like it was, and place it on my desk."
    "手紙を読み終えると、元通りに折りたたみ、机の上に置く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4266
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_1b84d0c2:

    # "I don't know what to think of this. I feel empty and confused."
    "なにを思えばいいのかわからない。俺はむなしい気分になり、そして困惑する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4270
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4273
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_f6d02331:

    # n "{vspace=60}Why now, after all this time?"
    n "\n\nどうして今になって？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4275
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_2bb63ffe:

    # n "Just yesterday I decided that I can't let myself stay like this, that I'd try to get on top of my own life. Reading this letter just reminds me of what could have been."
    n "つい昨日、俺はこのままじゃいけない、自分の人生に打ち勝つために努力するんだって決心したばかりだ。この手紙を読んで、俺はあり得たかもしれない自分のことを気づかされた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4277
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_06d51b1e:

    # n "Of course I wish that I didn't have to be here. I'd want to be in the same class with Iwanako again. Maybe we would talk every day now and go on dates."
    n "こんなところに来たりするはめになんてなりたくなかった。当たり前じゃないか。また岩魚子と同じクラスになりたかった。きっと俺たちは毎日おしゃべりして、デートもしてただろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4279
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_61cb1164:

    # n "{vspace=30}My life didn't go like that."
    n "\n俺の人生はそうはならなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4281
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_912464d3:

    # n "I didn't really need to be reminded of this. Iwanako needed to write this letter for her own sake and I'm glad for her that she could, but it would've been better if I hadn't read it."
    n "こんなことを思い知らされる必要なんてなかった。岩魚子は自分自身のために手紙を書き、俺もそうしてくれたことはうれしく思う。でも俺はこの手紙を読むべきじゃなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4283
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_0eb29a35:

    # n "{vspace=30}Of course, she is right. I thought of the same thing yesterday. I had fallen into a pit of depression and now have to try to climb out."
    n "\nもちろん、岩魚子は正しい。俺も同じことを昨日考えた。俺は絶望の穴のなかに落ちて、そこから這い出さなきゃいけなくなっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4288
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4293
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_b0768104:

    # "I rip out a page from my notebook, and after a moment of thinking how to frame my words, write a short reply to Iwanako."
    "俺はノートのページを破ると、どう文章を組み立てようかしばらく考えてから、岩魚子への短い返事を書く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4295
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_6411365c:

    # "I find it difficult to be really honest to her, but at least I try to appear somewhat convincing. I don't write her about Yamaku at all."
    "岩魚子に対して本心から素直になるのは難しいことに気づくけど、それでもどうにか説得力のあるように仕上げる。山久学園のことはなにも書かない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4297
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_08d8589d:

    # "I doubt she will write me again, but I don't feel at all sad about it. I fold my own letter to her and as I have no envelope, set it next to Iwanako's. I'll mail it to her later."
    "岩魚子がまた返事をくれるとは思えないけど、悲しみはまるで感じない。書いた手紙を折りたたむけど手持ちの封筒がないので、岩魚子の手紙に並べて置く。あとで送ろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4299
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_5697b0dd:

    # "Then I lie back on my bed, looking at the monotone gray ceiling."
    "単調な灰色の天井を見上げながら、ベッドに横になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4301
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_24367a3a:

    # "A bird sings outside of my window and a sudden gust of wind flutters my curtains. The summer afternoon feels still, as if time had stopped for a brief moment."
    "小鳥が窓の外で鳴いている。急な突風がカーテンをはためかせる。夏の午後は平穏で、一瞬時間が止まったかのように感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4303
translate jp a2_rin_iwanakos_regret_52d337ba:

    # "I think about all the things I've lost and will never regain."
    "俺は自分が失ってしまった、そしてもう二度と取り戻せない、あらゆるものごとに思いを巡らせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4323
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4326
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_227ca630:

    # n "Thus the languid days of mid-June pass by."
    n "かくして、６月中旬の気だるい日々は過ぎていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4328
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_b26d5d13:

    # n "I mail my letter to Iwanako, and receive no reply."
    n "岩魚子に手紙は送ったけど、それから返事はない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4330
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_316e9300:

    # n "Having decided to ditch the old me, I start observing my fellow students even closer than I did before, hoping to understand how other people cope with their own issues."
    n "過去の自分と決別することを決めた俺は、ほかの人たちが自分の問題とどうやって折り合いをつけているのかを知りたいと思って、以前よりもさらに念入りに仲間連中を観察しはじめる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4332
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7a0e76ff:

    # n "I start seeing things I didn't before, and it makes me wonder if I've been wrong twice."
    n "すると今までは見えなかったものが見えてきて、俺は二度までも間違えたのかと驚きを覚える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4334
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_e1c9f223:

    # n "Superficially, everyone is abnormal yet so strikingly normal that it shocked me at first. I admired the way my new school mates turned my prejudices around just like that, simply by being themselves."
    n "最初に衝撃を受けたのは、みんな普通じゃないのに、実は驚くほど普通と言うことだ。新しい学校の仲間たちがありのままに振る舞うだけで、自分の先入観があっさりひっくり返されてしまったことに感嘆していた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4336
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_8975466e:

    # n "Now that I've gotten used to it, I begin noticing other kinds of tones in the people surrounding me every day."
    n "それに慣れると、日々自分を取り巻く人々の、別の傾向が見え始める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4338
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_3747762e:

    # n "{vspace=30}There is this soft, numb sadness all around me."
    n "俺の周りの至る所に、ぼんやりとした、痺れるような悲しみがある。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4340
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_db40dd2c:

    # n "I can see the effort everyone has to make just to get through the day, and how it weighs on their shoulders, like it weighs on mine."
    n "俺にはみんなが１日をただただ乗り切ろうと努力しているのが、そしてそれが彼らの両肩に重く圧しかかっているのがわかる。俺の肩にも圧しかかっているのと同じように。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4342
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_63f098e4:

    # n "Even the brightest smile is just slightly subdued, every outburst of annoyance just slightly dampened. It's subtle, but it's definitely there."
    n "とびきりの明るい笑顔でさえどことなく控えめで、いら立ちが爆発する時もわずかに抑え気味になる。わかりにくいけど、でも間違いなくそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4344
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_4e9413b0:

    # nvl clear
    # n "I try to think what it means, what I can learn from others. I wonder if deep down, everyone is as lost as I am. Is there even one person in here who has truly found peace? I start to feel doubtful about myself once again."
    nvl clear
    n "これがどういうことか、そこから俺はなにを学べるのか考えてみる。心の底では、みんな俺のように自分を見失っているんじゃないか。ここには本当に安息を見いだしている人は一人でもいるんだろうか？　俺はまた自分自身を疑い始めてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4348
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c6e8d3ec:

    # n "I can't decide whether these people are happy, unhappy, or if they've just learned to cope and now live in an unfeeling limbo like I did all spring."
    n "みんなが幸せなのかそうでないのか、あるいはただ折り合いの付け方を学んで、俺が春のあいだずっとそうだったように、感覚を失った忘却の中で生きているだけなのか、俺には判断がつかない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4350
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_848255c3:

    # n "I escape from these feelings into the towering piles of books I carry to my room from Yuuko's sanctuary. After realizing that this will just shut me down even more, I start going to the art club's room more often, usually whenever I can."
    n "俺はそんな感覚から離れて、優子さんの聖地から部屋へと持ち帰った本の山へと逃げ込む。そんなことをしたら余計に行き詰まるだけだと気づいてからは、俺はできる限り美術部に顔を出すようにする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4352
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_69391b28:

    # n "{vspace=30}Rin too seems to spend more time in there than in her own classroom."
    n "琳は自分の教室よりも、ここで時間を過ごすことのほうが多いみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4354
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_87587db8:

    # n "I've often seen her totter towards the door at the very end of our corridor. That wooden door and the room behind it, smelling of paint and paper, seem to mean more to her than the rest of the world combined."
    n "廊下のいちばん端のドアに向かってよたよたと歩いていくのを何度も見かけている。あの木製のドアと、その向こうにある絵の具と紙の匂いがする部屋は、琳にとってそれ以外の世界をすべて合わせたものよりも大事な場所みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4356
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_0c2b44ff:

    # n "She says she has special permission to use the room, which I don't doubt at all. I don't think Nomiya would deny Rin anything."
    n "琳は好きに美術室を使える特別許可をもらっているという。その通りなのだろう。野宮先生なら琳のどんな頼みだって断らないと思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4358
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_b8fb91e5:

    # n "He seems to dote on her like an uncle upon a favorite niece."
    n "お気に入りの姪に接するおじのように、先生は琳を溺愛してるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4360
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_dd653e4b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=90}The object of his affection, however, has no favorites. She says she appreciates the teacher a lot for going the extra mile for her sake, but even when she says that, her expression is the same as always."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\nでも先生が好意を向ける相手は、なんの好意も持っていない。先生が自分のためにいつも労力を惜しまないことを感謝しているとは言うけど、そう話すときでさえ、琳の表情はいつもと変わらない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4364
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_cd545299:

    # n "It's as if she was talking about a particularly unremarkable rock that she saw the other day. I can't really figure out their relationship."
    n "以前見かけた何の変哲もない岩について話をするような口ぶりでだ。俺には二人の関係がさっぱりわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4366
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_1d544f0b:

    # n "Rin doesn't seem to let anyone close. I don't think even Emi could say she's crossed the gap that seems to separate Rin from the rest of the world."
    n "琳は他の人を近づけさせることはしないみたいだ。笑美でさえ、琳とその周りの世界を隔てる溝を乗り越えられているとは言えないと思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4368
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_9b05e8d2:

    # n "{vspace=60}I don't understand it. She seems so indifferent, yet so passionate at the same time."
    n "\n\nわからない。琳はあんなに無感動に見えるのに、同時に情熱的でもある。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4372
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_da468326:

    # n "Somewhere, the school bells ring the last call of the day."
    n "どこかで、この日の最後のチャイムが鳴る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4377
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4382
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_e28d4011:

    # "I realize I've been zoning out for who knows how long. Dazed, I sit up straighter, trying to look as inconspicuous as possible."
    "時間の経過がわからなくなるくらい、意識が飛んでいたことに気づく。もうろうとしながら、俺はできるだけ注意を引かないように姿勢を正す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4384
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c16629e4:

    # "The pungent smells of linseed oil and turpentine mix in my nostrils as I draw a deep breath. I feel drowsy and lightheaded."
    "深呼吸をすると、亜麻仁油とテレピン油の刺すような臭いが鼻の中で混じり合う。気だるくなって、頭がくらくらする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4386
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_da418f20:

    # "It's already this late and a few club members left early, so it's just me, Rin, the teacher, and two other girls who are also about to leave."
    "もうすでに遅い時間で、しかも部員の何人かは早々に帰ってしまった。美術室にいるのは俺と琳、先生、それからいままさに帰ろうとしている女子が二人。それだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4393
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_8bdc5dfa:

    # "Rin is sitting to my right, slowly working on a painting while I'm idling the time away. I don't think she realizes I've been watching her this whole time."
    "琳は俺の右隣に座っていて、俺が時間をつぶしているあいだ、ゆっくりと絵を描き進めている。俺がずっとその様子を観察していたことには気づいてなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4400
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_ea856418:

    # "With a nimble move of her delicate ankle, she dips the brush into crimson paint and presses it lightly onto the canvas. A stain spreads around, as if the brush was bleeding."
    "その細い足首の機敏な動きで、筆を深紅の絵の具に浸し、キャンバスに軽く押しつける。その周りに、筆が血を流しているかのようなしぶきが飛ぶ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4402
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_09cae2ce:

    # "Her progress has slowed down to a crawl. By now I've learned that this is dangerous for her technique, as the paint must not be allowed to dry before she's finished."
    "琳の作業ペースがさらに遅くなる。これが琳のやり方にとって危険だというのはこの頃わかるようになった。描き終える前に絵の具が乾いてはいけないからだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4404
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_1dbd175a:

    # "It occurs to me that I am literally watching paint dry. And yet somehow I'm not feeling bored, despite spacing out just now."
    "俺は自分が文字通り、絵の具が乾くのを眺めていることを自覚する。それなのに、どういうわけか俺はただただぼうっとしているにもかかわらず、退屈を感じずにいる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4411
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4414
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_17f9fe6f:

    # n "{vspace=60}Most of the time, the art club is very relaxed and free-form. Apart from times when Nomiya gets really excited about some technique or style he wants to teach us about, everyone is free to pursue their own interests."
    n "\n\n美術部の部活のほとんどの時間は、とてものんびりしていて、自由気ままだ。野宮先生がなにかの技術やスタイルを俺たちに教えようとして本当に興奮しているときは別にして、みんな自分の興味のあることに自由に取り組んで構わない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4416
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_20d87659:

    # n "Lacking one, I keep floating around without a direction. I try this and that, but nothing really leaves me with a deeper impression, not to mention that I don't seem to have a special knack for anything."
    n "興味のあることなんて一つもない俺は、あてもなくその辺を漂っている。あれやこれやと試してみるけど、どれも俺に深い印象を与えない。俺にはなんの特別な才能もないってことはいうまでもない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4418
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_2552927d:

    # n "Well, I did get praised for my attempt at watercolors, and I felt pretty good about that, myself, but that's it."
    n "まあ、水彩画に挑戦したときは褒められたわけだし、自分でもいい気分だった。でもそれだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4420
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d1d44b53:

    # n "I suppose it's to be expected. I joined the art club mostly on a whim, after all."
    n "まあ当然だろうな。俺が美術部に入ったのは結局気まぐれなのだから。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4422
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_deb32a7c:

    # n "I'm thinking that maybe I should quit the club, if it's going to be this pointless. But there's nothing really wrong with pointlessness and I can't exactly say I'm unhappy."
    n "こんなに無意味になってしまうなら、部活なんてやめるべきかもしれないと考えている。でも無意味であることは別に悪いことじゃないし、それが不幸だとも言い切れない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4424
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_420b6a97:

    # n "{vspace=30}Unsatisfied maybe, but I've got only myself to blame for that."
    n "\n不満ではあるのかもしれないけど、でもそれは他でもない俺自身のせいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4429
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4434
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_35fd7417:

    # "As the pair of girls exit the club room with a cheerful 'bye-bye', Nomiya stands up from his desk. His chair scoots back with a loud screech that breaks the harmony of this quiet afternoon."
    "女の子２人が元気よく『バイバイ』といって部室を出て行くと、野宮先生は机から立ち上がる。いすが静かな午後の調和を壊すような甲高い、うるさい音を立てて後ずさる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4436
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_09aed754:

    # "He taps a pile of papers in his hands twice against the tabletop in order to straighten them, then stretches his back."
    "先生は手に持った紙の束を机の上で２回軽く叩いて整えると、背筋を伸ばす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4441
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_16caabf9:

    # no "I have a faculty meeting to attend, so I can't stay. I'll have to do some paperwork later, so if you want to stay we can talk then. Sorry about this."
    no "職員会議があるものでな、もう行かなくてはならん。その後で書類仕事もあるから、もしここにいたかったら、そのときに話をしよう。すまないな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4443
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_1b907472:

    # "There are two people here, but he's really talking to only one of us. Nomiya spends extra hours of his time mentoring Rin after official club hours are over, and I'll bet he'd like to discuss his plan of getting Rin's art into a gallery a little more."
    "ここには二人いるけど、実際先生は一人にしか話しかけていない。先生は正式な部活の時間のあとも琳の指導に時間を割いている。きっと画廊に展示する琳の絵をもっと増やす計画について話し合いたいんだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4448
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_12a3e31b:

    # rin "It's all right. I think I'll probably be here, but it's not a big deal if I'm not. I don't really have much going now."
    rin "大丈夫です。たぶんここにいると思います。いなくてもたいして問題ないですけど。今はあんまり進んでないし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4450
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_19d8f3d4:

    # "Rin answers without moving her eyes from her work in progress. The tone of her voice is neither the polite kind expected when talking to a teacher, nor her usual monotone."
    "琳は目の前の絵から視線を動かさずに答える。その声のトーンは、先生と話をするときのような丁寧な感じでも、いつもの琳のような単調な感じでもない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4452
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_09117975:

    # no "So I won't need to send a search party if you aren't here?"
    no "ではお前がここにいなくても、捜索部隊をよこす必要はないんだな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4454
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_8fe359b1:

    # rin "Yes, no thanks, I don't like to party. We can talk later."
    rin "はい、大丈夫です。部隊行動は好きじゃないです。話は今度にしましょう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4460
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_f323091d:

    # no "Good girl."
    no "よしよし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4467
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7ff6360e:

    # "Smiling, the teacher picks up the rest of his papers and makes his way to the door. I glance at the clock above it and then at my watch to double check."
    "笑顔を見せ、先生は残りの書類を手にとってドアに向かう。俺はドアの上にある時計を見て、念のために腕時計も確認する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4469
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_2c7ef247:

    # "They're three minutes apart, but nevertheless the club's meeting time is over now."
    "３分ずれてる。それでも部活の時間はもう終わりだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4471
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_25bf711b:

    # "Rin seems intent on staying here to work on her piece while waiting for the teacher."
    "琳はここに残って作業を続けながら、先生が戻るのを待つつもりみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4473
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_96279b02:

    # "I can't quite imagine what their one-on-one time would be like."
    "俺には二人が１対１でいるときの様子がまったく想像できない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4475
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_bf6fe87c:

    # "Would they actually discuss anything? Rin is always so subdued in what she says, and when she does say something it's difficult to understand what she's talking about."
    "本当に何かを議論したりしているんだろうか？　琳の話し方はいつも抑え気味で、何か言うことがあったとしても、何の話をしているのか理解するのは難しい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4477
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_521e2056:

    # "Maybe Nomiya just talks endlessly like he does at club meetings, letting Rin absorb what she will from his infinite well of art knowledge, like a sunflower turning to face the glowing sun."
    "もしかして、先生は部活の時みたいにただ延々としゃべって、その無限に湧く芸術に関する知識の泉から、琳が望むものを吸収させようとしてるんだろうか。ひまわりが煌々と輝く太陽のほうを向くように。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4482
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_f11bba04:

    # hi "Do you mind if I stay? I er… thought maybe I'd give watercolors another try."
    hi "俺もここにいていいか？　俺、えっと……また水彩画やってみようと思ってさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4484
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_2cf7d506:

    # "I blurt out the excuse sort of accidentally, embarrassing myself. Rin doesn't take her eyes off her painting."
    "うっかり言い訳めいたことを口走ってしまい、恥ずかしくなる。琳は絵から目をそらさない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4486
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_a61bcc4a:

    # rin "Okay."
    rin "いいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4491
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d6c6a4a3:

    # "I shift around in my chair, then get to fetching a cup of water, brushes, colors and some paper. The sound of my footsteps invades the still afternoon air."
    "俺は椅子から立ち上がって、コップ１杯の水、絵筆、絵の具と紙を何枚か取りに行く。俺の足音が静かな午後の空気を破る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4493
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_0b3fecb7:

    # "Before starting, I try to recall what the teacher told us, an important philosophy of the medium: working with watercolors means more working with water than working with color. I try to keep that in mind, and dip my tiny sable brush into the water cup."
    "始める前に、先生が言ったこと、水彩という表現手法の重要な哲学を思い出そうとする。水彩画を描くことは絵の具よりも水で描くことなんだと。それを胸に刻み込んで、セーブルの絵筆を水に浸す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4495
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_b6d15185:

    # "I'm mixing yellow and blue, trying to capture the sunlit treetops outside of the window. The sun is low, so the yellows are more pronounced and everything looks darker."
    "太陽に照らされた窓の外の梢をとらえるために、黄色と青を混ぜる。太陽はもう低くなっていて、黄色がもっと目立ち、すべてのものが色濃く見える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4497
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_32148698:

    # "I still can't quite connect what I see with what my hand does with the paints, but it's a passable attempt for my level."
    "俺はいまだに自分が見ているものと、この手で描こうとしているものとを結びつけることができないでいるけど、俺のレベルとしてはまずまずだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4499
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_ad9b260c:

    # "After a while I start losing my focus and move the paper aside, deciding to watch Rin work for a while, instead."
    "少し時間が経つと俺は集中力が切れてしまい、代わりに紙を横にずらして、しばらく琳の作業を観察することにする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4501
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_b50cfe7d:

    # "That little while stretches first into a long while, then into a really long while."
    "その少しの時間が、まずは長い時間に、さらには本当に長い間に伸びていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4508
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_bfba4ad8:

    # "Rin paints, her entire being fully concentrated on the brush between her slender toes and the painting coming to life one stroke at a time."
    "琳は描く。その全身全霊が細いつま先に挟まれた筆に集中し、一筆ごとにその絵に命が吹き込まれていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4510
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_4e4d77f0:

    # "She seems determined and yet at the same time relaxed, effortlessly moving the brush around, never hesitating. Colors meet and part, mix and cover each other on the canvas, bending to her quiet will."
    "琳は真剣そうだけど、同時にリラックスしているようにも見える。悠々と筆を動かしていて、ためらいが全くない。琳の静かな意志に従って、色同士がキャンバスの上で出会っては別れ、互いに混ざり、重なっていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4512
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_fad37be1:

    # "I don't know anything about composition, structure or any of that stuff, but I really like Rin's paintings. I like how she looks when she paints."
    "構図とか構成とか、そういったことは何もわからないけど、俺は本当に琳の絵が好きだ。絵を描いているときの琳の姿が好きだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4514
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_2b1738e6:

    # "As usual, the silence between us compels me to speak rather than merely wait for her to open up. She might end up saying nothing at all."
    "いつものことだけど、二人の間の沈黙のおかげで、ただ琳が口を開くのを待っていないで、こっちから話さなきゃという気になってくる。最後まで琳は何も言わないかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4518
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_41914933:

    # hi "Do you mind if we talk?"
    hi "ちょっと話してもいいか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4523
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7d238992:

    # rin "I don't mind."
    rin "いいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4525
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_da6d5488:

    # hi "I kinda wanted to ask more about why you get so weird about this thing the teacher wants to arrange for you."
    hi "先生がなにか段取りをつけてくれてるけど、そのことでお前がすごく変な風になるのはどうしてなのか、もう少し聞きたくてさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4527
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_a7910d63:

    # "Rin picks up a tube of paint and squeezes it between her toes on a palette almost as easily as someone with opposable thumbs would. Taking up a brush again, she replies."
    "琳は絵の具のチューブを拾い上げると、親指が向かい合うようについているのとほぼ同じような容易さで、足の指を使ってパレットの上に絞り出す。ふたたび筆に持ちかえると、琳は答える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4532
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_6c2a270a:

    # rin "A lot of things. And some not-things. Unthings. I don't think that's a word."
    rin "いろいろあるんだよ。それとないことも。なしごと。そんな言葉ないか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4534
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_93ed1bf2:

    # hi "Do you want to talk about it?"
    hi "話してくれるか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4536
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_43996054:

    # "I try to reach out to her clumsily, ignoring the embarrassing feeling of awkwardness. Rin keeps her focus on the painting, spreading more and more paint on the canvas, her lips forming a perfectly straight line as she concentrates on the job."
    "気まずさで恥ずかしくなるのを無視して、俺はぎこちなく琳の本音に近づこうとする。琳は絵に集中し続け、絵の具をどんどんキャンバスに塗っていく。集中が深まるにつれて、くちびるがまっすぐな線を形作る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4541
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_4d44250e:

    # rin "Not really."
    rin "やめとく"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4546
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_404bb560:

    # rin "Talking is hard. I mean, it's not hard, I'm talking even now. But saying the right things is really hard for me."
    rin "話すのって難しいんだよ。じゃなくて、難しくはないよ、今だって話してるし。でも思った通りのことを話すのは私にはすごく難しいんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4551
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_25ddfbed:

    # rin "No matter what, I just can't say the things I want."
    rin "なにがあっても、自分が本当に言いたいことは言えないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4553
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d624635c:

    # hi "That sounds weird."
    hi "それは変じゃないか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4558
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d17fccd9:

    # rin "It's true. I say all kinds of things that I don't really mean all the time. And sometimes I forget words and then I use the wrong words. I even come up with new words for things that already have some. That's the worst thing."
    rin "本当だよ。私はいつだって、実際には思ってもいないことばっかり言ってる。時には言葉を忘れて、間違った言葉を使っちゃう しかも、ふさわしい言葉があるのに新しい言葉を思いつきで使っちゃうことまである。それって最悪だよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4560
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_13c2ae7c:

    # rin "I get really nervous and everything comes out a mess and even I don't really understand what I want to say."
    rin "緊張しちゃって、口にする言葉が全部めちゃくちゃになって、自分でも何が言いたいのかよく分からなくなるんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4565
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_05d21a57:

    # rin "I think there's something wrong with me that makes it like this. Remember when I said I can only think of four things at the same time?"
    rin "私にどこかおかしなところがあって、そういう風になっちゃうんだと思う。一度に４つのことしか考えられないって話したときのこと、覚えてる？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4567
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_69498fb0:

    # "I nod wordlessly."
    "俺は黙ったままうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4572
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_13352f38:

    # rin "It's not really four. I mean, it is four, but everything else is also there kind of in the background. Like being at an amusement park and a beehive at the same time. But that's not the point."
    rin "本当は４つじゃないんだ。じゃなくて、４つなんだけど、ほかのことも全部、なんとなく意識の後ろの方にはあるんだよ。遊園地と蜂の巣に同時にいるようなもの。そこは本質じゃないんだけどさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4574
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_e9c685c1:

    # rin "I used to do better. Like six or seven things. I think so, at least. I feel like I'm becoming dumber."
    rin "前はもっとましだったんだよね。６つ７つはいけたよ。少なくとも、自分ではそう思ってる。なんだか前よりバカになっちゃったみたいだな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4576
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_e0c46d77:

    # hi "I think everyone has times when they feel like they can't say the right things."
    hi "誰だって、思った通りのことを言えないって気持ちになることはあると思うぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4581
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_eeda2f0e:

    # rin "But it's there all the time. Stronger and deeper. Yeah, deeper is a good word. I like that word. Deeper."
    rin "でも私はいつもそうなんだよ。もっと強くて深いんだ。うん、深いってのはいい言葉だよね。好きな言葉だよ。深いって"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4583
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_8cc7511c:

    # rin "It's that feeling of being underwater. Maybe it's just art."
    rin "水のなかにいるときの、あの感覚だよ。ただの芸術かもしれないけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4588
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_14383edf:

    # rin "The more I paint, the more words I forget. Maybe at some point I will forget how to speak completely."
    rin "絵を描けば描くほど、どんどん言葉を忘れちゃう。そのうちに話し方を完全に忘れちゃうかもね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4590
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_30b8ec5b:

    # rin "It feels like I'm slowly forgetting everything. Do you remember what you thought about things three or four years ago?"
    rin "いろんなことをだんだん忘れていってるような気がするんだ。３、４年前にどんなことを思ってたか、君は覚えてる？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4592
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_ae6f824c:

    # rin "I don't."
    rin "私は覚えてない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4594
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_64165fa6:

    # "A long pause ensues, during which time seems to bend around itself, almost tying itself into a knot. I don't think I've ever heard Rin talk this earnestly and for so long about anything before."
    "時間がひとりでに曲がりくねって、結び目を作るかのような長い沈黙が後に続く。琳が何かについて、こんなに長いこと真剣に話をするのを聞くのは初めてだと思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4599
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_3fe0ddeb:

    # rin "It's like I'm fading away from the world."
    rin "自分がこの世界から消えていっちゃうような感じがする"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4606
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_38f07e4d:

    # "Rin's foot has stopped its work on the canvas and she is staring at her painting, unmoving, as if gazing at some faraway horizon."
    "キャンバス上で作業をする足を止め、琳はその絵を身動きせずに、遠くの地平線を見つめるかのようにじっと凝視している。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4608
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_70f963ec:

    # "Sunlight briefly glints in the corner of her onyx eyes. Something floats up into the top layer of Rin's being and she lets out a long breath."
    "日差しが一瞬、琳の真っ黒な目の隅にきらめく。なにかが琳の存在の表面に浮かびあがり、琳は深い息を吐く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4622
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_eef28cb2:

    # "Then she blinks and it's gone."
    "琳がまばたきをすると、それは消え失せてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4627
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7382481b:

    # rin "Paintings stay behind. When I look at my old things, I remember what I was thinking back when I made them."
    rin "絵はあとに残るから。昔の絵を見るとさ、それを描いたときに考えていたことが思い浮かぶんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4632
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7f72158e:

    # rin "They make me feel like I can be with all the past mes when I was a different me."
    rin "今とは違う、過去の全部の私と一緒にいられるような気分になるんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4637
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_035a3dde:

    # rin "I guess they are the proof of my existence."
    rin "昔の絵は私の存在の証明なんだろうなって思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4639
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_bcdb01a2:

    # "She uses the exact same words Nomiya used when he spoke to us of the nature of art. I didn't think Rin was paying any attention, back then. I wonder if she was listening, or whether she had heard the same passionate speech from Nomiya before."
    "琳は野宮先生が俺たちに芸術の本質を語ったときと全く同じ言葉を使う。あのとき琳がちゃんと聞いていたとは思わなかった。 本当にあの場で話を聞いていたのか、それとも先生の同じような情熱的な演説を前にも聞いていたんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4641
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_15728ad9:

    # "Either way, I feel overwhelmed."
    "どっちにしろ、圧倒された気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4643
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_97a50540:

    # hi "Boy, are you complicated. I would've taken up writing a diary."
    hi "まったく、ややこしいやつだなあ。俺だったら日記を書いてるぜ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4651
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_9334f29b:

    # "Her eyes quickly flicker to my direction and then back to the painting, but she doesn't pick up the brush any more."
    "琳の目が俺のほうに向かって揺れ動いて、また絵のほうに戻る。でも、琳はもう筆を取り上げない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4655
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_97fda8c8:

    # rin "That's a great idea. Why didn't I ever think of that?"
    rin "それ、すごくいいアイディアだね。なんで今まで思いつかなかったんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4657
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_eaf90844:

    # hi "Are you being sarcastic?"
    hi "嫌味かよ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4662
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_f73aa286:

    # rin "What's sarcasm?"
    rin "なにが嫌味なの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4664
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_6c70247a:

    # "I don't call her on the joke, if it is one."
    "琳の冗談をとがめるのはやめておく。もし冗談ならだけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4669
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_8919b7e0:

    # "Right at that moment, Nomiya returns from his meeting. He waves to us a very melodramatic hello, mildly surprised to see me here along with his pet student. Walking with a boisterous gait to his desk, he drops his papers upon it."
    "ちょうどそのとき、先生が会議から戻ってくる。先生はやけに芝居がかった会釈を俺たちに向けると、俺が愛弟子と一緒にいるのを見て少し驚く。荒々しく自分の机まで歩いていくと、先生はその上に書類を落とす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4671
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_4cfad8df:

    # "He picks up a handkerchief and cleans his glasses with incredibly meticulous care before walking over to us."
    "ハンカチを取り出して、信じられないほど几帳面にめがねをふいてから、俺たちのほうにやってくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4673
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_9d6c8d19:

    # "Before he is within earshot of us, Rin says something to me in a quick, quiet voice."
    "先生が俺たちと話ができる距離まで近づく前に、琳が素早く、静かな声で俺に言う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4680
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_ed717c5d:

    # rin "Change is the scariest thing in the world to me."
    rin "私にとって、変わるっていうのはこの世でいちばん怖いことなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4685
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_af10d756:

    # rin "And I seriously don't know if I want to change into a person who could do the thing the teacher wants me to do. I don't know if I could even if I wanted to."
    rin "私が、先生が私にやってほしいと期待してることができるような人間になりたいのかどうか、真剣にわからないんだ。もしなりたかったとしても、できるかどうかさえわからないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4690
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_328fc196:

    # no "Hello again!"
    no "やあやあ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4699
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c3eddc3c:

    # no "What's going on?"
    no "なにをしているんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4701
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_a41505a7:

    # "He smiles a bit sheepishly, looking at both of us with uninhibited interest."
    "先生は少しばつが悪そうに微笑むと、俺たち二人を遠慮のない興味をもって見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4703
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_ca51afbf:

    # hi "Ah, nothing. We were just talking about that thing with your acquaintance and the gallery. For Rin's works. Sort of."
    hi "ええと、特になにも。先生のお知り合いの画廊のことで話してただけです。琳の絵を置こうっていう。そんな感じです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4708
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_974dce79:

    # no "Oho? Any decisions?"
    no "ほほう？　なにか決まったのかね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4710
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_74953757:

    # "I look at Rin, who is trying to arrange the bothered expression on her face into something else."
    "俺は思い悩んだような表情をどうにか変えようとしている琳を見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4714
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_e2bf940d:

    # hi "Anyway, I don't think I have much else to say, other than that you should go for it." nointeract
    hi "なんにしても、俺からはやってみればとしか言えないよ" nointeract

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4747
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_3e0b13e1:

    # "Rin looks absentmindedly at me, not saying anything. I can't even tell if my words had any effect on her."
    "琳は上の空で、何も言わずに俺を見る。俺の言葉が少しでも効いたのかどうか、それさえわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4749
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_32c3680b:

    # hi "I just don't get it. Anyone else would be jumping up and down in excitement."
    hi "全然わからねえよ。ほかの人だったら興奮して飛び跳ねてるぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4751
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d5492d08:

    # hi "What's the point of doing your best, being at this art club, if you don't do anything with your talent?"
    hi "自分の才能を使いもしないんだったら、この美術部でベストをつくす意味がどこにあるんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4753
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_671af57e:

    # hi "I'm telling you, I'm going to be angry with you if you give this up."
    hi "いいか、これでお前がやらないなんて言ったら怒るからな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4755
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_45889942:

    # "My voice rises higher. I don't know what makes me say this. It's like I've been taken over by some force out of my control, but I really do feel angry."
    "声が大きくなる。なぜこんなことを口走っているのかわからない。なんだか自分でも抵抗できない力に支配されてしまったかのようだ。でも俺は確かに怒りを感じている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4757
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c1c0bd9a:

    # "Images of a letter written on cute stationery flash in my mind, images of the masked faces of my parents, my doctors, images of the time I've wasted. They mix into my feelings about Rin like a torrent of molten iron."
    "可愛らしい便せんに書かれた手紙、マスクをした両親と医者の顔、俺が無駄にしてきた時間のイメージが脳裏に浮かぶ。それがみんな、勢いよく流れる溶けた鉄のように、俺が抱いている琳への感情と混ざり合う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4762
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_dc656221:

    # "I want to continue, but Rin suddenly stands up."
    "俺は続けたかったけど、琳がとつぜん立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4764
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_b8b5b263:

    # rin "Fine."
    rin "好きにすれば"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4766
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_82a1a2f3:

    # rin "I'm going."
    rin "帰る"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4771
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_135473cb:

    # "She trots out of the room without anyone saying anything. I stare after her, still seething, though with the voice of rationality in the back of my head wondering if I made her angry as well."
    "それ以上誰も何も言わず、琳は小走りで部屋を出ていく。怒りを抑えられないまま、俺はその背中を見つめる。でも理性の声が頭の奥で、俺は琳も怒らせてしまったのだろうかといぶかっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4777
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_6f108829:

    # "The teacher lets out an embarrassed, but extraordinarily loud laugh."
    "先生がうろたえたように、しかし異様なほど大きな声で笑う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4782
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c697fa89:

    # no "You care a lot for her, don't you?"
    no "ずいぶん手塚のことを心配してるようだな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4788
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_801bf249:

    # rin "I don't think I want to talk about this."
    rin "そのことは話したくない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4790
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_82a1a2f3_1:

    # rin "I'm going."
    rin "帰る"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4798
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_1e638891:

    # "Rin stands up and trots out of the room without anyone saying anything more."
    "琳は立ち上がると、小走りで部屋を出てしまう。みんなそれ以上は一言も口を開かない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4804
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7187c5d1:

    # hi "I'm sorry. I think I made her upset."
    hi "すみません。怒らせちゃったみたいで"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4809
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c62951c0:

    # no "Hahaha, don't worry about it. She'll be fine, I'm sure. I'll talk to her later."
    no "はっはっは、気にするな。あいつなら大丈夫だ、保証する。私から後で話しておこう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4814
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d0be9e3e:

    # no "Now now, my boy. It's a big decision and even though I'd like Tezuka to be more decisive as well, she needs time to mull it over."
    no "まあまあ。私も手塚にはもっと決心を固めてほしいが、それでも大きな決断だ。じっくり考える時間が必要だろう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4819
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_67af2069:

    # no "Why don't we let her decide. You have good intentions, but in the end it comes down to her own feelings."
    no "手塚に決めさせてやろうじゃないか。いい心もちだが、結局、手塚の気持ち次第だ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4824
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_e0490bd6:

    # no "Any thoughts on the subject, Tezuka? You've been quiet all afternoon."
    no "お前の考えはどうだ、手塚？　午後のあいだ、ずっと静かだったじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4826
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_74b16468:

    # "We both look at Rin, who doesn't return either of our gazes."
    "二人して琳を見るけど、琳は俺たちのどちらにも目を合わせない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4831
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_3511362d:

    # rin "No. I think I'm going."
    rin "いえ。もう帰ります"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4836
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_2aedbdc3:

    # no "You are? What a shame. Promise me you'll give me some kind of an answer in a week or so, all right?"
    no "本当か？　それは残念だ。では１週間くらいで答えを聞かせてくれると約束してくれ、いいな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4841
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_6b6cdbe8:

    # rin "All right."
    rin "わかりました"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4846
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_f323091d_1:

    # no "Good girl."
    no "よしよし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4854
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_4e595710:

    # "Rin stands up and trots out of the room without anyone saying anything further."
    "琳は立ち上がると、小走りで部屋を出てしまう。みんなそれ以上は一言も口を開かない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4860
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_63b67738:

    # "Nomiya looks at me over his circular pink glasses, smiling sympathetically."
    "野宮先生は丸いピンク色の眼鏡ごしに、同情するような笑顔で俺を見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4865
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_1e3c9571:

    # no "You've made friends with her then, Nakai?"
    no "手塚とは仲良くなったようだな、中井？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4867
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_92c150da:

    # hi "Uh… well, something like that, I guess. Depends on how you look at it. To be honest, I'm not really sure."
    hi "ううん……ええ、そんな感じです、たぶん。見方次第だと思いますけど。正直言って、あまり自信がないです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4869
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_302f295e:

    # "It's more like me and Rin just tend to hang around each other irregularly, talking or not about something that more often resembles some twisted mockery of philosophy rather than normal, everyday things that 'friends' chat about."
    "どっちかというと、俺と琳は気まぐれにつるんでいて、『友達』どうしがする日常的な普通の話じゃなく、へんてこな哲学のまねごとのような話をしたりしなかったりしているだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4874
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_1bf1566d:

    # no "Well, that's all good, isn't it? You're a new student and we should be promoting integration into the student body and such. I can't remember all the buzzwords they spew at faculty and Yamaku Foundation meetings, but that's how it is."
    no "なに、結構なことじゃないか。君は新顔で、君がほかの生徒たちに馴染めるよう後押しをしてやるのも我々の仕事だ 職員や山久財団の会議で聞くような流行り言葉はいちいち覚えていられないが、まあそういうことだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4879
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_4b1119ec:

    # no "Tezuka isn't the most social person around these parts, either."
    no "手塚にしても、この界隈でもっとも社交的な人間というわけではないからな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4881
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_b01b9b80:

    # hi "Yeah, that's definitely true."
    hi "ええ、それはそのとおりです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4886
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c5f11d49:

    # no "So she's talked about my suggestion to you?"
    no "それで、手塚は君に私の提案のことを話したのかね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4888
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_edd9333b:

    # hi "Oh, no, not really. I think it's been more me pressing her to decide something. Maybe I shouldn't have."
    hi "ああ、いえ、そういうわけじゃ。むしろ俺があいつに決めろってしつこく言ってた気がします。良くなかったのかもしれません"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4893
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d410c3a8:

    # no "No, I'm sure it's fine. I'm too soft with her, even when I shouldn't. I don't really know how to handle Tezuka, she's so independent and willful."
    no "いや、それは大丈夫だろう。私が手塚を必要以上に甘やかしすぎているんだ。手塚をどう扱えばいいのか、私にはよくわからん。とても自立心が強いし、頑固だからな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4898
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_417ffc82:

    # no "I wonder if this is what every old geezer of an art teacher who got his hands on a young and fiery prodigy felt like."
    no "若くて激情的な天才児を手に入れた老いぼれ美術教師の気持ちというのは、こういうものなのかね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4903
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_51dc75f6:

    # "He chuckles ironically to himself a little bit, turning to face Rin's latest work which she left drying on the easel. She departed so abruptly that I wonder if she considers it finally finished."
    "先生は皮肉っぽく含み笑いをすると、画架の上で乾かされている琳の描きかけの絵に顔を向ける。琳は唐突に飛び出してしまったけど、もう描き終わったと判断したんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4908
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_9214b9cf:

    # no "So, let's see the painting then."
    no "さて、これを見てみようか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4910
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7c46d6c3:

    # "He leans in closer, peering at the canvas."
    "先生は身を寄せると、キャンバスに目を凝らす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4915
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_914d53fa:

    # no "It draws you in, doesn't it?"
    no "引き込まれるじゃないか、そう思わないか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4920
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_e12a28a3:

    # "Nomiya stands back straight, his face a dreamy, nostalgic visage. I don't answer him, as he seems to be taking my agreement as a given."
    "野宮先生はまっすぐ後ろに下がる。その顔は夢を見ているような、なにかを懐かしむような表情だ。俺が同意していると決めてかかっているようなので、その問いには返事をしない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4925
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7931b7b8:

    # no "I sometimes stay here after hours just to look at Tezuka's paintings. She's really just prodigious, and at such a young age. I get shivers just thinking of what she could become with a few more years of refinement."
    no "手塚の絵を見るだけのために、時々放課後にここに来るんだ。あの若さなのに、すばらしい才能だ。あと数年も修練すればどれだけ成長できるか、考えるだけで震えてしまうよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4930
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_9f1e64c0:

    # no "You asked what makes an artist, remember? This is it. They take a piece of the world and reshape it in their own image. Metaphorically, of course."
    no "以前に芸術家を芸術家たらしめるものは何なのかと聞いただろう、覚えているかね？　これこそがそうだ。芸術家は世界の断片を手にし、自らのイメージでそれを作り直すんだ。もちろん比喩的にだがね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4935
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_727eee25:

    # no "Looking at her makes you wonder what the world looks like through her eyes. It's a wonderful thing, to be young and full of passion, the most extraordinary time of your life. You would do well to remember that, Nakai."
    no "手塚を見ると、彼女の目を通して見る世界がどんなものなのか知りたくなるんだ。若く情熱に満ちた、とてつもなく充実した時間を過ごせるというのは、それはすばらしいものだ。よく覚えておくといいぞ、中井"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4937
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_093214bf:

    # hi "Yes, sir."
    hi "はい"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4942
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_062b9f9f:

    # no "It's so silly."
    no "ばかげたものでなあ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4947
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_25ccbb21:

    # no "People always ask artists 'Where do you get your ideas?' as if ideas were something sold at the market for pocket change."
    no "誰もが芸術家に『どこからアイディアを得るのか？』と聞くんだ、アイディアというのはスーパーで売っていて、ポケットの小銭で買えるものだと言わんばかりに"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4952
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_a1344707:

    # no "You can't explain inspiration. For people like Tezuka, it's like breathing. It's an instinct."
    no "インスピレーションは説明できるものではない。手塚のような人間にとっては息をするようなものだ。本能なのだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4954
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_fec23f85:

    # no "I've met maybe one or two with the same kind of raw potential. But no amount of potential will amount to anything if one doesn't work to realize it."
    no "これまでも一人か二人、同じくらいの才能を秘めたものに会った。だが本人が努力をしてそれを自覚しなければ、どんな潜在能力も全く意味がないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4956
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_a6f93213:

    # no "It's practice, technique, skill. Draw for an hour every day for a few years and even the most hopeless case becomes a passable artist."
    no "練習、技巧、そして技能だ。２、３年の間、毎日一時間絵を描き続ければ、どんなに才能のないものでもそれなりの芸術家にはなれる"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4961
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7935faf9:

    # no "Tezuka is not brilliant because she was born with a natural talent for this kind of thing. She's brilliant because she works harder than anyone, ever since she learned to hold a pen, most likely."
    no "手塚が優れているのは、こうしたことへの才能を持って生まれたからではない。ペンを持つことを覚えて以来、誰よりも熱心に努力しているからだ。恐らくはな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4966
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_f844fc3c:

    # no "And all of it with her feet, no less. Absolutely phenomenal."
    no "そして何よりすべてを足でこなす。まさに驚くべきことだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4968
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7e41b15b:

    # "Silence finally lands in the clubroom as Nomiya lets himself get drawn back into Rin's painting, gently murmuring acceptance toward the still-wet canvas."
    "野宮先生がふたたび琳の絵に引き込まれると、美術室を沈黙が覆う。まだ湿っているキャンバスに向かって、穏やかに高い評価をつぶやいている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4970
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_aef027b7:

    # hi "What kind of things do you paint yourself?"
    hi "先生はどういった絵を描かれるんですか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4975
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_0cde825b:

    # "As if waking from a reverie, he looks at me, surprised at my talking to him."
    "夢想から覚めたかのように、俺が声をかけたことに驚きながら先生は俺を見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4980
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_30e3212d:

    # no "Oh, I don't. Not any more."
    no "ああ、私はなにも描かんよ。今はもう、な"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4985
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_7e3a9800:

    # no "I became an art teacher only after my career in that field came to an end. Now I just pass on knowledge to the next generation."
    no "絵画という分野でのキャリアが終わったあとで、美術教師になったに過ぎない。今は知識を次の世代に伝えているだけさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4987
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_a54a4c4e:

    # "The way Nomiya answers is curious, both giving and withholding information. I feel like asking more, but he cuts in before I get the chance."
    "野宮先生の答え方は興味深い。情報を明らかにすると同時に隠してもいる。もっと尋ねたくなるけど、そのチャンスを得るまえに先生が割り込んでくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4992
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_3620d4d5:

    # no "Now you should run along, my boy. It's almost dinner time, isn't it?"
    no "さあ、そろそろ戻りなさい。もう夕食の時間だ、違うか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4994
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_30a2c079:

    # hi "Yes, sir. Have a good evening."
    hi "そうですね。おやすみなさい"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:4999
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_d5060056:

    # no "You too."
    no "ああ、おやすみ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5006
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_c4e31806:

    # "I quickly collect my stuff and step out into the deserted hallway, leaving the teacher alone with his musings."
    "俺はいそいそと荷物をまとめると、物思いにふける先生を一人残して、人の気配のない廊下へと出る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5008
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_df6312a4:

    # "The weekend will be here soon. It's amazing how fast time flies here."
    "もうすぐ週末だ。驚くほど時間が過ぎるのが早い。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5010
translate jp a2_rin_in_her_own_image_de53eb0b:

    # "I promised Emi I'd join her for the celebration of her triumph at the track meet last week. That should be plenty of fun."
    "先週の競技会の祝勝会に参加するって、笑美と約束してたな。なかなか楽しいことになりそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5027
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5f69e3b7:

    # hi "Are you sure you want to go?"
    hi "本当に行くのかよ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5029
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_6bc2ef2c:

    # "The weather that has been wonderful for all of June has finally taken a turn for the worse. The leaden clouds drooping over the town look worrisome and the air feels heavy and still, just like before rain."
    "ずっと快晴だった６月の天気もとうとう下り坂になった。街に覆いかぶさる鉛色の雲が気がかりだし、空気は雨が降る直前のように重たくよどんでいる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5031
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_099eb7f2:

    # "The forecast says there's a 60%% chance of rain this afternoon. Maybe this will mark the beginning of the rainy season."
    "天気予報では午後の降水確率は６０パーセントだと言っている。これで梅雨入りしてしまうのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5036
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_58790d74:

    # emi "Of course I'm sure! I've been waiting for this all week!"
    emi "もちろん！　一週間ずっと楽しみにしてたんだから！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5038
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ce3732e8:

    # "Emi had planned a picnic at some nearby park, with snacks aplenty bought from the convenience store, but with the weather this gloomy, it seems risky."
    "笑美はコンビニでお菓子を山ほど買い込んで、近くの公園でピクニックするつもりでいた。でもこんなにどんよりとした天気ではそれも危なそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5043
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_7b26a75b:

    # emi "I asked some other people to come too, but they didn't want to go because of the weather. We have to prove them wrong!"
    emi "他にも何人か誘ったんだけど、天気が悪いからって来たがらなかったんだ。みんなにそれが間違いだったって証明してやらないとね！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5045
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_849cb3c9:

    # hi "Wrong how?"
    hi "なにが間違ってるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5050
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_4739a185:

    # emi "You know, like how it always rains when you think it won't, and when you think it will, it doesn't? We'll go no matter what, so it's a win-win situation!"
    emi "ほら、雨って降らないと思ってると降るし、降ると思ってたら降らないものでしょ？　あたしたちはどっちみち行くんだから、これはウィン―ウィンのシチュエーションってわけ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5055
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5cb1fe75:

    # emi "I've been going without sweets for weeks because of practice for the track meet. But now I can splurge on anything I want. Nothing is going to stop me now!"
    emi "競技会の練習のために何週間も甘い物を我慢してたんだもん。でも今はいくらでも好きなことできるんだから。もうあたしを止められるものは何もないよ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5057
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_3fa3dd5f:

    # hi "I thought you were all about a healthy lifestyle and stuff."
    hi "いつでも健康第一の生活してると思ってたよ、俺は"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5062
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_295ec481:

    # emi "Ohoho, Hisao, you understand so little. There's not a single girl on this planet who doesn't love sweets!"
    emi "ちっちっち。わかってないなあ、久夫くん。甘いものが嫌いな女の子なんてこの世に１人もいないんだよ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5071
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_e4461ab3:

    # rin "I don't like sweets."
    rin "私は好きじゃないけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5077
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_2f027dc4:

    # emi "She doesn't count. Anyway, is this clear?"
    emi "琳はノーカンだから。とにかくわかった、久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5082
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_d0c30fe8:

    # hi "Completely. We will go and eat our fill of sweets."
    hi "よくわかったよ。今日は俺たちでたらふくスイーツ食うか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5088
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_0269e7d1:

    # emi "Damn straight we will."
    emi "もっちろん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5093
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_2c8829e5:

    # emi "I'm going to have to work it off later but it's so worth it."
    emi "あとでまた運動しないといけないけど、ほんとにそれだけの価値はあるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5095
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9de0ffc2:

    # "Emi seems to be extremely determined about this. She is positively exhilarated, brimming with energy as always, but something seems special today."
    "笑美の決意はものすごく固いみたいだ。笑美はまさに浮き足立っていて、いつものようにエネルギッシュだけど、今日は特別な何かがあるらしい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5097
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b3344af1:

    # "It looks like she can hardly stop herself from jumping up and down on the spot."
    "まるでその場で飛び跳ねるのを止められないってぐらいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5102
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_269bc9d0:

    # emi "Come on!"
    emi "いこ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5108
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_af3682c1:

    # "I grasp the wooden handle of the umbrella I brought and start to follow the two girls, who seem to have no qualms about leaving me behind if I keep daydreaming."
    "俺は持ってきた傘の木製の柄を握って、二人の女の子のあとについて行く。もし俺がぼんやりしていても、置き去りにしていることなど気にもかけそうにない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5110
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_2b2b7ceb:

    # "My umbrella is really fancy, the old-fashioned kind with a curved handle and a metal spike at the end. It used to belong to my grandfather. It looks like an antique, but it's in really good shape; almost as good as new."
    "この傘は実にしゃれたもので、古めかしい曲がった柄と、先端には尖った金具がついている。もともとは祖父が使っていたものだ。骨董品にも見えるけどとてもいい状態で、まるで新品同様だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5112
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_09850ca4:

    # "It's really big, too. I remember how my grandfather, my grandmother, and I all fit neatly under it when a rainstorm caught us on an afternoon walk years ago, when I was around nine or ten."
    "しかもかなり大きい。何年も前、午後の散歩中に大雨に降られたとき、祖父と、祖母と俺の３人がきれいに収まっていたのを覚えている。９歳か１０歳のときのことだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5114
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_8ed983ef:

    # "My grandparents are both gone now, but I still have the umbrella to keep me dry when it rains."
    "祖父母はもう亡くなっているけど、この傘は今も俺を雨から守ってくれる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5119
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_0a6494df:

    # "We walk along the road leading down from the school towards the convenience store, the clouds casting their dark shadow down on us. The weather seems to be taking a turn for the worse and I am pretty sure I just felt a raindrop on my head."
    "学校からコンビニに向かう道に沿って歩いていくと、雲が俺たちに暗い影を落とす。天気がさらに悪くなりはじめてるようだ。しかも今、間違いなく頭に雨粒が落ちたのを感じた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5121
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_f3c28e11:

    # hi "Didn't you guys think of taking umbrellas? It really looks like it'll rain."
    hi "二人とも傘を持ってこようって思わなかったのか？　本当に降ってきそうだぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5127
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_35b0ee41:

    # "Rin looks at her limply hanging sleeves and shrugs her shoulders."
    "琳はだらりと垂れた袖を見て、肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5133
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_bf1e5e95:

    # emi "I don't have one. Besides, a little rain won't kill us."
    emi "あたし傘持ってないし。それに、ちょっとぐらい降られても死なないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5135
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_08db4ae6:

    # "She pushes her chest out, looking very confident about that."
    "笑美は自信満々そうに胸を張る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5140
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b4c311d9:

    # emi "We aren't made of sugar!"
    emi "あたしたち、お砂糖でできてるわけじゃないんだから！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5145
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_a683532b:

    # hi "I thought that's exactly what girls were made of, especially considering what you're planning to gorge yourself on today."
    hi "女の子はまさにそれでできてると思ったよ。今日これから食べまくろうとしてるもののことを考えたら、なおさらさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5150
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_46b36b45:

    # "She just sticks out her tongue in reply."
    "答えるかわりに、笑美はべーっと舌を突き出すだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5156
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9153f7ed:

    # "The walk down from the school to the local shopping district is not a long one, but it's not very short, either. It's all downhill so our steps roll easily, but time stretches out nevertheless."
    "学校から地元の商店街に下っていく道はそう長くないけど、とても短いってわけでもない。全体が下り坂だから俺たちは軽々と歩いていくけど、それでも時間はかかる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5158
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_7b5d5cc5:

    # "The distance is right there, in that gray area where you don't expect the trip to be quickly over with, but you aren't preparing for a long walk, either."
    "距離にしても、すぐに到着するとは考えていないけど、長い道のりを覚悟するほどでもない、という中途半端なところだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5160
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ed4e4f5f:

    # "Thus, the trip is slightly too long to stay comfortably quiet the whole time, though the girls don't seem to mind."
    "つまり、始終快適な静けさというには少しばかり長すぎる道のりだ。女の子勢は気にしてないみたいだけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5162
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_d4c61962:

    # "Rin walks calmly ahead, seemingly lost in thought. I'm kind of wary about starting a conversation, since the last time didn't end very well for either of us."
    "琳は静かに前を歩いている。考えにふけっているようだ。会話を始めるのになんだか慎重になってしまっている。この前の会話はどちらにとってもいい終わり方をしなかったからな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5164
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_f50f0b8c:

    # "I haven't exchanged a single word with her since then."
    "あれから琳と一言も言葉を交わしてない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5166
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_122a7f22:

    # "Emi, on the other hand, is way too happy about just walking."
    "一方で笑美は、歩いているだけでもとても楽しそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5168
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_19f259a3:

    # "She seems to literally jump a little on every step, or skip over cracks, or balance on the edge of the sidewalk. Every now and then she comments on something to which Rin replies in an automatic-sounding, nonsensical way that makes Emi giggle a little."
    "足を踏み出すたびに文字通りジャンプしたり、地面のひびを飛び越えたり、歩道の端でバランスを取ったりしている。 ときどきとりとめのないことを言うと、琳が自動応答っぽい調子で意味をなさない返事をして、それを聞いた笑美がくすくすと笑う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5176
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_a402f7bd:

    # "As we reach the bottom of the hill, the first raindrops begin to fall. I feel one hit the top of my head, then two more hit my nose in quick succession."
    "丘のふもとにたどり着くと、最初の雨粒が降りはじめる。一滴が頭のてっぺんに当たり、続いて二滴がたて続けに鼻に当たる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5186
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_47b46cfd:

    # "It's not one or two rainclouds any more. The entire sky has turned shadowy gray, billowing rainclouds swirling right on top of us."
    "いまや雨雲は１つ２つじゃない。空全体が陰った灰色になり、俺たちの真上で雨雲が渦を巻いている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5191
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_bfa2c4c5:

    # emi "Oh, shoot. I guess we aren't going to have a picnic then."
    emi "うそっ！　ピクニック、できなくなっちゃうなあ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5193
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_0d57a6b0:

    # hi "What now?"
    hi "どうするんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5202
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_d0463f18:

    # rin "Maybe we could have a rain picnic. A picnic in rain."
    rin "雨天ピクニックなんてどうかな。雨のなかでピクニック"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5207
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b5a20dc9:

    # emi "No, we'd all just catch a cold and I don't like getting me or my snacks wet."
    emi "やだあ、風邪ひいちゃうし、あたしもお菓子も濡れるのやだもん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5212
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_67969337:

    # rin "I kind of like it. Not the snacks part though."
    rin "私は好きだよ。お菓子が濡れるのはいやだけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5221
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_305a5dba:

    # "Emi considers our problematic situation for a moment while I open my umbrella and lift it up, trying to hold it so that all three of us get covered."
    "俺が傘を広げて持ち上げ、３人とも中に収めようとしているあいだに、笑美はこの厄介な状況をしばらく検討する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5226
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_d1bf1bf8:

    # emi "Hey Hisao, have you been to the Shanghai yet?"
    emi "ねえ久夫くん。上海には行ったことある？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5232
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_09a08c8e:

    # hi "Yeah, our class president took me there on my first week."
    hi "ああ。俺のクラスの委員長に、最初の週に連れてきてもらったよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5234
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5b7f6132:

    # hi "It's a café somewhere around here, right? I've heard of it."
    hi "この辺にある喫茶店だろ？　聞いたことはあるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5240
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_00c1acbc:

    # emi "It's a nice place. Let's go there and wait out the rain. If it's just a really quick shower, we can still go for the picnic, and if it gets worse, we'll just order cake there instead."
    emi "いいところなんだ。そこで雨宿りしようよ。通り雨ならそのままピクニックもできるし、雨がひどくなったら代わりにそこでケーキ食べようよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5251
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_fadbfbd1:

    # "Neither Rin nor I have better ideas, so with Emi taking the lead, we start walking briskly along a side street."
    "俺も琳もほかにいい案はなく、笑美に先導されて、俺たちはわき道を足早に歩き始める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5259
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_3466701d:

    # "The café is only a few blocks away, but even with the umbrella, we can't avoid getting slightly damp. The rain keeps coming down harder and harder."
    "店はほんの数ブロック先だけど、傘をさしていても濡れるのは避けられない。雨はどんどん強くなる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5261
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_4123512e:

    # "Raindrops leave tiny dots on the black asphalt road, which then combine into bigger patches like pointillist artwork being made in front of our eyes in mere seconds."
    "雨粒が黒いアスファルトに小さな点をつくり、それがくっついて大きなまだらになり、俺たちの目の前にほんの数秒で点画が描かれたようになる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5263
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_563ca0b4:

    # "It's pouring heavily, drumming on the hoods of the cars parked on the sides of the street and already flowing in little creeks along the sidewalks."
    "雨は激しく降っていて、路肩に停まっている車の屋根に打ちつけられている。すでに歩道に沿って小さな川ができて流れている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5265
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_44289002:

    # "The yellow light shining through the rainwater streaming down the windows looks very warm and inviting."
    "窓を流れ落ちる雨水を通り越して、黄色い光が暖かく、歓迎するように届いてくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5277
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_f17ebc05:

    # "I shake the excess water off the umbrella and head inside with them, following Emi to a vacant table in the furthest corner of the small café."
    "俺は傘を振るって余分な水滴を落とすと、二人と一緒に中に入る。笑美を追って店のいちばん奥の角にある空いたテーブルにつく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5281
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_38c5bc52:

    # "The place is almost full; apparently other people had the same idea as Emi, and now we are all stranded together here in this cozy little place."
    "店内はほぼ満員だ。笑美と同じことを考えた人は他にもいたらしい。いまや俺たちもこの小さく居心地のいい場所で足止めされてるってわけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5286
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b21b3c9c:

    # "Varnished wooden pillars and paper screens mix with Parisian-style tables and chairs in discordant harmony, a contrast of old and new."
    "ニスの塗られた木の柱と障子が、パリ風なテーブルと椅子に混在して、不調和のハーモニーを見せる。古めかしさと新しさのコントラストだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5288
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_400e6d18:

    # "Light jazz plays quietly in the background, though it's mostly drowned out by the murmur of the customers."
    "軽いジャズが静かに流れているけど、お客のざわめきでほとんどかき消されている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5291
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_a3c1fb07:

    # "I notice Yuuko is at work here today, but it seems like she's serving a full house all by herself, frantically gliding from one table to another and trying to keep up with everything."
    "優子さんが働いているのに気づく。でも今日は一人きりで給仕をしているようだ。必死にテーブルからテーブルへ動き回って、遅れないようにしている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5293
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9d76d792:

    # "I watch her deliver a tray of tea cups and pastries to another table taken by Yamaku students, then take an order from a middle-aged couple sitting across from us before finally turning to serve us."
    "トレイに乗せたティーカップとケーキを山久学園の生徒が座っている別のテーブルに運び、真向かいのテーブルに座っている中年の男女の注文を取ってから、ようやく俺たちのところにやってくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5295
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_03240e71:

    # hi "Hi, Yuuko."
    hi "こんにちは、優子さん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5305
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ba644fac:

    # yu "Umm… ah, welcome to the Shanghai. "
    yu "ええっと……そうそう、上海にようこそ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5307
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_c87117cf:

    # hi "Looks like you're busy."
    hi "忙しいみたいですね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5312
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b0e105a0:

    # yu "Ahaha, I'm completely over my head here. I wish I had another pair of hands."
    yu "あはは、ほんとに参っちゃうわ。猫の手も借りたいぐらいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5317
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_c6b45be8:

    # yu "What can I get for you today?"
    yu "ご注文は？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5319
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_c24276ad:

    # "There's only one waitress serving the full house, frantically gliding from one table to another and trying to keep up with everything. To my surprise, I think I recognize her."
    "給仕をしているウェイトレスは１人だけで、必死にテーブルからテーブルへ動き回って、遅れないようにしている。驚いたのはその顔に見覚えがあることだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5321
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9d76d792_1:

    # "I watch her deliver a tray of tea cups and pastries to another table taken by Yamaku students, then take an order from a middle-aged couple sitting across from us before finally turning to serve us."
    "トレイに乗せたティーカップとケーキを山久学園の生徒が座っている別のテーブルに運び、真向かいのテーブルに座っている中年の男女の注文を取ってから、ようやく俺たちのところにやってくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5323
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_39c19179:

    # hi "Yuuko?"
    hi "優子さん？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5333
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_c3bd38b8:

    # "Now that she's close and facing me I see that it really is her, the part-time librarian of Yamaku in full waitress attire. It's a pretty cute outfit, and she has tied her hair up in buns to match."
    "実際に近くで顔を見てみると、確かに学校の図書室でアルバイトをしている優子さんが、全身ウェイトレスの格好でそこにいる。とても可愛らしい制服で、それにあわせて髪をおだんごにまとめている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5338
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_4f7e4c33:

    # "It's a completely different image from her mousy, plain style at her other job. Yuuko blinks a few times looking confused, then remembers that she was about to say something."
    "図書室にいるときみたいな、おとなしめで質素な装いとはまったく違うイメージだ。優子さんは困惑したように数回まばたきすると、自分がなにか言いかけていたことを思いだす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5343
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9ffc9a0b:

    # yu "Umm… ah, welcome to the Shanghai."
    yu "ええっと……そうそう、上海にようこそ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5345
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_850cd723:

    # hi "So you work here too? I thought you were a university student or something."
    hi "ここでも働いてたんですか？　大学生かなにかだったと思ってたんですけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5350
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_6713aec7:

    # yu "Ehh, yes, that too. It's a part-time job as you can see, ehehe. It's Sunday, so there aren't any lectures."
    yu "ええ、そうね、ここでも働いてるの。見てのとおりアルバイトよ、えへへ。今日は日曜だから講義はないのよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5355
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_550ff9a8:

    # yu "Good thing, too, since today has been so busy I'm wishing for another pair of hands. Anyway, I'm in a bit of a rush as you can see. What can I get you today?"
    yu "それに、今日は猫の手も借りたいぐらい忙しいしね。というわけで、見ての通りだけど大わらわなの。それで、ご注文は？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5375
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_3a2cd7f8:

    # "Emi doesn't hesitate even for a second. Her eyes glitter like those of a kid in a candy store."
    "笑美は１秒たりともためらわない。目がお菓子屋に来た子供のように輝く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5381
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_6394dfb1:

    # emi "Tea for everyone! And cake for me!"
    emi "みんなに紅茶！　あとあたしにはケーキも！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5386
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b8da4fc6:

    # "Yuuko tries to stay as formal and professional-looking as possible, smiling cheerily at my ravenous companion."
    "優子さんは腹をすかせた笑美に明るい笑顔を向けて、できるだけフォーマルに、プロらしく立ち振る舞おうとする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5391
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_1d3f802b:

    # yu "Ahh… yes, today we have a choice of strawberry shortcake, raspberry layer cake, or lemon meringue pie."
    yu "ええと……はい、今日はイチゴのショートケーキとラズベリーのレイヤーケーキ、それからレモンメレンゲパイの３つをご用意してます"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5396
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_8cfc55e1:

    # emi "Strawberry… no, lemon! No, actually I'll take both!"
    emi "イチゴの……ううん、レモン！　待って、両方がいいな！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5398
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_21d4daeb:

    # "She looks at me in challenge."
    "笑美は挑発するように俺を見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5400
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_1e25eb13:

    # hi "Err… I'll take just the pie."
    hi "ええと……俺はパイだけください"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5405
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_be162ee9:

    # rin "Nothing."
    rin "何もいらない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5410
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_3e9984c4:

    # "Emi makes a face at Rin as though she had bitten into a lemon. She's clearly unhappy with her for not joining in."
    "笑美はレモンを丸かじりしたかのようなしかめ面を琳に向ける。明らかに琳が乗ってこなかったことに不満そうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5412
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_486bd4b0:

    # emi "Oh come on, Rin. That's not polite at all."
    emi "なあにそれ、琳。そんなの失礼じゃない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5417
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_6cfa5027:

    # rin "Nothing, thank you."
    rin "何もいらない、です"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5422
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_0cd503b1:

    # emi "No, no, you silly! I meant that you should order something too."
    emi "そうじゃなくて！　琳もなにか頼みなよってこと"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5427
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_4bd6ecfd:

    # rin "I'll take a straw then. My feet are all wet."
    rin "じゃあストローください。足、濡れちゃったから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5432
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b0a07651:

    # yu "Sorry?"
    yu "え、なんて？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5437
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5f4fa944:

    # rin "The drinking kind of straw. One, please."
    rin "飲むのに使うストロー。ひとつください"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5442
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ce38e976:

    # "Yuuko is obviously uncertain of what to think about this. She fiddles with her pen and stationery for a moment, looking like she's about to cry, before deciding that we've finished ordering."
    "優子さんは明らかにどう受け取ればいいのかわからずにいる。今にも泣き出しそうな顔でしばらくペンとメモ帳をいじっていたけど、やがて俺たちが注文を終えたと判断する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5447
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_cc959d1f:

    # yu "Thank you very much!"
    yu "ありがとうございます！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5468
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_405f8ba2:

    # "She bows down a little bit too deeply and scampers to safety behind the counter."
    "優子さんは深々とお辞儀をすると、カウンターの向こう側へと逃げるように走っていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5470
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ea10d872:

    # "After that ordeal is over with, I have a chance to relax a bit and take a better look at the surroundings."
    "今の試練が終わったところで、ようやく俺は少しリラックスして、周りをもっとよく見ることができる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5472
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_bd1b8aba:

    # "Almost every table is occupied by people happy to be out of the rain, thankfully sipping their tea while waiting to dry off."
    "どのテーブルも雨を逃れて安心したような人たちが座っていて、服などが乾くのを待つ間、紅茶をありがたそうにすすっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5474
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_3f0290a9:

    # "Fragments of grumbling about the lousy weather or discussions over recent homework carry from nearby tables to my ears. Each one overlaps the other, but all are covered by the sound of falling rain."
    "ひどい天気に不平をいう声や、学校の宿題のことを話し合う声の切れ端が、近くのテーブルからちらほら耳に入ってくる。それぞれが重なりあって聞こえてくるけど、どれも降りしきる雨の音に覆われている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5487
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ede2d3e1:

    # "After a while Yuuko returns to our table, carrying a tray with a huge teapot, three cups, a slice of cake and two slices of pie."
    "しばらくすると、優子さんが俺たちのテーブルに大きなティーポットと３つのカップ、ケーキ一切れとパイ二切れを乗せたトレイを持って戻ってくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5514
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_bfab7d89:

    # "She slaps the tray onto our tiny table with a clatter, almost sending the teapot toppling over into Rin's lap. We barely recover before she bows again and leaves, hurrying off to serve the other customers."
    "優子さんが小さいテーブルにトレイを叩きつけるようにガシャンと置くので、ティーポットが琳のひざに倒れこみそうになる。 俺たちがかろうじてそれを押さえると、優子さんはまたお辞儀をしてほかのお客のところへと急ぐ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5516
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_0495dd26:

    # "Emi has been eyeing her strawberry cake very hungrily all this time, but somehow she managed to contain herself until Yuuko was out of sight."
    "笑美はイチゴのケーキをとてももの欲しそうに見つめていたけど、優子さんが見えなくなるまでかろうじてこらえた。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5521
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_81c33a42:

    # "She digs in with gusto, while I content myself with pouring tea for everyone and placing the straw in Rin's cup."
    "俺がみんなのカップに紅茶を注いで、琳のカップにはストローを差しているあいだに、笑美はがつがつとケーキを満喫する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5526
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_360a5904:

    # "Rin looks at the way the tea swirls round and round in her white china cup, her eyes half closed, almost like she is being hypnotized."
    "琳は白磁のティーカップのなかで紅茶がぐるぐると回るのを見ている。目は催眠術をかけられているみたいに半開きだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5537
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_84f452ed:

    # "I pick up my fork and eye the food in front of me. The pie I got looks perfectly done, a thick layer of meringue atop creamy lemon custard."
    "俺はフォークをもって目の前の食べ物を見やる。注文したパイは最高の見栄えだ。レモンカスタードの上に厚いメレンゲの層が乗っている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5539
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_07a85540:

    # "After having the first bite, I pause, savoring the combination of tangy citrus and smooth, sugary meringue. It's quite good, though a bit too sweet for me."
    "最初の一口を食べると俺は一息ついて、鼻を突き抜けるシトラスの香りと、甘くなめらかなメレンゲのコンビネーションを味わう。ほんとうにうまいけど、俺にはちょっと甘すぎるな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5552
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_41146ec4:

    # emi "Iff ver’ good."
    emi "ふごいおいひいね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5554
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_4a14d022:

    # "She's talking through a mouthful of cake, already halfway through her slice even though it's not exactly small."
    "笑美はケーキをほおばったまましゃべっている。そんなに小さくもないケーキがもう半分になっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5559
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_12e48ba5:

    # emi "I want to taste some of that."
    emi "そっちのも食べてみたいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5571
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_e02cf045:

    # "Before I get to respond, she strikes out at my delicious pie, takes a piece with her fork, and escapes with it."
    "俺が答える前に、笑美は俺のおいしいパイに攻撃をしかけ、フォークでひとかけらを取り、そのまま逃げおおせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5576
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_6e1d50dc:

    # emi "This is pretty good too."
    emi "こっちもすごいおいしいや"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5578
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_bee4267d:

    # hi "What are you doing? You have a slice of your own!"
    hi "おい、何するんだよ？　そっちも同じのがあるだろ！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5583
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_aeba857e:

    # emi "Yeah, but if I started on that before finishing the cake, it'd be rude, don't you think?"
    emi "うん。でもこっちのケーキを食べ終える前に、パイまで食べ始めちゃったらお行儀悪いでしょ。そう思わない？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5585
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_00945715:

    # "Her insolence is outrageous, but the gentleman in me allows for no retaliation."
    "笑美の生意気な態度にあきれかえるけど、俺のなかの紳士が仕返しをさせまいとする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5590
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_bfb9c019:

    # "I glare angrily at her, and she replies by sticking out her tongue impishly. Emi is even more hyper than usual today, but I don't mind. It's good for her to let off some steam."
    "俺が腹立たしげににらみつけると、笑美はいたずらっぽく舌を出してみせる。今日の笑美はいつも以上にテンションが高いけど、俺は気にしない。笑美が日ごろの憂さを晴らすのにはこれがいい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5592
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_747cf144:

    # "I take another sip of the tea in my cup. It's good and hot, even though I don't usually care much for tea, and the atmosphere in the café is very relaxing."
    "俺はまた紅茶をすする。紅茶にはそんなにこだわりはないけど、これは熱くてうまい。それにこの店の雰囲気はとても落ち着く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5594
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_7a190aa3:

    # "I don't mind spending the rest of the afternoon here, not even after Emi orders her second piece of strawberry cake and Rin spends most of the time staring fixedly at the rain streaming down from the heavens."
    "ここで午後の間ずっと過ごしたってかまわない。笑美がイチゴケーキのおかわりをして、琳が天から降ってくる雨をじっと見続けていても。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5598
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ca7047ca:

    # "Even Yuuko rolls her eyes at the third piece of cake disappearing into Emi's bottomless stomach just as quickly as the previous two."
    "それまでの２つと変わらない早さで、３つめのケーキが笑美の底なしの胃袋に収まってしまうのを見て、優子さんもあきれた表情を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5607
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_07bb4832:

    # "Despite the passing of time, it's still raining outside when we exit the Shanghai, though it seems to be letting up a little."
    "時間は経っていたけど、俺たちが上海を出るときになっても雨は降り続けている。とはいえ、少しは弱まってきているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5609
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_7ec30225:

    # hi "Too bad it had to rain on your parade."
    hi "せっかくのお祝いだったのに残念だな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5614
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_61c5bee7:

    # rin "Weren't we supposed to have a picnic?"
    rin "ピクニックするんじゃなかったの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5623
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_219f0fd1:

    # "Emi doesn't look too distraught over this turn of events."
    "笑美はこの事の成り行きにもあまり動揺していないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5625
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_272c0c0d:

    # emi "Nah it's fine! We had a good time, didn't we? I feel really pumped up."
    emi "別に平気だよ！　みんな楽しかったでしょ？　あたし、すっごく元気になったよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5630
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_dde8dca8:

    # emi "It isn't even raining that hard any more. I kinda want to hike back to school to get rid of this energy and work off some of that cake."
    emi "それに雨、弱くなってきたじゃん。学校まで歩いて戻ってさ、エネルギー使って、ケーキの分のカロリーも消費したいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5632
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5bf538f9:

    # "She stretches her arms out, and arches her back like a cat. After rolling her shoulders around twice, she smiles brightly."
    "笑美は両腕を伸ばすと、猫のように背中を反らす。腕を２度ぐるぐると回すと、明るい笑顔を浮かべる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5637
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_26ea8915:

    # emi "Man, I can't really run with these legs, though, especially uphill. I wish I'd brought my other ones."
    emi "ちぇー、でもこの足じゃ走れないなあ、上り坂じゃ特にさ。もうひとつの、持ってくればよかったな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5639
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_3f083cc4:

    # "This notion sounds odd, spoken so casually. But I guess for Emi, changing legs is sort of like someone else changing shoes."
    "そんなに軽くいわれると妙に聞こえる。でも笑美にとっては、義足を取り替えることはほかの人が靴を履き替えるのと似たような感じなんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5644
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_f47cd2f4:

    # emi "Maybe if I walk really fast, that'll be kinda like running. I think I'll do that."
    emi "すごい早く歩けば、走ってるみたいになるよね。やってみよっと"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5649
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_8419b1e3:

    # hi "I won't be able to keep up with that going uphill, though; I really am in bad shape. Plus, you'll get wet without an umbrella."
    hi "この上り坂じゃ俺はついていくのは無理だな。マジで体調悪いし。それに傘、差さないと濡れるぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5655
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5581b9df:

    # emi "It's hardly even a drizzle, now. A few drops won't hurt. I think I'm gonna go to the track after I change my legs, too."
    emi "もうほとんど降ってないじゃん。少しぐらいなら平気だよ。足、取り替えたらまた運動場に行くし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5657
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5adabb30:

    # "Emi skips away from the protection of my umbrella and goes on ahead at a brisk pace. Suddenly, she seems to remember something as she stops and spins around."
    "笑美は俺の傘の下からスキップしながら出ていってしまい、元気よく前に進んでいく。とつぜん、なにかを思い出したように立ち止まって振り返る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5662
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_f7f342fd:

    # emi "See you tomorrow!"
    emi "また明日ね！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5667
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_1300b086:

    # emi "Come eat lunch with us on the roof! I'll bring enough for three."
    emi "また屋上でお昼食べようね！　３人分作ってくるからさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5681
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_5994e5d1:

    # "Rin and I are left to watch her wave at us and skip off again. Soon she disappears around a street corner. I'll never understand why Emi is perpetually in such a hurry to get somewhere."
    "琳と俺は笑美が手を振って、また走り去っていくのを見送る。やがて通りの角を曲がって姿が見えなくなる。どうして笑美がいつもどこへいくにもあんなに急ぎ足なのか、俺には決して理解できそうにない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5683
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9de0a517:

    # hi "So, would you like me to walk you back to school so that at least one of you won't get wet?"
    hi "さて、あいつはともかく、お前は濡れないように学校まで送ろうか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5688
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_917e323a:

    # rin "If you are happy with it."
    rin "そうしたいならいいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5690
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_081997b2:

    # "It seems neither of us wants to keep alive the strained atmosphere from the argument a few days ago in the art room, which makes me feel relieved. I don't want to bear grudges and I'm happy that Rin feels the same way."
    "どうやら二人とも、数日前に美術室で言い争ったとき以来のぎくしゃくした空気を引きずりたくなかったようで、俺はほっとする。このわだかまりに耐えるのは嫌だし、琳が同じように感じていることが嬉しい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5692
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_a4940714:

    # "Thus it is decided that we are content with each other's company for now, and we start walking in the same direction as Emi, albeit at a considerably calmer pace."
    "だから俺たちはいま、お互いに連れだって歩くことに満足していることになる。ペースはかなり落ち着いているけど、俺たちは笑美と同じ方向に歩きはじめる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5701
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_28660696:

    # "I get a bit closer to Rin, even though the umbrella is already big enough to shelter us both. I can feel her nearby warmth providing a contrast to the chill of this rainy weather."
    "傘は俺たち二人を覆うのに十分な大きさだけど、俺は少し琳に近づく。雨の冷たさと対をなすように、すぐそばにある琳の温かさが感じられる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5703
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_72ea9d07:

    # "Raindrops hitting the umbrella make a distinctive sound, playing the staccato melody of rainfall for nobody in particular."
    "雨粒が傘をたたいて、誰にともなくスタッカートの演奏をしているような独特の音を立てる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5705
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_99870d6e:

    # "I realize I haven't been outside in the rain in what feels like forever. I inhale, taking in the scent of rain, feeling the weather with all my senses."
    "雨の日に外出するのはものすごく久し振りだったことに気づく。雨の匂いを胸の奥まで吸い込んで、全身の感覚で気候を感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5707
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_c06bc197:

    # "The world melts into a blur inside the rain."
    "世界全体が雨のなかに溶け込んで、ぼやけている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5709
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b3914233:

    # "The colors of the sky have deepened from gray to dark blue, with hues of red added to the mix from the sunlight reflecting off the clouds. The low-hanging sky looks pretty, as if I could reach out my hand and touch it."
    "空の色が灰色から濃い青に深まり、そこへ雲に反射する夕日の赤い色が混ざり合う。手を伸ばせばさわれそうなくらい、低く垂れ込める空がきれいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5713
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_12f442bc:

    # rin "Have I told you how much I like rain? It's like painting. It makes me feel connected."
    rin "雨がどれくらい好きかって話したっけ？　絵を描くみたいなものだよ。一体感を感じるんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5715
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_e8ad2cee:

    # "Almost echoing my thoughts, Rin lets out one of her own. It slips out of her mouth, circling around us gently."
    "俺の考えに同意するかのように、琳は自分の考えを表に出す。それは口から滑り出て、俺たちの周りを穏やかに回っている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5717
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_c34eeec9:

    # rin "Everything looks so soft, like the outlines of things just disappear. I like that."
    rin "いろんなものの輪郭が消えていくみたいにさ、なにもかもやわらかそうに見えるんだ。それが好きなの"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5719
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b8cff13e:

    # rin "It's like the rain is hugging me."
    rin "雨が私を抱きしめてるみたい"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5721
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_7bca3577:

    # "Her voice sounds different from usual; more gentle, now, and soft. I wonder if it's only because of the rain, or because of the mood the rain brought upon the quiet artist girl."
    "その声はいつもと違って聞こえる。いつもよりずっとやさしく、やわらかな声だ。単にこの雨のせいなのか、それとも雨がこの物静かな芸術少女をそんな気分にさせているからなのか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5728
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_3cc00c31:

    # "I feel that mood in myself too, enhanced by her words."
    "琳の言葉を受けて、俺自身もそんな気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5730
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_4d384378:

    # hi "Yeah. I like rainy weather too. It's nice every once in a while."
    hi "ああ。俺も雨は好きだよ。たまにはいいよな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5732
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9ac76414:

    # hi "I wonder what is it about the rain."
    hi "雨ってなんなんだろうな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5738
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_365fb0a2:

    # rin "Everything."
    rin "あらゆるものだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5748
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_806207ff:

    # "A silence follows the statement, as it allows for no continuation. I decide to push the direction of the conversation a little."
    "それ以上続ける言葉がなく、沈黙が降りる。俺はもう少し突っ込んで話してみる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5750
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_6ffa8683:

    # hi "But you know, if you like the feeling of being connected, what's the problem with showing your paintings to others?"
    hi "でもよ、その一体感が好きなら、どうして絵を誰かに見せるのはいやなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5752
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b0a1274d:

    # hi "Don't you want to be connected to other people?"
    hi "ほかの誰かと一体感を感じたくはないのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5759
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_ca48ed5c:

    # rin "It's not the same thing. You're comparing apples and squids."
    rin "それは別問題だよ。イカとりんごが同じだって言うようなものだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5761
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_beb31f10:

    # "I brought up the subject Rin wants to avoid, and it shuts her down again. The question stays hanging between us for the rest of the trip back to school, and I can't help wondering what on Earth I could have said to truly reach Rin."
    "琳が避けたがっている話題を俺が持ち出したおかげで、また琳は黙ってしまう。 学校に戻るまでの間、その問いがずっと俺たちの間にぶら下がっていて、なんて言えばちゃんと琳の心に届くんだろう、と考えずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5763
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_469f10a3:

    # "Does she feel that she's lacking an identity?"
    "琳は自分にアイデンティティが欠けていると思っているのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5765
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_f419d33b:

    # "She has a strong personality, but if pressed to elaborate, I'm not sure I could describe it accurately. She feels like a person who is in constant conflict with herself. I never know what to expect when I talk to her."
    "琳は強い個性をもってるけど、やれといわれてもそれを的確に説明することはできそうにない。琳はきっといつも自分自身と衝突しているような人間なんだろう。琳と話すとき、俺はいつも全く予想がつかない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5767
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_71c6eace:

    # "I wonder how she herself experiences that disconnect."
    "琳本人はその食い違いをどう感じているんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5769
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_e52a8fd6:

    # "If Rin is asking herself every day 'Who am I?' and obsessively paints images to define herself day after day, what does she think of that way of living?"
    "もし琳が自分に『私は誰？』と毎日問い続けて、日々とりつかれたように自分を定義するために絵を描いているのだとしたら、そんな生き方をどう思っているんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5774
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b3d1464c:

    # "The irony is, that's the exact same question I've been asking myself for the past four or five months. For me, it was miserable. I can only assume that it's the natural state of being for this girl."
    "皮肉なのは、４、５か月前の自分がまったく同じ疑問を俺自身に投げかけていたってことだ。自分にとっては、惨めなものだった。俺はただ、それが琳にとっては自然なことなんだ、と推測することしかできない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5783
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_6c89f004:

    # "When we stop in front of the dormitories Rin turns to face me, as if sensing my thoughts from afar. Her gaze travels emptily past my left shoulder into the shapeless rainfall."
    "寮の前で足を止めると、まるで遠くから俺の考えを見透かしたかのように、琳が俺のほうを向く。そのうつろな視線は俺の左肩を通り越して、不定形の雨の中へと向かっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5785
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_4044761d:

    # "Her dark eyes seem to suck the low ambient light into themselves, like a reverse mirror."
    "琳の黒い目が、鏡が光を反射するのとは逆に、周辺の弱い光を吸収しているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5787
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_9dacc14c:

    # "That empty gaze lets nothing out. If I want to understand what's going on behind those eyes, I have to work it out myself."
    "その虚ろな視線は何も投げかけてこない。その裏で何が起きているのか理解したければ、自分でどうにかするしかない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5789
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_64451b1e:

    # "Rin opens her mouth, then closes it without saying anything. The silence lasts for a few more moments before she takes a step towards the dorm building door."
    "琳は口を開けると、何も言わずにまた閉じてしまう。琳が寮のドアに向かって歩き出すまでもうしばらく沈黙が続く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5796
translate jp a2_rin_umbrella_logic_cake_b2a7bd4f:

    # rin "See you tomorrow."
    rin "また明日ね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5812
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1e0d3b8a:

    # "The next morning, like every second Monday morning until he says otherwise, I have an appointment with the nurse."
    "次の日の朝。第二月曜日はいつも、他に指示がない限りはナースの診察を受けることになっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5814
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_b9334d67:

    # "They allow me to skip part of my first class in the morning, and I don't feel any shame in skipping the rest, either."
    "そのときは朝イチの授業を抜け出す許可をくれる。ついでに残りの授業をサボっても、俺は悪いともなんとも思わない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5816
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1c1f7584:

    # "Rather than being thankful I get to miss world history, I instead feel dread when I think about these appointments."
    "世界史の授業をとばせることを喜ぶよりも、ナースの診察のことを考えて気分が滅入ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5824
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_e2439b37:

    # "I wake up at the normal time anyway and wash myself in the bathroom I share with Kenji, tidying my sleep-disheveled hair."
    "とにかくいつもの時間に起きると、健二と共同で使っているシャワー室で体を洗い、寝癖のついた髪をととのえる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5826
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_4d931a6f:

    # "I quickly get dressed and put my laundry in the basket."
    "素早く着替えて、洗濯物をかごに入れる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5832
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ed95adc1:

    # "I pack up for the school day. I have all my homework done, like usual, so I have a bit of free time now."
    "学校へ行く用意をする。いつもどおり宿題は全部やってあるから、少し時間に余裕がある。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5834
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8ba91f08:

    # "There's no point in going to the morning class for 20 minutes before I'd have to get to the nurse's office, so I lie down on my bed and read a book until it's time to go."
    "医務室にいく前に２０分だけ朝の授業に出てもしょうがないから、出かける時間になるまでベッドに寝転がって本を読むことにする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5844
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_e0069ae8:

    # "The door to the nurse's office is open, which is unusual. I enter while knocking to announce my arrival. Looking up from his computer screen, he motions me to take a seat with a friendly hello."
    "医務室のドアが開いている。珍しいな。俺は着いたことを知らせるためにノックしながら中に入る。パソコンから顔を上げて、ナースは親しげに挨拶をすると席に着くよう促す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5846
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_d5daf2a5:

    # "Steam wafts up from a piping hot cup of coffee on his desk. It's probably not his first today."
    "机の上の熱々のコーヒーのカップから、湯気が立ちのぼっている。今日の最初の一杯目、というわけではなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5854
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_57deba61:

    # nk "How are you feeling on this wonderful morning, Hisao?"
    nk "実にさわやかな朝だね。調子はどうかな、久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5856
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_141a8926:

    # hi "I'm all right, I think. It was cold yesterday because of the rain so I woke up feeling a bit groggy."
    hi "順調、だと思います。昨日は雨が降ってて寒かったから、起きるときに少し足元がふらふらしました"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5861
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_2b31cf45:

    # nk "You too, huh? Quite a few kids got caught without an umbrella, so we've been spending time handing out masks and curing sniffles. Hmm… all right, today it's tests day. Give me your arm."
    nk "君もかい？　かなりの数の子が傘を持ってないときに降られてね。それで、僕たちも延々マスクを配ったり、鼻風邪を診たりしてるわけさ。うーん……よし、今日は検査の日だね。腕を出して"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5866
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_48a69d05:

    # "I extend my left arm towards him, keeping my face expressionless. The nurse ties a rubber tourniquet around my bicep with a practiced movement and briskly goes about his business."
    "俺は無表情を保ったまま、左腕をナースに差し出す。ナースは俺の二の腕に慣れた手つきでゴム製の止血帯を巻くと、きびきびと仕事を進める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5868
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_925e6d4a:

    # "I don't think anybody really likes getting stuck with needles, but at least I got over my distaste for them. I had to. Now, I barely even twitch at the moment of truth."
    "注射されるのが好きな人なんて誰もいないだろうけど、少なくとも俺は苦手さを克服した。そうするしかなかった。今では針が刺さるその瞬間でさえ、体はぴくりとも動かない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5870
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_fa0a8dc1:

    # "Once that's done, a blood pressure check follows, then there are checklists and questionnaires to go through. The nurse nods and scribbles in my answers to the questions as I give them."
    "それが終わったら血圧測定、そしてチェックリストと問診票の確認が続く。ナースは質問に対する俺の答えを、答えるそばからうなずいて書き留めていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5875
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_93180efa:

    # nk "All right. Let's have a listen, now."
    nk "オーケー。それじゃあ音を聞いてみようか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5881
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_9ed5c0d1:

    # "I unbutton my shirt and put it neatly on the back of the chair I was using while he puts on his stethoscope."
    "ナースが聴診器をつける間に、俺はシャツのボタンを外して、座っていた椅子の背もたれにきれいにかける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5883
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ff63063b:

    # "I know by heart the order of places where he's going to listen to my lungs and heartbeat. I adjust my breathing to be even and deep without even being asked. It's become routine now, for both of us."
    "ナースが俺の呼吸や心臓の音を聞く時に、聴診器を当てる場所を俺は覚えてしまっている。言われるまでもなく、呼吸が深く規則正しくなるよう調整する。今ではこれが、俺たち２人にとってのお決まりの段取りだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5885
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_52844129:

    # "It's funny, this is pretty much the only time in one's life when you really concentrate on breathing and nothing else. It has always amused me."
    "面白いよな。ただ呼吸をすることだけにこんなにも集中するのは、人生の中でもこんなときくらいだろう。聴診のたびにそのことが楽しいと思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5887
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1d8005c6:

    # "The nurse lifts the cold steel stethoscope from my chest and places it a few inches lower, listening again. The contact of the metal makes me flinch on reflex, even though I was expecting it."
    "ナースは俺の胸から冷たい金属の聴診器を離すと、今度は数センチ下に当てて、また音を聞く。構えていても、金属が触れると反射的に体がびくりと動く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5892
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_5e0ad31c:

    # "He furrows his brow, but I can't tell if it's because he's unhappy or if he's trying to pick something specific out among the complex multitude of irregularities in my heartbeat."
    "ナースは眉間にしわを寄せるけど、なにか不満があるのか、それとも俺の心臓のあれやこれやの複雑な不規則さから何か特定のものを切り分けようとしているのか、俺にはわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5894
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_46d08a90:

    # hi "Is there something wrong?"
    hi "どうかしましたか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5896
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_83ffa8d2:

    # nk "Please don't talk."
    nk "ちょっとしゃべらないで"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5898
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1c3928c9:

    # "I shut up and become more anxious. The nurse is nice, but I can't help disliking these mandatory checkups. I wonder if I'm going to end up hating all medical appointments from now on because of these."
    "俺は黙ると、余計に心配になってくる。ナースはいい人だけど、この強制的な検査はどうしても好きになれない。これのおかげで、これから先の病院の予約が全部嫌いになるんじゃないかと思う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5903
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_d1512851:

    # "He finally lifts the circular metal plate from my chest, allowing me to talk again."
    "ナースはやっと丸い金属のプレートを俺の胸から離すと、また話をさせてくれる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5908
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_b4a4c732:

    # nk "Everything seems to be fine. Are you feeling all right yourself?"
    nk "どこも悪いところはなさそうだね。自分では調子がいいと思う？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5910
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_0d54728c:

    # hi "I suppose. I was out yesterday when it was raining, and yeah, I really felt a bit under the weather in the morning. Maybe I caught a cold."
    hi "そうですね。俺も昨日、雨のなか出歩いてたから、確かに朝はけっこう具合が悪かったです。風邪ひいたのかも"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5915
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_c91560b1:

    # nk "Were you with Emi? She came down with a cold, too. My people told her to stay in bed for a day or two."
    nk "笑美ちゃんと一緒だったりした？　あの子も風邪をひいちゃってね。保健師から１日２日寝てるように言われてたよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5917
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ba744dec:

    # hi "Really? I mean, I was with her but I didn't know she got sick."
    hi "ほんとですか？　というか、昨日は笑美も一緒だったんですけど、体調を崩したなんて知らなかった"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5919
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_0b6a89a1:

    # "I guess it was a dumb thing after all, for her to go out in the rain like that."
    "やっぱりばかな話だったんだろうな、あんな雨のなか出かけるなんて。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5924
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_12640c6f:

    # nk "Yeah. Well, let's put that aside. Everything seems to check out for you, but remember to be careful."
    nk "そうなんだ。まあそれは置いといて、何も異常はなさそうだけど、ちゃんと気をつけるようにね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5926
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_cb05dfc5:

    # hi "Of course. I really don't want to go back to the hospital."
    hi "もちろんですよ。また病院に戻るのはほんとに嫌ですから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5928
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a47e18a7:

    # "He catches something - maybe repressed terror, I don't know - in my voice and glances up from some papers he was looking at."
    "ナースは俺の声色から何かを感じ取ったようだ。押し殺された恐怖だろうか。俺にはわからない。書類から目を離し、ちらっと上目遣いでこちらを見やる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5933
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_c1fccc61:

    # nk "Hey, don't worry. At this stage, it would take a huge crash in your condition to get you rehospitalized."
    nk "心配するなって。この状態なら、よほど症状が悪化しない限りは再入院なんてことはないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5935
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_37e8f02c:

    # "It doesn't really reassure me, but grumbling about it to him won't make any difference. I quietly take my leave."
    "あんまり安心できないけど、ナースにそれを愚痴ってもなにも変わらない。俺は静かに医務室を出る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5942
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3ca6917a:

    # "Walking along the corridor from the auxiliary building to the main school building, I encounter a young female nurse coming the other way. She smiles at me when we pass by each other."
    "廊下に沿って、副校舎から本校舎に向かって歩いていくと、向かいからやってくる若い女性看護師に会う。すれ違いざまに俺に微笑みかけてくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5950
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_758fca0f:

    # "The lobby is empty of people. No surprise, since classes are still going on. I hear muffled sounds of discussion coming from behind the first floor classroom doors."
    "ロビーには誰もいない。授業はまだ続いているんだから当然か。１階の教室のドアの向こうから、なにかを話し合うくぐもった声が聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5952
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8f4f0716:

    # "I glance at my watch. I'd have to rush to get to my classroom in time, and I don't feel like going to class anyway, so I decide to climb up to the roof and have an extra-long lunch break."
    "俺は腕時計をちらっと見る。教室までは急がないと時間に間に合わないし、どうせ授業に出る気分じゃないので、俺は屋上に上がって長めの昼休みをとることにする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5954
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_f80f96fb:

    # "Emi promised she'd bring something for me today but if she's sick, that's probably not going to happen. I'm not feeling hungry anyway, so it's all the same."
    "笑美が昼食を用意してくれる約束だったけど、風邪をひいてるんじゃだめだろうな。でも別に腹は減ってないから同じことか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5962
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ce783db4:

    # "The climb up the steep stairwell to the roof is oddly liberating, almost like losing weight. I feel satisfaction that it doesn't wind me as badly as it did the first time I came up here."
    "屋上に向かう急な吹き抜け階段を上っていると、体重が軽くなっていくような、奇妙な開放感を感じる。初めてここに上がってきたときほど、息が切れなくなっていることに満足する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5964
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_552a32b4:

    # "I push open the squeaky door at the top and step into sunlight."
    "登りきったところできしむドアを押し開けて、日差しのなかに踏みだす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5971
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_098e4dce:

    # "The chain link fence allows for a grand view over the treetops, all the way to the gray silhouettes of downtown, further away."
    "金網のフェンス越しに木々の向こうの、遥か遠くの繁華街の灰色のシルエットまでの絶景を望むことができる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5978
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_cfdadc92:

    # "The dreary weather of yesterday is just a memory now. The silvery blue sky seems to be a mere arm's reach away."
    "昨日の陰鬱な天気はもう過去の記憶に過ぎない。銀色がかった青い空は、ちょっと手を伸ばせば届きそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5980
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_afaf2dd6:

    # "I forget for a moment that I'm in a bad mood. The warmth of the sun soaks into my bones, making me drowsy and lazy instead."
    "気分が沈んでいるのを少しのあいだ忘れられる。代わりに、日差しの温かさが骨にまで染みてきて、眠気と気だるさに襲われる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5986
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_f4e3115d:

    # "The bells ring for lunch break, startling me back into reality."
    "昼休みのチャイムが鳴ると、俺ははっとして現実に引き戻される。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5988
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_73dc5e64:

    # "Soon afterwards, the quad below me bursts into life. Students pour out of the doors down on the ground floor, intent on enjoying lunch at the quad and the lush gardens in this perfect weather."
    "その後すぐ、急に下の広場が活発になる。生徒たちは１階のドアから外にあふれ出し、この絶好の天気の下で、広場や緑に覆われた庭で昼食をとるのに夢中だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5990
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a71a6595:

    # "When I hear the door to the stairwell being pushed open, I don't bother turning to see who it is."
    "階段へのドアが押し開けられるのを耳にするけど、俺はわざわざ誰が来たのか見ることはしない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5992
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a27a7b71:

    # "The intruder starts coming towards me with uneven footsteps. The little riverstones the roof is covered with rattle and crunch underfoot."
    "侵入者は俺のほうに向かって不揃いな足取りで近づきはじめる。屋上に敷き詰められている小さい石が、その足元でがらがら、じゃりじゃりと音を立てる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:5999
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_540bddd7:

    # "The footsteps stop a few feet behind me, followed by a silence. I look upwards, into the glowing eye of the sun, absorbing its warmth with my whole body."
    "俺の数十センチ後ろで足音は止まって、沈黙が続く。俺は上を見上げて、赤々と輝く太陽に向き合い、全身でその暖かさを受け止める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6001
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_54db87eb:

    # rin "What are you doing?"
    rin "なにしてるの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6011
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_d038b878:

    # "I turn around out of courtesy at her first words, to behold the slim, awkward figure of Rin Tezuka. She looks very much like herself today, too. Her hair is maybe a tad messier than usual, as if she just got out of bed."
    "その第一声を聞いて、俺は手塚琳の細くて不恰好な姿を拝むために、礼儀正しく振り向く。 今日の琳も実にいつもの琳らしい。髪がいつもよりもちょっとだけ乱れているかもしれない。まるでベッドから起きたばかりみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6013
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_46cbea2f:

    # "She stands with her weight shifted onto one foot, looking at me with mild curiosity, as if I were something in a store's display window."
    "琳は片足に体重をかけてその場に立っていて、俺が店のショーケースにでも並んでいるかのように、軽い好奇心で俺を見ている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6015
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3dffdb2b:

    # hi "I don't know. Just spacing out, I guess."
    hi "さあな。ぼーっとしてただけだよ、たぶん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6017
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_0583026f:

    # hi "What about you?"
    hi "お前はなにしてるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6022
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ccebd45d:

    # rin "Emi promised food. We usually eat here."
    rin "笑美とご飯の約束。いつもここで食べてるんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6024
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3d573fdc:

    # hi "I'm afraid you're going to be disappointed. I heard Emi came down with a cold."
    hi "がっかりしないといいんだけどな。笑美なら風邪ひいたってさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6029
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_85c8758b:

    # rin "Oh. I guess that makes sense. She wasn't in class."
    rin "あーらら。まあ納得はいくけどね。授業にも出てなかったし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6031
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a486a105:

    # hi "It's not that common to get a cold in June though. You don't think she went running at the track afterwards like she said? The rain just kept going."
    hi "６月のこの時期に風邪ひくなんて珍しいけどな。笑美はあのあと、ほんとうに運動場に走りにいったのか？　ずっと雨が降ってたのに"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6036
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_cce2efb5:

    # rin "Probably."
    rin "たぶんね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6038
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_21ceee75:

    # hi "In the rain?"
    hi "雨のなかで？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6040
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_2bba3024:

    # rin "In the rain."
    rin "雨のなかで"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6042
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_5dd9cca7:

    # "That sounds like a bit too much for just keeping up with training regime. Emi is a hard-headed one, though, so I can see her running in the downpour just because she 'had to.'"
    "トレーニングメニューをこなし続けるためにそこまでするのは、やりすぎな気がする。笑美も頑固だから、とにかく『やらなきゃいけない』ってだけで、土砂降りのなか走ってるところが目に浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6044
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_bd7840cc:

    # hi "Well, that's obviously overdoing it. Probably why she came down with that cold, too."
    hi "まあ、どう見てもやりすぎだよな。だから風邪なんかひいたんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6046
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3a336db8:

    # hi "But I guess it's kinda cool."
    hi "でも、なんだかカッコいいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6051
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_0be871b4:

    # rin "Speaking of that, I'm not feeling well either. I…"
    rin "そういえば、私もなんだか具合悪いや。私ね……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6058
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_27104c7c:

    # rin "ACHOO!"
    rin "へっくしょん！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6062
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_6ca82ceb:

    # "Rin sneezes pretty hard, failing to stop it in time. She cranes her head down to wipe her nose on her shoulder, so deciding that would be too unladylike I pull out my handkerchief and hold it to her nose."
    "琳はこらえきれずに派手なくしゃみをする。肩のところで鼻をぬぐおうとして首を曲げるので、さすがにみっともなさすぎると思って、俺はハンカチを引っ張りだして鼻のところにあてがってやる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6067
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_88be6b14:

    # hi "Here. Bless you."
    hi "ほら。お大事にな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6072
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8724c482:

    # rin "Danks."
    rin "ありがど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6074
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a99a7c91:

    # "She clears her nose and I dab the handkerchief gently on it, wiping it clean."
    "琳が鼻をかむと、俺はハンカチをやさしくたたいて周りを拭いてやる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6076
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_119cd5ee:

    # "Her nose is really cute. Oddly enough it's probably the girliest part of Rin's face. I think I'm blushing a little, but Rin doesn't notice."
    "琳の鼻はほんとうに可愛い。変な話、きっと琳の顔のなかではいちばん女の子らしい部分だ。自分が少し赤面してる気がするけど、琳は気づいていない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6081
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_57460ad3:

    # rin "Thanks - I think I might be coming up or down with something, too. Like I was saying."
    rin "ありがとう。私もなんか病気になっちゃうかも。さっき言ったみたいに"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6083
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_528ea70e:

    # hi "Hope not."
    hi "そうならないといいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6088
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_b2ec0df6:

    # "Rin doesn't seem to be to bothered about eating, so despite the lack of Emi-provided lunch, we stay up on the rooftop. She comes over and stands next to me, right up against the fence, looking into the same abstract distance as I am."
    "琳は食事のことは気にしていないみたいで、笑美の弁当がおじゃんになっても俺たちは屋上にいつづける。琳は近づいてきて俺の隣に来ると、フェンスの真正面に立って、俺と同じようにぼんやりと遠くを眺める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6090
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_439b01c5:

    # "Nobody else seems to be coming around to intrude upon this calmness, either. It's quiet and peaceful."
    "俺たちの他には誰も、この場所を訪れて平穏を破ろうとする人はいないようだ。ここは静かで平和だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6098
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_71d21036:

    # "What does one do on a lunch break if not eat?"
    "昼食をとらないなら、昼休みはなにをすればいいんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6100
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_e6666841:

    # "It turns out that, between the two of us, we don't really know. Fortunately, passing time is an activity that manages itself just fine."
    "結局俺たちは、２人そろってそれがわからない。幸い、ただ暇をつぶすというのは何もしなくてもうまくいくので、問題ない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6102
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_85a6c26d:

    # "Even though there's no conversation to fill the silence between the passing seconds, no pointless activities like cloud-gazing to spend upon the minutes between now and then, time marches on relentlessly."
    "過ぎゆく数秒の合間の沈黙を満たすような会話も、雲の観察みたいな現在と未来の間の数分を費やすための無意味な行動もしないけど、それでも時間は容赦なく過ぎていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6104
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_6f2e7376:

    # "I keep checking the time on my watch, then decide it's a dumb thing to do. Instead, I try to hold out for as long as possible before I check it again. Maybe I can hold out for six or seven minutes."
    "俺は何度も腕時計を見るけど、意味のないことをしているなと思う。代わりに、なるべく長い間時計を見ないようにしてみる。６、７分は耐えられるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6109
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_cadefd22:

    # "Rin remains silent, idly looking up at the cerulean expanse above us."
    "琳はいまだに黙り込んでいて、ぼんやりと紺色の上空を見上げている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6111
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_79d9dee7:

    # "I wonder why, more often than not, we don't speak much. She said that she doesn't like speaking because of her perceived difficulties with expressing herself properly."
    "どうしてだろう、俺たちはたいていの場合、あまり会話をしない。琳は自分自身をきちんと表現するのが難しいと自分で思っているから、話をするのが好きじゃないと言っていたけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6113
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_b9cf993f:

    # "As for me, I think I just got sucked into the habit at the hospital, where I spent such a long stretch of time never really talking to anyone."
    "俺からすれば、俺はただ病院にいたころの癖に飲み込まれただけだ。あんなにも長い時間、誰ともまったく話すことのなかったころの。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6115
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a605ae4b:

    # "Most of the time I feel comfortable about this quiet mood. And even when I get the feeling that I have to break the silence, it's always so difficult to come up with something to talk about when it's with Rin."
    "大体の場合、俺はこの静かな雰囲気を心地よいと感じる。そしてこの沈黙を破らなきゃいけない気がしたときでさえ、琳相手に話すべきことを考えつくのはあまりにも難しい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6117
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_cb9cd256:

    # "She and I are on such different wavelengths that nothing seems to be on common ground."
    "琳と俺はまるっきり考え方が異なっている。共通点が何もない気がする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6119
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_89c88dc7:

    # hi "What is it that you like about the sky so much?"
    hi "なんでそんなに空が好きなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6124
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_02dbf055:

    # "She turns to me, her eyes dark and serious."
    "琳が俺のほうを向くと、その目は暗く真剣だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6129
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_912d5d3e:

    # rin "Sky is the only thing that is perfect."
    rin "空は唯一の完璧なものなんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6134
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1a1c6d75:

    # rin "I know it. You could say I'm an expert of sky if you wanted. And I am even if you didn't want to. A sky expert."
    rin "私にはわかるんだ。私のこと、空の達人って呼んでくれてもいいよ。呼ばなくてもそうだけど。空の達人だよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6136
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_9c6f1449:

    # rin "It's always different, but it's always perfect also when it's different."
    rin "いつも見え方は違うけど、違ってても完璧なんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6145
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_02cc049d:

    # "I follow her gaze up into the boundless blue expanse, thinking of her words."
    "俺は広大な青い空を見上げる琳の視線を追うと、その言葉について考える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6147
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_2ef60a0c:

    # hi "Have you ever wanted to be something different?"
    hi "なにか違うものになりたいと思ったことってないか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6149
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_b59915f9:

    # rin "It wouldn't be so bad to be the sky."
    rin "空になるっていうのもいいかもね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6151
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ef0dbe44:

    # hi "No, I mean, someone else, someone different. To go to a normal school like everyone else, not have to worry about stuff…"
    hi "そうじゃなくて、つまりさ、ほかの誰かだよ、違う誰か。普通の学校に行けるようになるとか、あれこれ心配する必要がなくなるとか……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6153
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_bd837947:

    # rin "What stuff?"
    rin "あれこれって？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6155
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_6a9937f6:

    # "I try to find the right words for a moment, but can't manage to form a sentence that I'd be comfortable with actually using."
    "しばらく適切な言葉を探してみるけど、実際に気兼ねなく口にできる言葉を組み立てることができない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6157
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_15b65e57:

    # hi "Man, I don't really want to say it aloud."
    hi "ったく、こんなこと口に出して言えるかよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6159
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_73585fa5:

    # rin "Try. I'm not so good at mind reading."
    rin "言ってみなよ。読心術はあんまり得意じゃないから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6166
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_2c07280e:

    # hi "Don't you ever want to not be disabled?"
    hi "障害なんかなければいいのにって思ったことないか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6168
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3b191ae2:

    # "She thinks about this and then shakes her head, frowning."
    "琳は考え込むと、しかめ面をして頭を振る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6173
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_d853c451:

    # rin "That's a hard question. I don't know what to say."
    rin "難しい質問だね。なんていえばいいのやら"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6175
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8d2a2019:

    # hi "It's okay if you don't say anything."
    hi "別に答えなくてもいいんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6177
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_30599372:

    # hi "For some reason, I'm just so unsatisfied with who I am right now that I'm constantly thinking stuff like that. It's pretty hard to admit, but there it is."
    hi "どうも俺は、今の自分がものすごく不満で、おかげでいつもそんなふうに考えちまってるんだ。認めるのは嫌だけど、でも実際そうなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6179
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3cc0719b:

    # "Honestly, I feel relieved about finally saying it aloud to someone, even if it's just Rin."
    "正直、やっとこのことを人に言えたことで安心できた気がする。その相手が琳一人であっても。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6187
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a360150e:

    # rin "I think I want to be different, sometimes. I've thought about changing myself lately, but it's a bit scary, like walking backwards with your eyes closed."
    rin "私、他のものになりたいって思うことはあるよ、ときどきね。最近は自分を変えたいって考えたりするけど、でもちょっと怖いんだ。目を閉じて後ろ向きに歩くみたいに"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6192
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_69a3b380:

    # rin "The difficult part is to know where your toes are not pointing. I mean, directions."
    rin "なにが難しいって、つま先がどこを向いていないのか把握することなんだ。つまりさ、歩いてる方向をね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6197
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ca624994:

    # rin "Even if I don't do anything, I would never stay the same."
    rin "何もしなくたって、私は決して同じままではいられないけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6202
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3763393f:

    # rin "It's like my old paintings. They are different than what I paint now, because I'm different, but they are still my paintings so there's something same. That's really strange."
    rin "私が昔描いた絵みたい。いま描いてるのとはまた違うんだ。私が違うから。それでも私の絵ではあるから、やっぱりどこか一緒。変だよね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6207
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a6726314:

    # rin "I am different every day, but I'm still me every day. Who am I then?"
    rin "私は毎日変わってるけど、それでも私は毎日私なんだ。じゃあ今の私は誰？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6209
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_50091291:

    # hi "Is that a riddle?"
    hi "なぞなぞか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6214
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_e22ccec5:

    # rin "If you want it to be. I don't know the right answer though, so you have to come up with it yourself."
    rin "君がそう思いたいならね。ちゃんとした答えはわからないから、答えは自分で決めてね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6216
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_b720495f:

    # hi "Well, it's the sky, isn't it? Going by your definition just now."
    hi "それなら答えは空だ、違うか？　お前のさっきの定義で言えば"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6221
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_557eb9d2:

    # "I actually manage to surprise her by that. Maybe she had already forgotten about it."
    "そのつもりはなかったけど、俺の回答は琳を驚かせる。もう忘れてしまったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6226
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_dac97b59:

    # rin "That's right! But I was thinking about myself when I said that. Very strange."
    rin "正解！　でもさっきそのことを話したときから自分でも考えてたんだ。ほんと変な話"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6231
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_170dcb0a:

    # rin "Could it be that I actually am the sky?"
    rin "もしかして、私は実は空なのかな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6233
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_d8dc2da4:

    # hi "I don't think that's possible. Your logic's a bit off somewhere."
    hi "それは無理だと思うぞ。お前の理屈はなんかずれてるよな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6238
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a23d6fd2:

    # "She looks down and shuts up and I can see she's quickly going over the deduction mentally, seemingly unhappy with the result she finally arrives at."
    "琳は下を向いて黙り込む。急いで頭の中で今の仮説を考え直しているのがわかる。最終的にたどり着いた結論には不満なようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6243
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8068bd34:

    # rin "Yeah, maybe I'm not the sky. Would make sense, I have a hard time knowing what kind of a person I am."
    rin "たしかに、私は空じゃないのかも。それもそうだろうね、自分がどういう人間なのか理解するのに、私自身苦労してるから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6245
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_f417e07e:

    # hi "You're not the only one."
    hi "それはお前だけじゃないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6250
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_40581402:

    # rin "It's like my mind is in some other place than the rest of me."
    rin "まるで私の心がどこかほかの場所にあるみたいだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6252
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_e4e2aec9:

    # hi "Underwater."
    hi "水の中だな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6257
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_d2903701:

    # rin "Yeah. I wonder how it got there."
    rin "そうだね。どうやって入ったんだろうね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6259
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_4c2f4395:

    # "I have no answer, so a brief silence falls between us for a moment. I shift my gaze back to the sky above us."
    "俺は答えられず、しばらく二人の間に沈黙が落ちる。俺はまた視線を空に戻す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6266
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6269
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_9c58aac5:

    # n "{vspace=60}The last time I really paid much attention to the sky was… I guess it must've been at the hospital. I could only see a thin strip of sky from the window of my room. If I walked up to the windows and pressed my face against the cold glass, the strip became bigger, but not by much."
    n "\n\n最後に本気で空を意識したのは……病院にいたときだったな。病室の窓から細長い空が見えただけだった。窓辺に歩み寄って、冷たいガラスに顔を押し付ければ、細長い空はもっと大きくなったけど、それほど違いはなかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6271
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_94b4b108:

    # n "That sky made me feel sad and lonely, a reminder of the world on the other side. I wonder if there's another world beyond the sky we see from up here on the school's roof, as well."
    n "あの空は俺を哀しく、寂しい思いにさせた。空の向こう側にある世界のことを思い起こさせた。こうやって学校の屋上で見上げている空の向こうにも別の世界があるんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6273
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_95f5a4f7:

    # n "I can't stop comparing life at Yamaku to my hospitalization, but I really should. I'm not there any more."
    n "山久学園での生活と入院生活を比べずにはいられないけど、でもそんなことはもうやめなきゃいけない。俺はもう病院にはいないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6275
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_93edddf7:

    # n "The narrow sky from the window of my hospital room, the faces of the doctors, the faces of my parents. The off-white walls everywhere. Iwanako's letter, echoing the words she never said. They're things of the past now."
    n "病室の窓から見える狭い空、医者の顔、両親の顔。灰色がかったあちこちの壁。本人が一度も口にすることのなかった言葉を繰り返す、岩魚子の手紙。今となってはみんな過ぎたことだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6277
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_c3f30b3b:

    # n "I wish I could forget everything up until now and that time would stop completely. There would be only me, Rin, and the sky, an eternal lunch break on this rooftop. Perfect, unchanging, and forever."
    n "今までのことを何もかも忘れてしまえたら、時間が完全に止まったらいいのにと思う。俺と琳、そして空だけがある。永遠に続く屋上での昼休み。完璧で、変わることなく、終わることもない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6281
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6284
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_a5e3b947:

    # hi "I'm not sure if I like or hate this school."
    hi "この学校が好きなのか嫌いなのかわからないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6286
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_bd053e7a:

    # rin "I could have gone to a normal school if I wanted, but I chose to come here."
    rin "私ね、私が言えば普通の学校にも通えたんだ。でも、私はこっちを選んだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6292
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_7df9d21b:

    # hi "Why?"
    hi "どうして？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6297
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_77391177:

    # rin "I just decided I would. Kind of like melon or plum jelly."
    rin "そうしたかったからだよ。メロンとプラムのゼリーならどっちを選ぶかって話"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6299
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_f26920b3:

    # hi "Do you think it was a good idea?"
    hi "それでよかったと思うか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6301
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_4aa40b80:

    # hi "I mean, there are a lot of good things about this school, but I think there are a few bad things also."
    hi "つまりさ、この学校もいいところはたくさんあるけど、でも悪いところも少しはあるからさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6306
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_b1f1c9df:

    # rin "I know."
    rin "そうだね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6311
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ab454743:

    # rin "I kind of collect people, because they are interesting. People here really are amazing. Most of them. But not all."
    rin "私、いろんな人から聞き集めてるんだ、みんな面白いから。ここの人はみんなすごいよ。だいたいは。でも全員じゃない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6316
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_92cbc45b:

    # rin "Some people can't take it. They hurt too much. It gets really bad sometimes, you know. They hurt."
    rin "耐えられないって人もいるよ。辛すぎるんだって。時には本当にひどくなるんだよね。辛いんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6321
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ed282d18:

    # rin "I wonder if you're like that too? I hope not. I don't like things like that."
    rin "君もそうなのかな？　そうじゃないといいけど。そういうのは好きじゃないからね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6323
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ea49da3e:

    # hi "Hey, I'm not your case study. And I'm not going to give up and die or anything."
    hi "おいおい、お前の事例研究にされてもな。それに、諦めて死のうとしたりしてるわけじゃないって"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6325
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_00b8c1b8:

    # hi "Anyway, I meant more that this place is too distant from the real world."
    hi "とにかく、この学校は現実の世界とはかけ離れてるなって言いたかったんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6330
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1251a1da:

    # rin "What's the real world?"
    rin "現実の世界って？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6332
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1a0216ec:

    # hi "Everything out there. Real people, with normal everyday lives that fit together like a puzzle."
    hi "外のもの全部だよ。現実の人たちが普通の日常生活を送ってて、お互いパズルみたいにかみ合ってる"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6337
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_27cb8156:

    # rin "You don't think we aren't like that? Real people?"
    rin "私たちはそうじゃないっていうの？　現実の人じゃないの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6339
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_20931774:

    # hi "Maybe we aren't. Well, no, we are. I just meant that it feels more like we're the leftover pieces."
    hi "違うかもしれないぜ。まあ、いや、違わないか。俺たちは余ったパズルのピースみたいな感じがするってだけ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6344
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_00846f37:

    # "Rin thinks for a while, her almond-shaped eyes narrowing as she bites her lip a little bit, like a child."
    "琳はしばらく考え込むと、子供のように唇を軽く噛み締めてアーモンドの形をした目を細める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6349
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_29ec4427:

    # rin "Is it hard to be disabled?"
    rin "障害があるって大変なの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6351
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_be079ba4:

    # "Her question earns a dry chuckle from me."
    "琳の質問に俺は乾いた笑いを返す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6353
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_eeb1ec5c:

    # hi "You tell me. You've been in this business a lot longer than I have."
    hi "それを聞きたいのはこっちだよ。お前は俺よりずっと長いことやってるだろ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6358
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_f046f792:

    # "She thinks about that for another while."
    "琳はまたしばらく考え込む。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6363
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8bc95197:

    # rin "I don't really feel that disabled. I mean I do pretty much everything differently, but it's not that hard. I can always practice."
    rin "自分が障害者だって感じたことはあんまりないよ。そりゃ、ほとんどのことは普通の人と違ったやりかたをしてるけど、そんなに難しくないんだよ。練習はいつでもできるからね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6368
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_83118606:

    # rin "I've started to practice food things this year. I think I'd want to learn to cook in a real kitchen someday."
    rin "今年から食べもののことも練習してるんだ。そのうちほんとうの台所で料理ができるようになりたいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6370
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_71bf09d8:

    # hi "That's admirable, but I don't think it's just a state of mind."
    hi "それは立派だよ。でも障害ってのは感じるかどうかの問題じゃないと思うぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6375
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_24061be6:

    # rin "Maybe not to you."
    rin "君にとってはそうなのかもね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6377
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_e09592b0:

    # "I have no good counter to that, so I concede by falling silent. The situation is making me more and more confused."
    "いい反論が浮かばず、俺は黙りこんで降参する。この状況にますます混乱させられる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6379
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8212c609:

    # "I know what I want, but don't know how to reach it. Rin seems to believe she can simply will herself into the shape she thinks she needs to be, but can't decide whether she wants to be a bird or a butterfly."
    "俺は自分が望んでいるものはわかってるけど、どうすればそれに手が届くのかはわからない。 琳は自分が望めば、必要に応じてどんな形にでもなれると信じているけど、鳥になりたいのか、蝶になりたいのかを決めかねているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6384
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_6c09eda5:

    # rin "I think, in the end I'm not really that happy with who I am either, but that doesn't mean I regret being who I am."
    rin "きっとね、結局私は今の自分に満足ってわけじゃないんだけど、今の自分を後悔してるわけでもないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6391
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_9f8e8a9d:

    # rin "That's the thing that's wrong with you, Hisao."
    rin "それが君の悪いところだよ、久夫"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6399
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_20687841:

    # "I've only started to process that rather blunt statement before Rin suddenly hugs me."
    "俺はただ、そのいくぶん無愛想な言葉を解釈しはじめるだけだった。琳が突然抱きついてくるまでは。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6401
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_5edd2f8f:

    # hi "What are you doing?"
    hi "なにしてるんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6403
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_0bf87644:

    # "I've never been hugged by a girl with no arms before. To be honest, it doesn't really, physically feel like a hug. The awkward way she presses her body against mine and the lack of embracing arms makes it feel like she fell on top of me."
    "腕のない女の子に抱きしめられたことなんて一度もない。正直なところ、身体的には本当に抱きしめられている感じはしない。 琳が気まずい形で体を押しつけてくるのと、体を抱く腕がないおかげで、琳が俺の上に倒れ込んだような感覚がする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6405
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_9600e917:

    # "But the warmth of a real hug is still there, and that's how I recognize it for what it is."
    "それでも本当に抱き締められているときの温もりはあるので、それで俺はこの出来事をあるがままに理解する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6412
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_87afa234:

    # rin "I'm hugging you, Hisao."
    rin "ハグしてるんだよ、久夫"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6414
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_2a014120:

    # hi "I know that, but…"
    hi "それはわかってるよ。でも……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6419
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_33027e00:

    # rin "Is it wrong? I thought this is what you're supposed to do."
    rin "なんかおかしい？　こういうときはこうするものだって思ってたけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6424
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_cb4daae3:

    # rin "I'm not really used to this kind of thing. The first time Emi hugged me I got surprised and kicked her in the stomach. I can kick pretty hard so she hasn't been hugging me an awful lot after that."
    rin "こういうことってあんまりしたことないんだ。初めて笑美が私をハグしたときは、びっくりしてお腹蹴っ飛ばしちゃった。私のキックはかなり強いから、それからは笑美もあんまり抱きついてこないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6426
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_3ba2bb6a:

    # hi "It's not wrong. Just, no, it's just me… things are a bit hard for me, for the time being. I can't seem to react properly to anything."
    hi "別におかしくないよ。ただ、いや、俺がおかしいんだ……ちょっと大変なんだ、最近。いろんなことにきちんと返事ができなくなってるみたいで"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6431
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_168c01ee:

    # rin "Really? So it is hard being disabled after all?"
    rin "ほんとに？　じゃあやっぱり障害があるって大変なの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6433
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8c20d62c:

    # "I guess she has me cornered there. I don't have the energy to start arguing against it, but I feel like I have to get something out."
    "琳に追い詰められてしまった。反論する気力もないけど、なにか言ってやらないといけない気持ちになる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6435
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_c65083e6:

    # hi "Well, I… no, it's not hard. I think it's just me overthinking things."
    hi "まあ、俺は……いや、そんなことない。ただ俺が考えすぎてるだけだと思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6437
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_230d189d:

    # hi "I really wish I didn't feel so sorry for myself all the time."
    hi "四六時中、自分を哀れむのをやめられたらいいのにって、ほんとそう思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6439
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ccd77ee4:

    # "I wonder if I always was this fragile or if I became this way after my incident. Nothing had ever truly shaken my world like that before, so there's no telling."
    "俺はいつもこんなに脆かったのか、それともあの発作のあとこうなってしまったのか。本当に俺の世界を揺るがしたものはそれ以前にはなかったから、今となってはもうわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6444
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_503674f2:

    # "Rin presses her cheek against me tightly. I can feel the warmth of her body close against me."
    "琳は俺に頬をぎゅっと押しつける。その体が俺に触れて、温もりが伝わってくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6446
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_da9d3724:

    # "Her body temperature feels really high, as if she had absorbed the sunlight into herself and was now sharing it with me. Or perhaps it's a natural state for her."
    "琳の体温はすごく温かくて、まるで太陽の光を体に取り込んで、それを俺に分け与えてくれているかのようだ。それとも、これが琳の自然の状態なんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6448
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_08a4f92b:

    # "It's the most comforting thing I've felt in a long, long time."
    "こんなにも安らぎを感じるのは、本当に久しぶりだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6453
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_621e6be1:

    # rin "Wow, your heartbeat really does sound really weird. It's like a drunken percussion orchestra."
    rin "わあ。君の心臓、本当に変な音だね。酔っぱらった打楽器のオーケストラみたい"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6455
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_e4036b7f:

    # hi "Please don't say stuff like that. I get very uncomfortable."
    hi "頼むからそういうことは言うなよ。すごく不愉快なんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6457
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_0792ef14:

    # "I laugh at her comment anyway, in an attempt to ease the tension. It sounds a little bit too forced."
    "どちらにせよ、俺は緊張を和らげようとして琳の言葉を笑い飛ばす。少し無理やりに聞こえるけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6459
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_cc302c66:

    # hi "Man, I'm sorry I'm such a mess."
    hi "ったく、ごめんな、なんか俺めちゃくちゃだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6464
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1d428a4a:

    # rin "It's okay. It's the best part of you."
    rin "気にしてないよ。それが君の一番いいとこだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6466
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_ac2c6ae0:

    # hi "Hearing that doesn't make me happy."
    hi "そんなこと言われても嬉しくねえよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6472
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_47e961c6:

    # "She breaks off the hug and settles down. An awkward silence falls upon us like a blanket; me feeling embarrassed about myself and Rin trying to arrange her expression to something she likes."
    "琳は俺から離れると座り込む。気まずい沈黙が毛布のように覆いかぶさってくる。俺は自分が恥ずかしくなり、琳は表情を自分好みのものに変えようとする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6479
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_0f8ac52a:

    # "One last time, I glance upwards."
    "最後にもう一度、ちらりと上を見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6481
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_94b37b4c:

    # hi "This rooftop is really great. It's like I'm just a little bit closer to the sky."
    hi "この屋上は本当にいいな。空に少し近づいてるみたいで"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6483
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_1290a498:

    # rin "I know a better place, but we can't go there on lunch break. I can take you there sometime if you want."
    rin "もっといいところも知ってるけど、昼休みじゃ行けないんだ。行ってみたかったら今度連れていってあげる"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6487
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_614c05ea:

    # "The bells ring for the beginning of the afternoon classes and Rin stands up to make her way downstairs. I don't hurry after her, deciding to stay up here for just a little while longer."
    "午後の授業を知らせるチャイムが鳴ると、琳は立ち上がって階段のほうへ向かう。俺は急いで後を追うことはしないで、もう少しだけここにいることにする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6495
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_8e7e3fe6:

    # hi "Thanks for the hug."
    hi "ハグしてくれてありがとな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6500
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_459eb315:

    # rin "Thanks for not kicking me."
    rin "蹴っ飛ばさないでくれてありがと"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6505
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_f928590d:

    # "After Rin leaves I finally let tears roll down my cheeks and cry for my condition for the first and only time in my life."
    "琳が去ったあと、俺は人生で初めて、そして一度だけ、涙が頬を流れるにまかせて、自分の境遇に泣く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6507
translate jp a2_rin_six_meters_closer_f0a826f5:

    # "Then I cast away that hollow person lying on the hospital bed, forever."
    "そして病室のベッドに横たわるうつろな自分を打ち捨てる。永遠に。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6522
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_0c7a6676:

    # "Two days later, I'm feeling less miserable. I even go for a long, brisk, healthy walk like the nurse recommended, something which I had avoided and dodged with all sorts of excuses earlier."
    "あれから二日後、陰鬱な気分は和らいでいる。今ではナースが勧めたように、速足で長めの健康的な散歩もするようになった。これまではあれこれ言い訳をつけて避けてきたことだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6524
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_dfe75ccf:

    # "I feel more active in class as well, delighting our science/homeroom teacher, Mr. Mutou, with correct and promptly delivered answers."
    "授業中ももっと活発になった気がしている。素早く的確な答えを返して、科学兼担任の武藤先生を喜ばせている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6526
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_32a72467:

    # "The break right now between the two morning classes is too short for any sort of meaningful activity, but too long to just spend it sitting in the classroom and doing nothing."
    "午前の二つの授業の間の休み時間は、何か意味のあることをするには短すぎるけど、ただ教室で机に向かって、何もしないで時間をつぶすには長すぎる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6534
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_1bbb83b4:

    # "Going out into the hallway isn't much better, but flexing my stiffened muscles is a better use of time than letting them get even stiffer by staying seated."
    "廊下に出たところで大した違いはないけど、こわばった筋肉をほぐすのに時間を使うのは、これ以上座り続けてさらに筋肉を凝り固まらせるよりはいい。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6536
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_de58a2a5:

    # "The door of the neighboring classroom door opens and the students of 3-4 emerge to further fill up the already semi-crowded hallway. It seems their teacher kept them in for a few extra minutes."
    "隣の教室のドアが開いて、４組の生徒たちが、すでに人であふれかかっている廊下をさらに埋め尽くさんと出てくる。どうやら向こうの先生は授業を数分延ばしたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6538
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_67787767:

    # "Emi is among them. She notices me noticing her, which almost makes me look away on reflex."
    "そのなかに笑美もいる。俺が笑美を見つけたことに向こうも気づいて、反射的に俺は視線をそらしかける。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6545
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_cab84d38:

    # "I don't, however, and Emi smiles at me as she happily skips towards me past the other students."
    "だけど俺はそのままでいる。笑美は俺に嬉しそうに微笑んで、ほかの生徒たちを通り越して俺のところにスキップしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6547
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_9b081749:

    # "Emi looks pretty energetic, showing no sign of illness whatsoever. It seems she recovered from the cold."
    "笑美はとても元気そうに見えて、病気だったような素振りはまったくない。風邪は治ったんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6552
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_06f44852:

    # emi "Hey! Good morning!"
    emi "おはよう！"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6554
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_030f5290:

    # hi "Nice to see you back on your feet. Feeling better now?"
    hi "元気になったみたいで良かったよ。気分はいいのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6556
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_974dc0ef:

    # "She looks fine to me, but I still feel compelled to ask."
    "俺には良さそうに見えるけど、それでも聞かないといけない気がする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6561
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_44a0dd28:

    # emi "Thanks! And yeah, I do. It was just a cold, nothing serious."
    emi "ありがと！　大丈夫だよ。ただの風邪だもん、大したことないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6563
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_d9d535ec:

    # "Emi laughs confidently, as if to emphasize her condition. I wonder for a moment what would count as serious in Emi's book."
    "笑美は体の状態を強調するかのように、自信満々に笑う。笑美にとって『大したこと』に当たることって一体なんだろう、と俺は一瞬考える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6565
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_97384fe7:

    # "She seems to be eager to put the topic aside, though."
    "ただ、笑美はこの話題から離れたいみたいだけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6570
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_a72ee8ff:

    # hi "Where are you going?"
    hi "どこ行くんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6575
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_afcc772c:

    # emi "Off to Rin's room to see if she's awake yet."
    emi "琳の部屋まで、琳がもう起きてるか見に行こうと思って"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6577
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_6a8698c6:

    # hi "Oh? She skipped the morning class?"
    hi "んん？　琳のやつ、朝の授業をサボったのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6582
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_a4817366:

    # "A sheepish smile emerges on Emi's face and she gets slightly flustered."
    "照れくさそうな笑いを浮かべて、笑美は少しうろたえる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6584
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_02e691fd:

    # emi "Err… not exactly. It seems that she caught the cold that I had."
    emi "うーん……そういうわけじゃないんだ。風邪、うつしちゃったみたいでさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6586
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_05ccd50e:

    # hi "Sorry to hear that. Well, she was out in the rain on Sunday with us, after all. I saw her on Monday and she was feeling a bit under the weather back then too."
    hi "そりゃ大変だ。まあ、日曜に俺たちと雨のなか歩いてたからな。月曜に会ったとき、具合が悪いって言ってたし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6591
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_0ea3a3ff:

    # emi "Yeah. Anyway, I'll ask the nurse for some cold medication to give her if she doesn't get better soon."
    emi "うん。それじゃあナースくんに言って、琳がすぐに良くならなかったときのために風邪薬もらってくるね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6598
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_5ec79a5d:

    # "She leaves for the girls' dorm. I want to go with her to wish Rin well. I want to tell her that I'm better now too, but it doesn't feel appropriate."
    "笑美は女子寮に向かう。一緒にお見舞いに行きたいな。俺も良くなったって伝えたいけど、それは場違いな気がする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6600
translate jp a2_rin_indecision_7661ba13:

    # "An unspecified feeling diverts my thoughts away. Somehow I just can't summon the resolve to go in there. Is this what Iwanako went through when she tried to tell me what she felt?"
    "よくわからない気持ちが考えをそらす。どうもあそこに行く勇気が出ない。岩魚子が俺に気持ちを伝えようとしたときも、そうだったんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6616
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_9627548a:

    # "Even though I'm feeling more energetic, I'm still hesitant about going over there to talk to Rin."
    "元気になったとはいえ、琳のところへ行って話をする、となると躊躇してしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6618
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_750f7d41:

    # "It's not until two days later, on Friday, that I finally gather enough courage to enter the girls' dorm. I ask the first person I meet inside for directions to Rin's room."
    "ようやく女子寮に入る勇気をかき集めることができたのは、それから二日もたった金曜日のことだ。中で最初に出会った人に琳の部屋への道順をたずねる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6622
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_97afac10:

    # "I knock on Rin's unmarked door and wait."
    "琳の部屋の、表札のないドアをノックして待つ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6628
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_18c99880:

    # "After a few seconds of silence I hear something rustling inside the room. I start wondering if maybe I should've brought something for her, like a can of warm coffee or some oranges. I could have peeled them for her. Well, too late now."
    "少しの沈黙のあと、部屋の中から物音が聞こえてくる。なにか温かい缶コーヒーか、みかんでも持ってくるべきだったかと思いはじめる。それを琳にむいてやるんだ。もう遅いけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6630
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_6f38b94f:

    # "The door opens soundlessly - it was already unlocked - and I find myself staring at Rin, who stares back at me."
    "ドアが音もなく開くと――鍵はかかっていなかった――俺は琳を見つめていることに気づく。琳も俺を見つめ返す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6632
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_47a36aa7:

    # "She looks like she just got out of bed, with her hair all messed up."
    "ベッドから起きたばかりのようで、髪がぼさぼさだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6639
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_1280accd:

    # "…and barely any clothes on."
    "……そしてほとんどなにも着てない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6641
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6646
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_a7bd979d:

    # rin "Hellooooo."
    rin "こんちわああ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6650
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_e8bead8c:

    # "There is a strange, stupid-looking smile on Rin's face. I'm not exactly sure why."
    "その顔には間の抜けた、妙な笑顔が浮かんでいる。どうしてかはわからないけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6652
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_c61f2f45:

    # "Rin smiles so rarely that it seems to be out of place every time. Especially so now, given her partially undressed state. Said state makes me feel extremely conflicted about whether or not this was a good idea."
    "琳が笑うことはほとんどないので、実際に目にするといつも場違いな感じがする。こんな半分裸の格好をしている今はなおさらだ。こんな状況なので、はたしてここに来るべきだったのかどうか、俺は激しく葛藤する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6654
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_04e8d61e:

    # "Her cheeks are flushed rose-red, contrasting with the milky-pale complexion of a person who doesn't get enough sunlight. Her forehead looks sweaty, as though she might have a fever."
    "琳の頬は真っ赤になっていて、十分に陽を浴びていない青ざめた乳白色の肌と対照的だ。熱があるみたいで、ひたいに汗をかいている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6656
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_9ce0b847:

    # hi "Um, hi."
    hi "んん、よお"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6661
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_84c4aced:

    # "Now what? I didn't plan anything further than this, and Rin is staring at me with those expectant eyes of hers again."
    "それで？　ここから先は何も考えてなかった。琳はまたなにか期待するような目で俺を見つめている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6663
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_b52ba645:

    # "Something about this situation gives me very strange vibes. Her eyes are even more vacant than usual and she seems to have a hard time focusing them on anything."
    "この状況の何かが、俺をとても妙な気分にさせる。琳の目はいつもよりうつろで、どこにも焦点を合わせられずにいる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6665
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_6396491d:

    # "The lack of clothing is disturbing, but since she herself doesn't seem to be bothered, why should I be?"
    "ほとんどなにも着ていないのが落ち着かないけど、琳がなんとも思ってないなら、俺だって気にする必要はないよな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6667
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_cce8bcc0:

    # "I keep telling myself that."
    "ひたすら自分にそう言い聞かせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6669
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_eae37868:

    # hi "Err, I thought I'd pay you a visit since you haven't been at the art club… and I wanted to talk with you and wish you well."
    hi "えーと、お前が美術部に来ないもんだから、なら俺のほうから来ようと思ってさ……それとお前と話したりとか、早く良くなれよって言いたかったから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6671
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_a13edec0:

    # "Rin doesn't show any sign of recognizing what I just said, making me wonder if she actually understood my words, or if she even heard them."
    "琳は俺の言ったことを理解する素振りも見せないので、本当に俺の言葉がわかってるのか、そもそもちゃんと聞いていたのかさえ怪しくなる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6673
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_1215af9d:

    # "Maybe it's the fever making her groggy; she might've actually been asleep before I came over."
    "熱のせいでもうろうとしてるんだろうか。俺が来るまで寝てたのかもしれないな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6678
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_a61bcc4a:

    # rin "Okay."
    rin "いいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6687
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_188e4bd8:

    # "She turns on her heel and withdraws from the door, walking back inside the small room. From the doorway I can see her walk to her bed and half fall down, half sit down on the messy pile of bedsheets."
    "琳はきびすを返すと、ドアのところから引き下がって、小さい部屋のなかに戻っていく。戸口から琳がベッドへと歩き、乱れたシーツの山に半ば倒れ込み、半ば座るのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6689
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_d49e37e9:

    # "The open doorway seems to be more of an obstacle in my mind than the closed door was, but since Rin doesn't say anything else, I step through it, and into her room."
