translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_2b2f3d20:

    # rin "I probably said stupid things too."
    rin "私もたぶん悪いこと言った"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6978
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_fc2ec18c:

    # rin "It's just sometimes a bit hard to keep my thoughts the way I like them."
    rin "ときどき自分の考えを思った通りに保つのが難しくなるってだけなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6983
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_19c9760f:

    # rin "They are not very straight, at least most of the time."
    rin "きちんとしてないんだよね、たいていの時は"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6985
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_e3a6cb78:

    # rin "Not that I want to have them straight… I just wish they were at least in some shape."
    rin "別にきちんとしててほしいわけじゃないけど……ただなにかの形になってたらいいのにって思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6987
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_1bf58210:

    # rin "Round is fine too. But I need more definition."
    rin "丸もいいよ。でももっとはっきりさせないと"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6992
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_76820e70:

    # rin "My thoughts are very messy."
    rin "私の考えってすごいぐちゃぐちゃなんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:6997
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_f5ef1093:

    # rin "Messy."
    rin "ぐちゃぐちゃ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7009
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_460db745:

    # "She repeats the word melancholically, then flops lying down on her bed and nuzzles her head against her pillow, shutting her eyes."
    "琳は気だるそうに言葉を繰り返すと、ベッドにどさっと倒れこみ、頭をもぞもぞと枕に押し付けて目を閉じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7011
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_3644a735:

    # rin "Enough. Tired. You should go. I'm going to sleep again."
    rin "もういいや。疲れた。そろそろ帰って。また寝るから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7016
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_aff87f6e:

    # "She opens one of her eyes to look at me."
    "片目を開けて俺を見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7018
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_7aa3ac74:

    # rin "Was it you who likes to look at sleeping girls? Or someone else?"
    rin "寝てる女の子を見るのが好きなのって、君だっけ？　それとも他の誰か？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7020
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_6a127921:

    # rin "Maybe there were many of those."
    rin "そういう人っていっぱいいたかも"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7025
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_15d2a524:

    # rin "I can't remember."
    rin "覚えてないや"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7027
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_0dc515b7:

    # rin "You can stay if you want."
    rin "いたかったらいてもいいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7031
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_ce3d561c:

    # hi "No no, I'll leave. I have to… do homework anyway."
    hi "ああいや、戻るよ。どうせ……宿題とかしなきゃいけないし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7038
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_83c27023:

    # "I stand up from the chair and take a step towards the door."
    "俺は椅子から立ち上がると、ドアのほうに向かって踏み出す。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7040
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_286b119b:

    # rin "Wait."
    rin "待って"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7042
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_8adc13a5:

    # "Her request stops me in my tracks, not that I intended to scoot off right away."
    "琳の要求に俺は足を止める。俺もすぐに出ていくつもりだったわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7047
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_776ec858:

    # "I look over my shoulder at the girl lying on her bed, again with the strangest kind of smile on her features."
    "肩越しにベッドに横たわる琳を見ると、またしてもその顔にとびきり奇妙な笑顔が浮かんでいる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7049
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_26f9d43b:

    # "She should smile more often."
    "琳は普段からもっと笑ったほうがいいな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7051
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_6436f5b9:

    # rin "I can walk you to the door."
    rin "見送るよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7056
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_82453a5e:

    # rin "It's the least a gentleman can do."
    rin "紳士のたしなみとしてそれぐらいはね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7061
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_ffd15e86:

    # "Rin giggles like a little kid, making me beyond absolutely certain that she took far too much of her cold medication today."
    "琳は小さい子供のようにくすくす笑う。今日の琳が風邪薬を飲み過ぎたのは、どう考えても間違いないと確信する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7063
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_f571d1da:

    # rin "I have always wanted to say that."
    rin "それ、ずっと言ってみたかったんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7075
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_c550dcd2:

    # "Slowly and with difficulty, Rin first rises to a sitting position again, then she stands up with even more difficulty and more slowly still."
    "ゆっくりと大変そうに、琳はまずもう一度座った姿勢になる。そしてさらにゆっくりと、さらに大変そうに立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7077
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_a966c638:

    # "As if guided by some masculine automation, my eyes instantly lower to the curve of her thighs and the striped panties, at which point my manners force me to lift my gaze back to Rin's eye level."
    "男の本能に導かれたかのように、俺の目は一瞬で琳の太ももの曲線と縞柄のパンティへと下がってしまうけど、俺の良心が視線をむりやり琳の目の高さまで持ち上げる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7079
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_c446b4d6:

    # "It's getting almost too hard to do that."
    "そうするのもあまりに難しくなっていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7081
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_fbf8f278:

    # "Rin is standing, although barely. It looks like she has trouble keeping her usually decent balance; again, probably a side effect of the medicine."
    "琳はやっとのことで立っている。普段はちゃんとしている平衡感覚を保つのが難しいみたいだ。これもたぶん薬の副作用なんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7086
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_89489f93:

    # "She takes an unsteady step towards me, then another smaller one as she notices that it's not a good idea to try to take big steps."
    "琳はふらつきながら俺に一歩歩み寄る。すると大またに歩くのはまずいと気づいて、小さい歩幅でもう一歩近づく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7088
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_29362930:

    # "I feel my muscles tense as I prepare to catch Rin if she falls down."
    "琳が転んだときに受け止めるために身構えると、自分の筋肉が緊張するのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7099
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_8d3688aa:

    # "She manages to take two more steps before she falls against me. To my surprise, neither her downwards momentum nor our slight height difference are able to stop Rin from pressing her heart-shaped lips squarely against mine."
    "琳はもう二歩前に進むと、俺に向かって倒れ込む。驚いたのは、琳は倒れる勢いも、わずかな身長の差も乗り越えて、そのハート型のくちびるを真正面から俺のそれに押し付けてきたことだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7101
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_e50b9402:

    # "As our lips part after a confusing moment of nothing but the taste of… Rin, I look down at her, trying to find some explanation for this bewildering event."
    "琳の味……それ以外には何もない、混乱する瞬間の後、二人のくちびるが離れると、俺は琳を見下ろして、この途方に暮れるような出来事の説明を考え出そうとする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7109
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_d095d57c:

    # "The euphoric smile of a madman broadens on Rin's lips again and—"
    "陶酔したような狂人の笑みが、琳のくちびるをもう一度横に広げて――"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7114
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_8762fc07:

    # rin "I wonder if I will remember this tomorrow."
    rin "これ、明日まで覚えてるかなあ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7116
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_28032cb5:

    # "I am absolutely stumped on how to respond."
    "俺はどう返したらいいのか、さっぱりわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7121
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_e889ee98:

    # "Rin takes a step backwards, separating her body from mine, and making me only now realize that they were even connected in the first place."
    "琳が一歩後ろに下がって体を離すと、そもそも俺たちは最初から触れあっていたんだと気づく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7132
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_f7ad6c54:

    # "The second step is actually a fall backwards, luckily straight onto her bed."
    "二歩目で後ろに倒れ込む。幸いベッドの上にだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7134
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_231ffb8d:

    # "The soft thud Rin's thin body makes against the mattress breaks the silence."
    "琳の細い体がマットレスにぶつかる、やわらかなどさっという音が、沈黙を破る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7139
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_a540fde7:

    # "I move quickly over to her to see if she hurt herself, only to be met with the peaceful face of dreaming."
    "俺はすぐさま駆け寄って、琳がどこか痛めたりしていないか見るけど、安らかな顔をしてまどろんでいるだけだった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7141
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_ff2f4896:

    # "Rin sleeps."
    "眠ってる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7143
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_279fef22:

    # "She is lying diagonally across the bed, somehow managing to have simultaneously fallen asleep while standing up, and fallen down in a way that she didn't injure herself."
    "琳はベッドに斜めに横たわっている。どうやってか、立ったまま眠りに落ちると同時に、うまいこと怪我をしないようにベッドに倒れ込んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7145
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_66487e9c:

    # "Fool's luck."
    "悪運の強いやつだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7150
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_746c90b4:

    # "I tuck Rin in, covering her with the sheets as well as I can."
    "俺は琳をベッドに押し込むと、できるだけ布団をかぶせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7152
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_6e7cc320:

    # "She feels very light, even though I am not that strong."
    "俺もそんなに力はないけど、琳はとても軽く感じる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7159
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_ce26f126:

    # "I stand up to look at her, the oval-shaped face, the dark eyelashes shut against the feverish cheeks, the slender body covered with the pale sheets."
    "立ち上がって琳を見る。卵形の顔、熱っぽい頬にかかる黒いまつ毛、青白い布団に包まれた細い体。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7161
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_ff2f4896_1:

    # "Rin sleeps."
    "眠ってる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7163
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_832a4a4b:

    # "A conflict - no. Conflicts, plural, churn inside of me. I think about calling a nurse to keep an eye on her, but decide against it. After taking one more glance at her peaceful face, I decide that she'll be fine."
    "葛藤が――いや、いくつもの葛藤が、俺の中で渦を巻く。看護師を呼んで琳を見ていてもらおうかと思ったけど、やめておく。琳の穏やかな顔をもう一度見て、きっと良くなるだろうと確信する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7165
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_fcc636bf:

    # "I do pocket the remaining pills, though."
    "ただ、残りの薬は回収させてもらったけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7172
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_0282c706:

    # "I exit the room, and close the door soundlessly behind me."
    "俺は部屋を出ると、後ろ手にドアを静かに閉める。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7174
translate jp a2_rin_signal_interference_0d0bb448:

    # "I exhale deeply, only now realizing I had held my breath for the better part of a minute. Taking a moment to relax, I try to calm down my heart, racing like a jackrabbit."
    "深く息をつくと、ようやく俺は、この一分足らずの間ずっと息を詰めていたことに気づく。その場で少しリラックスすると、ウサギのように速く打ち続ける心臓を落ち着かせようとする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7193
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_da768691:

    # "I had trouble getting to sleep that night, so the next morning finds me exceptionally groggy. I briefly consider skipping class but remind myself that I was supposed to be a stronger person now."
    "その夜はなかなか寝つけなくて、翌朝になるといつも以上にだるく感じる。授業をサボろうか考えるけど、もう俺は強くならなきゃだめなんだと自分に言い聞かせる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7198
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_4d4a171e:

    # "I get up like a good boy and put on my uniform, then make my way to the main school building without eating breakfast."
    "優等生のように起き上がって制服を着ると、朝食はとらないで本校舎のほうに向かう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7203
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_05b54343:

    # "I sit in my seat in classroom 3-3, waving a greeting to Misha and Shizune like I do every morning, and let the day wash over me."
    "３－３の教室の自分の席に座ると、毎朝そうしているようにミーシャと静音に手を振って、一日の流れに身を任せる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7207
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_39dcd7ca:

    # "The afternoon classes are always longer than those in the morning. This is true regardless of whether I count it by the minute or by the number of doodles drawn in my notebooks."
    "午後の授業はいつも午前の授業より長い。時間で計っても、俺がノートに描いた落書きの数で数えても、それは変わらない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7209
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_bad2a4a7:

    # "Today I'm especially distracted, as I keep thinking about Rin."
    "今日は琳のことが頭から離れなくて、なおさら集中できずにいる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7213
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7216
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_a7ad55fe:

    # n "{vspace=150}Did I manage to properly tell her that I want to get better? Did she understand a word of what I was saying?"
    n "\n\n\n\n\nもっと前向きになりたいってことを、俺はちゃんと琳に伝えられたのか？琳は俺の言葉を一言でも理解してたんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7218
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_8cd9bead:

    # n "I think about the kiss we shared and what it means. She was so out of her mind, maybe it means nothing. But we've been getting closer lately. What does that mean?"
    n "交わしたキスと、その意味を考える。琳は相当おかしくなってたし、意味なんてないのかもしれない。でも最近俺たちの距離は縮まってきている。それはどういうことだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7220
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_2d385375:

    # n "{vspace=150}I think about Rin more and more nowadays. I wonder if she thinks about me."
    n "\n\n\nこのごろの俺はますます琳のことばかり考えている。琳も俺のことを考えているんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7224
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7227
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_1214d37b:

    # "The ringing of bells makes me flinch, and then realize that I haven't been paying attention during the latter half of class at all."
    "チャイムが鳴ると俺ははっとして、後半の授業にまったく集中していなかったことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7229
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_611d3859:

    # "I look at the assortment of sketches traveling up and down the margins of my notebook, the only thing I got done in the last hour."
    "書き溜めたさまざまなスケッチが、ノートの余白を上下にのたくっているのを見る。この一時間の間にやったことといえばこれだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7231
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_2f609e60:

    # "Feeling vaguely disappointed in myself, I pack up and get to the hallway."
    "自分に漠然とした失望を覚えながら、俺は荷物をまとめて廊下に出る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7239
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_92a5364e:

    # "Rin is standing right outside the door, her presence stopping me in my tracks as soon as I spot her."
    "琳がドアのすぐ外に立っていて、俺はそれを見つけるなり立ち止まる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7241
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_6a1c126a:

    # "Her posture is relaxed as always, but I suddenly feel like I just ate a crowbar. I'm having a hard time meeting her gaze."
    "琳はいつものようにリラックスした姿勢だけど、こっちは鉄の棒でも飲み込んだかのように硬直してしまう。琳の視線になかなか向き合うことができない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7243
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_6086ef9c:

    # "She doesn't seem to have any trouble looking at me, but those dark eyes are making me feel flustered for no reason."
    "琳はこっちを見るのになんの問題もなさそうだけど、その黒い目は理由もなく俺を動揺させる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7245
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_3cca2612:

    # "It's hard to look straight at her so I turn my face away a little."
    "まっすぐ琳を見ることができなくて、俺はわずかに顔を背けてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7247
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_e6fdf171:

    # "I don't know what one should say in this kind of situation."
    "こういう場合なんていえばいいのかわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7249
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ba1b373b:

    # "Then again, I rarely know what to say to Rin in any given situation."
    "とはいっても、どういう状況であれ琳の前で何を話せばいいかなんてわかった試しもないけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7253
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_fe99ff84:

    # hi "Err… hi."
    hi "あー……よお"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7258
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "やあ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7260
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_54825b27:

    # "I try to get rid of the awkwardness in my voice and invoke a more natural way of speaking. I suddenly worry about where I should put my hands; it feels like they're in the way somehow."
    "自分の声からぎこちない感じを消して、自然に話そうとする。急に手をどこにおいたらいいのか気になってくる。どうも手が邪魔に思えてくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7262
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_5d82fa68:

    # hi "How are you feeling? You were pretty out of it yesterday."
    hi "気分はどうだ？　昨日、すげえだるそうだったぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7267
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_9603dd8a:

    # rin "I'm okay. What do you mean yesterday?"
    rin "大丈夫だよ。昨日って？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7269
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f5e68b5f:

    # hi "You don't remember?"
    hi "覚えてないのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7274
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_15286b70:

    # "She tilts her head to the side like a bird, looking somewhat confused."
    "琳は鳥のように頭を横に傾ける。なんだか混乱してるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7276
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f7cdbaac:

    # rin "Remember what? I have a pretty bad memory."
    rin "覚えてるってなにを？　私、物覚えが悪いからさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7278
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_10e8e888:

    # hi "About yesterday."
    hi "昨日のことだぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7283
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f6d99cc2:

    # rin "What about yesterday?"
    rin "だから昨日のなに？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7285
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_37249444:

    # hi "I came to see you and…"
    hi "俺がお前のところに会いに行ってさ……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7290
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_20c2b069:

    # rin "I don't remember that kind of thing happening."
    rin "そんなことあったっけ、覚えてないや"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7292
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c6141752:

    # "She really doesn't remember? I don't know if this is a good thing or a bad thing, but I feel disheartened all the same."
    "本当に覚えてないのか？　これがいいことなのか悪いことなのかわからないけど、どっちにしろがっかりだな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7297
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_0229b7df:

    # rin "I remember that I promised to show you one place, though. Did that happen for real?"
    rin "もっといいところに連れて行ってあげるって言ったのなら覚えてるけど。あれは現実だったのかな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7302
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_367f869d:

    # rin "Maybe I just think that I remember that and I really don't."
    rin "覚えてると思ってただけで、本当は覚えてなかったのかもね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7304
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_a8651867:

    # hi "No, that was real too."
    hi "いや、それも現実だ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7309
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c0b12ee8:

    # rin "Okay. Do you want to go?"
    rin "そっか。そこ、行ってみたい？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7311
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ae849c9c:

    # hi "Now?"
    hi "今からか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7316
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_be16d51f:

    # rin "Yeah."
    rin "うん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7318
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_753e7b61:

    # hi "Well, sure, why not. Is it far?"
    hi "ああ、もちろん。遠いのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7323
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_70f41190:

    # rin "It's not."
    rin "ううん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7332
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_29652379:

    # "Together, we walk downstairs and then outside. The usual summer day, whirring cicadas and all, greets us. It's immensely hot, and without the air conditioning the classrooms offer, I start sweating immediately."
    "一緒に階段を下って外に出る。いつと変わらない夏の日だ。ジリジリと鳴くセミや、いろいろなものが俺たちを出迎える。とても暑くて、教室と違ってエアコンがないから、俺はすぐさま汗をかいてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7337
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_e07774f2:

    # "We start along the tree-lined pathway that leads towards the dorms."
    "寮に向かう通りを、俺たちは街路樹に沿って歩く。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7339
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f551ed7e:

    # "The cherry trees offer shade, with the sunlight blinking through the holes in the canopy. The light creates a chaotic pattern of shadows dappled with bright places where the beams hit the pavement."
    "桜の木が葉の隙間から陽射しをまたたかせながら影を落とす。光が歩道を照らしながら、不規則なまだら状の模様をつくっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7341
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c98bc3d7:

    # "Rin's eyes are wandering in every direction but mine. I get the feeling that it's intentional."
    "琳の目はあちこちに向けられるけど、俺のほうは見ない。わざとそうしているという気がしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7349
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_2e222a59:

    # "She leads me to the back gate once again, taking us through it and into the forest beyond. As before, the dropping temperature and the drastically reduced levels of light make it feel like the forest is swallowing us into its cavernous belly."
    "琳は俺をまたあの裏門まで連れていって、２人そろってその向こうに広がる森に入り込む。 前と同じように、森の中の涼しさと、ぐっと弱まった陽射しのおかげで、まるで森が俺たちをその巨大な腹に飲み込んでしまったような感じがする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7354
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_9dd0c301:

    # "We head uphill along the same path as last time, snaking around trees and boulders, over roots and rocks, past wild undergrowth. Birds sing somewhere in the woods, soloists for the humming background music of the treetops."
    "木々や大きな岩を通り抜け、木の根や石を乗り越え、うっそうとした下生えを進みながら、この前と同じ道のりをたどって丘の上を目指す。 森のどこかで鳥たちが鳴いている。木の上でハミングのようなＢＧＭを奏でるソリストたちだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7359
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ece932ef:

    # "We go past the small clearing with the big maple that is now called the Worry Tree. The climb steepens, then becomes easier again."
    "今は心配の木と呼ばれている大きなカエデの木のある空間を抜ける。急な坂道を上ると、また平坦な道になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7364
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_eae3e2f5:

    # "I have to stop a few times to catch my breath, then hurry after Rin who doesn't stop to wait for me."
    "俺は息をつくために何度か立ち止まらないといけなくて、でも琳はそのたびに足を止めて待ってなんかくれないから急いで追わないといけない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7366
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_24e18fbf:

    # "Soon, I'm out of breath again."
    "そしてまた息が切れる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7374
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_3d6924b6:

    # "Suddenly the trees end, and we emerge from the forest. The boundary of the woods is sharp and abrupt, as though a line had been drawn to mark it."
    "とつぜん木々が途切れて、俺たちは森から抜け出る。森の境界線は、線が引かれたかのようにはっきりしていて、そして唐突だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7376
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_b328cd10:

    # "The hill continues to climb up a little further ahead, but from here to the top it's a rocky meadow, patches of grass and small bushes that look like they are growing straight from the rock."
    "丘はもう少し遠くまで続いているけど、ここからだと岩の多い草地に見える。草や茂みがまるで岩からそのまま生えているみたいに辺りを覆っている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7387
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_00e96c66:

    # "We soon reach the highest point, with the forest behind us and the view to every direction opening in front of our eyes."
    "ほどなく、俺たちは一番高いところにたどり着く。森は背後にあって、どの方向にも景色が目の前に広がっている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7389
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c275047d:

    # "The city lies far below and away, lazily reveling in the quiet afternoon mood."
    "はるか眼下の遠くに街があって、のんびりと静かな午後の空気を満喫している。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7391
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_7cd4cdea:

    # "You can see pretty far from here, and the vista is beautiful. I wonder how high up we are."
    "かなり遠くまで見渡すことができる。ほんとうにきれいな景色だ。どれくらい高いところまで来たんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7393
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ade27e71:

    # "I breathe the fresh air and feel my heart rate slowly going back down. I think I might've overdone it a bit; a higher pulse is dangerous for me. I'm feeling fine right now, though."
    "俺は新鮮な空気を吸い、心臓の鼓動がゆっくりと落ち着いていくのを感じる。今日は心臓に負担をかけすぎたな。脈が早くなるのは危険だ。今はもう大丈夫だけど。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7395
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_44de2fa5:

    # "The wind picks up, ruffling my hair and causing the trees below us to sway. It makes the grass undulate in waves as the breeze sweeps across the hilltop."
    "風が強くなってきて、俺の髪は乱れ、下にある木々が揺れる。そよ風が丘を吹き抜けると、草が波のようにうねる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7397
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_d53b5c0a:

    # "Sun shines from the open skies upon us, a few clouds passing by to shadow it. What was painful heat before is now gentle warmth."
    "広々とした空に太陽が輝いていて、いくつか雲が通り過ぎてそれをさえぎる。身を焦がすようだった暑さは、今では穏やかな暖かさだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7399
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_83b0b4e6:

    # "I take a good look around. The hilltop is pretty in the way nature often is, unplanned harmony found in the natural arrangement of things."
    "俺はこの景色をじっくりと見回す。この丘の頂上は、自然がたいていそうであるようにきれいだ。さまざまなものが自然に配置されたときに見られる、偶然の調和だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7401
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_d58dc6a6:

    # "The most striking feature is the abundance of small yellow flowers. They're literally everywhere in this small meadow. I can't help commenting on it."
    "一番目を引くのは、たくさんの小さな黄色い花だ。この小さな草地の、文字通りあらゆる場所に咲いている。俺は一言言わずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7403
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_fa8e435e:

    # hi "Wow. A lot of flowers."
    hi "へえ。たくさん咲いてるな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7409
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_cac2e220:

    # rin "Yeah. Do you know this kind? They will fly away."
    rin "うん、これ、なんだかわかる？　飛んでいくんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7411
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_bc28214e:

    # hi "Yeah. Dandelions."
    hi "ああ。たんぽぽだな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7416
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_5d1db3ac:

    # rin "There are not many of them at the school, because they cut the grass so often. Nobody cuts grass up here."
    rin "学校にはそんなに咲いてないんだ、芝生はいつもすぐ刈っちゃうから。ここなら誰も刈らないしね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7418
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f07a672d:

    # "The fragile-looking flowers will soon turn white and fluffy like cotton, and the wind will carry their seeds away."
    "はかなげな花はやがて白い綿毛になって、風が種を遠くまで飛ばす。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7427
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_1314e627:

    # "I crouch down to look at one tiny yellow flower, silently basking in the sunlight. There's not a hint of white yet, so it's still waiting for its time to be fulfilled."
    "俺はしゃがみこんで、静かに陽の光を浴びている、ひとつの小さなたんぽぽを見る。まだ白い色はどこにも見あたらないので、まだその時が来るのを待っているんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7429
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_4ce38942:

    # "I brush my fingers against the delicate yellow petals, feel the soft texture in my fingertips. It feels nostalgic somehow. I hear Rin approaching from behind and stand back up to face her."
    "繊細な花びらに指で触れると、やわらかな感触を指先に感じる。なんだか懐かしい。後ろから琳が近づいてくるのが聞こえて、俺は立ち上がって琳に向き合う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7439
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_e60db485:

    # "She has a weird look on her face."
    "琳は妙な表情をしている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7441
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_2260f6bc:

    # hi "Something on your mind?"
    hi "なにか悩みでもあるのか？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7446
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_1aff2323:

    # rin "I don't know. It's just…"
    rin "わかんない。ただね……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7450
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ea32318a:

    # rinbabble "You just look so sad all the time and become upset so easily and it makes me confused and I really don't remember much about yesterday except that you came to my room and that's why it might be because of me so if it's because of me I think that I know why, it's because people don't really like talking to me and you might be the same and that would be sad I know that people and I'm talking about others than Emi too always say that I'm strange and that I talk strange things so I thought I'd try not to say strange things but that just makes me think more and new and strange and colorful that was not a good word but maybe you understand anyway and odd things so if I want to say something I don't really know how and then the words are not the same as the thoughts because something goes wrong on the way out but it's not like the thoughts are really the thing I should be saying it's more like the idea of the thought or the feeling of the idea or the idea of the feeling but it's not really any of those either because there is no word for it unless I invent a new one which is not really useful so I've been thinking if doing things is better than saying so maybe because yesterday I took those pills and I was feeling a little strange I might have done something that I shouldn't besides I don't even know if it would be any better if I just could say the thought there is no telepathy that's real telepathy isn't there I think it'd be terrible and useful at the same time but right now I wouldn't mind because misunderstanding is so easy but understanding is not and I thought—"
    rinbabble "君はいつもそんなに悲しそうですぐ怒るから私わけわかんなくて君が私の部屋にきたこと以外は昨日のことあんまり覚えてなくてだからそれはたぶん私のせいでもし私のせいなら理由はわかってる、誰も私と話なんかしたくなくて君もたぶん同じでそれが悲しいんだみんなっていうか笑美以外の人たちのことだけどいつも私が変だとか私が変なこと話すっていうから私も変なこと言わないようにしてるんだけどそのせいでもっと新しくて変でカラフルなこと考えちゃう今のは言葉が良くなかったかなでも君ならわかってくれるかもそれとおかしなこともだから何かを言いたいって思ってもどうすればいいのかわかんないんだそれと言葉は考えとは同じじゃないんだだって口で言うときにおかしくなっちゃうからでも考えが本当に自分の言うべきことってわけじゃないんだむしろ考えの考え方とか考え方の感じ方とか感じ方の考え方だけどそのどれでもないんだなぜって私が新しい言葉を思いつくまでそれをあらわす言葉はないんだから実際にはあんまり役に立たないけどだから考えてるんだ口で言うより行動する方がいいんじゃないかってつまり昨日私があの薬を飲んでちょっと変な気分だったからやっちゃいけないことをしちゃったのかもだいたい本当に考えを口に出して言えたとしてもそれがほんとにいいのかなんてわかんないよテレパシーなんてないんだからつまり本物のテレパシーなんてないあったら恐いけど便利だよねでも今は気にしないよだって思い違いするのはすごく簡単だけどわかり合うのは簡単じゃないからそれで私――"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7458
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_e10eda3e:

    # "I grasp her shoulder and squeeze hard to make her stop. I don't have the capacity to take all that in at once."
    "俺は琳を止めるために、その肩をつかんで強く握りしめる。これじゃ一度で理解できる限度を超えてる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7465
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_162a7154:

    # "Rin shuts up instantly."
    "琳は即座に押し黙る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7467
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_4bf29cdb:

    # hi "Take a breath."
    hi "落ち着けよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7469
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_bf0b41f9:

    # hi "I'm not upset. Why would I be? I'm just a little confused, but it's all right."
    hi "別に怒っちゃいないぞ。そんなわけないだろ？　ただちょっと混乱してるけど、別に大丈夫だよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7471
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_b69da36d:

    # "I wonder if I was making a face she doesn't like again. I guess I've been thinking about yesterday all the time. Maybe I looked weird. I wish I had a mirror with me at all times."
    "また琳の嫌がるような表情をしてしまったんだろうか。ずっと昨日のことばかり考えていたみたいだ。それで妙な顔に見えたのかもしれない。いつも鏡を持ち歩いていればよかったな。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7473
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_e6cb0a39:

    # hi "No need to get it all said at once. I'll listen, even if you talk slower."
    hi "一度に全部言わなくたって大丈夫だよ。ゆっくりでもちゃんと聞くから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7478
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_8486b9e4:

    # rin "It just came out. Sorry. I'm okay now. I just wanted to say something. I didn't mean that much."
    rin "止まらなくなっちゃったんだ。ごめん。もう大丈夫。ただ、言いたいことがあっただけで。あんなにたくさん言うつもりじゃなかった"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7485
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f047e657:

    # rin "It's weird, isn't it?"
    rin "おかしいよね？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7487
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_975d9a82:

    # "She looks at me with a surprisingly timid expression, one that I haven't seen before. I can't help but laugh a little."
    "琳は驚くほど臆病そうな表情で俺を見る。そんな顔をするのは見たことがない。俺は思わずちょっと笑ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7489
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c3f7c66a:

    # hi "Yeah. It's weird."
    hi "ああ、おかしいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7491
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c103d455:

    # hi "You are a pretty weird person but there's nothing wrong with that."
    hi "お前はすごく変わったやつだけど、でもそれは別に悪いことじゃない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7493
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_0b33511e:

    # hi "Thanks for being worried about me, but I'm going to get better. I told you that yesterday, but I guess you don't remember that either."
    hi "心配してくれてありがとな。でもこれからは前向きになるから。それも昨日話したけど、やっぱり覚えてないんだろうな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7498
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_63a91b46:

    # rin "I don't. I wonder what else I forgot. Hopefully nothing important like my own name. That'd be terrible."
    rin "覚えてないや。ほかにもなにか忘れてるのかな？　大事なことは忘れてないといいんだけど、自分の名前とかさ。大変なことになっちゃう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7500
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_133253a1:

    # hi "Well, you kissed me."
    hi "お前、俺にキスした"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7505
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ee8add10:

    # rin "I did?"
    rin "私が？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7507
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f665380c:

    # hi "Yeah, you did. On the lips."
    hi "ああ、お前がだ。口と口とでさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7509
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_18f9b365:

    # "I try to sound as matter-of-fact as I can, but I worry that I might be blushing again."
    "なるべく事務的に話そうとするけど、また顔が赤くなってるんじゃないかと心配になる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7514
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_d08e9626:

    # rin "Did you kick me?"
    rin "私のこと、蹴っ飛ばした？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7516
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_356498d7:

    # hi "No! Why would I do that?"
    hi "まさか！　なんでそんなことしなきゃいけないんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7521
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_65e130b1:

    # rin "Then it's all good, right? It's okay, right? I didn't forget my name."
    rin "ならよかった、でしょ？　問題ないよね？　名前も忘れてないし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7523
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_f796cc09:

    # hi "Yeah, it's okay."
    hi "そうだな、問題ない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7525
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_e93c53f1:

    # "I wish I was more suave so that I could come up with a better follow-up to that, but nothing comes to mind. It's a good thing that Rin has more to say. It makes me feel relieved somehow."
    "今のにもっとましな返しが思いつけるぐらい、自分がそつのない人間だったら良かったのにと思うけど、いい返事はなにも思い浮かばない。琳がまだ話したいことがあってよかった。どういうわけか安心する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7530
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_be1c830f:

    # rin "I think I should say sorry. I'm really bad with people."
    rin "謝らないといけないね。私、人づきあいがほんとにへただから"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7535
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_165f7be4:

    # rin "Some things are hard to understand - like jellyfish. Do you understand jellyfish?"
    rin "すごくわかりづらいものってあるじゃない、くらげみたいなさ。くらげってどういうものかわかる？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7537
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_3c358b7f:

    # hi "I… I guess not."
    hi "いや……たぶんわからないな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7542
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_da809b5b:

    # rin "People are like jellyfish to me. I don't understand."
    rin "私にとっては人ってみんなくらげみたいなものでさ。わからないんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7544
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_5d832a75:

    # "Now it's her turn to make a face I don't really like seeing."
    "今度は琳が、俺の好きじゃない表情をする。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7551
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ec0cf1a7:

    # rin "I've never really had friends." nointeract
    rin "私、本当に友達がいたことないんだ" nointeract

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7565
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_5e0e40cb:

    # rin "It's really nice of you to say that."
    rin "そう言ってもらえると、すごくうれしいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7570
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_bcd2db98:

    # rin "I have always been able to tell everything to pencils and paints and paper. They are my best friends."
    rin "今までずっと、紙とペンとインクには何もかも伝えることができたんだ。最高の友達だよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7575
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_e3b17986:

    # rin "It is harder with people. I have to use words, that is hard for me."
    rin "人が相手になるともっと難しい。言葉で言わなきゃいけないのは、私には難しいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7577
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_b44986cf:

    # hi "Yeah I know, you told me. About how you forget."
    hi "そうだな、俺にも言ってたもんな。忘れることが多いって"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7582
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_9616f06f:

    # "Rin nods at me wordlessly and I dare to attempt showing her a little, encouraging smile. I hope I do it properly. She doesn't reply in any way."
    "琳は黙って俺にうなずきかける。そして俺は思い切って琳に小さく、励ますように微笑みかけてみる。うまくできているといいけど。琳はなんの反応も見せない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7584
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_daa649ee:

    # "I feel really glad. The distance Rin puts between herself and everything else has made me feel really uneasy ever since I met her. If we become real friends, I'm sure I could understand her more."
    "俺は本当にうれしい。琳が自分と他のすべてのものとの間に置いていた距離は、初めて琳と出会ってからずっと俺を不安にさせていた。俺たちが本当の友達になれたら、きっと琳のことをもっと理解できるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7586
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_b783b016:

    # "I'm sure that this way, we can close the gap of understanding between us."
    "そうすれば、お互いの理解の溝を埋められるに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7591
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_72e8931a:

    # "My thoughts don't transmit to Rin. She seems lost deep in thought, wandering amidst the sea of yellow flowers covering the grassy hilltop. It's just as well."
    "俺の考えは琳には伝わらない。この丘の上の草地で、黄色い花の海のただ中をさまよいながら、琳はぼんやりと考え事にひたっているみたいだ。ちょうどよかった。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7599
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_46b805c8:

    # "Time passes, the breeze making the taller grass sway gently in time with the wind. Rin hums a little song to herself so quietly that I can't tell what it is, if it's even anything at all."
    "時間が過ぎていき、そよ風が背の高い草を、風に合わせてやさしく揺らしていく。琳は一人で静かに鼻歌を歌う。その音は小さすぎて、なんの歌なのか、そもそもそれが歌なのかどうかもわからない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7601
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_b90ec1d8:

    # "A stronger gust sweeps over the hilltop, and the sound of the trees in the wind buries the song away."
    "もっと強い風が丘を吹きつけると、木々のざわめきがその歌に覆いかぶさる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7603
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_5da5720b:

    # "I check my watch, more out of habit more than anything else. It's 4:30 right now, on this Saturday afternoon."
    "俺は腕時計を確認する。単なる癖になってるな。今は土曜の午後、４時３０分だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7608
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_2acf58e1:

    # "Rin looks into the distant horizon with that odd, blank stare of hers, as if she were looking at nothing at all. Her pupils are dark and quiet like a pair of deep, still ponds."
    "琳は奇妙なぼんやりとした目で遠くの地平線を眺めている。まるで何も見ていないかのようだ。その瞳は深くて穏やかな二つの池のように暗く、静かだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7613
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_fce6bcae:

    # hi "I think I'm going to quit the art club. I realized it when we had that argument last week."
    hi "俺、美術部をやめようと思う。先週言い合いになったときに気がついたんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7615
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_2277f415:

    # hi "It was a good thing I tried it, but it's just not my thing, you know? I had more fun getting to know you than actually doing the art stuff in there."
    hi "挑戦したのはいい体験だったとは思うけど、でもやっぱり俺には合わなかったよ。あそこで美術やってるより、お前のことをもっと知ることのほうが楽しかった"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7617
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_bafe510f:

    # hi "But I want to stay as your friend. Would that be all right?"
    hi "でも、お前とは友達でいたい。それでもいいかな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7622
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_2317c582:

    # rin "Sure. It was getting pretty creepy anyway with you staring at me all the time."
    rin "もちろん。君がずっとじろじろ見てくるから居心地悪かったしね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7624
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c0438c81:

    # "Her comment makes me fluster immediately, but I manage a reply."
    "その言葉に俺は一瞬で動揺するけど、なんとか返答する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7626
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_8822a522:

    # hi "Sorry about that."
    hi "それは悪かったよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7631
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_32a46843:

    # rin "It's okay, I'm used to it. You're not the first person who likes to see me paint."
    rin "別にいいよ、もう慣れたから。私が描いてるのを見たがったのは君が最初ってわけじゃないしね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7636
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_16650d7a:

    # rin "Are you going to do some other thing?"
    rin "何かほかのことするの？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7638
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_61adb697:

    # hi "I don't know. Probably not."
    hi "さあな。たぶんしない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7643
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_c013d565:

    # rin "You are going to become better, right?"
    rin "これからもっと前向きになるんでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7645
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_21ce94c5:

    # hi "Sure."
    hi "だろうな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7650
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_8f3684f6:

    # rin "Me too, you know. I'm going to talk to that friend of the teacher and ask her to put my stuff in her place and work hard to get all that done."
    rin "私もね。例の先生のお友達と話をして私の作品を置いてもらうんだ。そうできるように頑張るよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7655
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_d222361c:

    # rin "I decided that just now, you know. But I think I knew it all along."
    rin "いま決めたんだ。でも最初からそうするつもりだったのかも"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7660
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_391fa556:

    # rin "I've had this feeling for a long time now, that I am going to change. Even if I hate it and don't want it, even if I wanted to, I would change."
    rin "長いあいだそんな気がしてたんだ、私も変わっていくんだって。変わるのはいや、変わりたくないって思ってても、変わりたいと思ってても、どっちにしても私はいつか変わるんだって"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7665
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_10113793:

    # rin "Like I am not enough the way I am. I think this could be a good way to do it because it's like a straight line."
    rin "つまり、今の自分は不十分だっていうか。変わっていくにはそれがいいんだろうね、直線みたいでさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7670
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_ea1b1fb6:

    # rin "Like I've learned all the things in my life so far just for this. It's just art, and it's the only thing I really know. I know what I'm going to do, so it's good. I'm not afraid at all."
    rin "今まで生きてきて学んだことは全部これだけのためだったんだ。芸術だけ、私が本当にわかるのはこれだけ、自分がこれから何をするかわかってる、だからいいことだよ。恐いことなんかなにもない"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7675
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_8c80e1f8:

    # rin "I feel like I always do. Is that weird?"
    rin "いつもとおんなじ気分がしてる。変かな？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7677
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_450d9397:

    # hi "No. Not at all."
    hi "いいや、全然変じゃないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7685
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_401c0c68:

    # "I close my eyes, and give in to the irresistible sensation that has been growing inside me all week long."
    "俺は目を閉じて、この一週間のあいだずっと俺の中で大きくなっていった、この抑えようのない気持ちに屈する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7687
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_04424fae:

    # "I float up, towards the surface of my own life."
    "俺は自分の人生の表面へと浮かび上がっていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7689
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_7ffd9b91:

    # "The pressure of being underwater slowly diminishes, the weightless sensation becomes stronger."
    "水の中にいるかのような圧力がだんだん和らぎ、重さがなくなるような感覚が強まっていく。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7691
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_21a26c98:

    # "I break the surface of the water, lifting my head into the sunlight and inhale deeply, breathing in fresh air as if for the first time in a long, long while."
    "水面を突き破って、頭を日差しのもとにさらして大きく息を吸い込む。本当に久し振りにそうするかのように、新鮮な空気を呼吸する。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7697
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_47fd6a45:

    # "My lungs fill with oxygen, and I open my eyes to see Rin's peaceful, determined face."
    "肺が酸素で満たされると、俺は目を開いて琳の穏やかな、決意に満ちた顔を見る。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7705
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_fb064e22:

    # "We walk down the slope carefully and slowly to avoid falling down, Rin in the lead and me a few steps behind."
    "俺たちは転げ落ちないように、下り坂を注意深くゆっくりと降りる。琳が先で、その数歩後ろが俺だ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7707
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_087395f5:

    # "Rin surely can do this. Even if she can't, she's going to pull through."
    "琳ならきっとできる。もしできなくたって、やりとげるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7709
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_8fa8b146:

    # "I'm sure that I can keep my head above water too, from now on."
    "俺もきっと、頭を水から上に出していられる。これからは。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7711
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_9d8af1cd:

    # "The sun sets behind our backs, setting the world ablaze in its orange glow."
    "俺たちの後ろで日が沈み、世界をオレンジ色に輝かせている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7713
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_925dbcbc:

    # "I keep watching the back of the red-headed girl descending the path a few steps ahead of me."
    "俺は数歩先で道を下っていく、赤毛の女の子の後姿を見続けている。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7715
translate jp a2_rin_dandelions_43f88eed:

    # "If it's only this much… this distance between us is definitely within my reach."
    "たったこれだけなら……俺たちの間のこの距離は、間違いなく手の届く範囲にある。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7723
translate jp a2rc1o1_bfb2bfa3:

    # hi "Wow, you're amazing."
    hi "へえ、お前すごいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7725
translate jp a2rc1o1_475c3327:

    # rin "It's not that amazing."
    rin "別にすごくはないよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7727
translate jp a2rc1o1_f1443d20:

    # rin "But thanks."
    rin "でもうれしいな"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7732
translate jp a2rc1o2_a061c071:

    # hi "Wow, I wish I was that good. I kind of embarrass myself."
    hi "ああ、俺もそんなふうにできればなあ。自分でも恥ずかしくなってくるよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7734
translate jp a2rc1o2_ce1bf2e5:

    # rin "Wouldn't you have to be me to be as good as me? I don't think you'd want to be me."
    rin "私みたいに上手くなるんだったら、私にならないといけないんじゃない？　君が私になりたがるとは思わないけどね"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7736
translate jp a2rc1o2_21c7b4a2:

    # hi "No, I guess not. Maybe just some sort of approximation then."
    hi "まあ、そうだな。せめてもう少し近づくくらいはしたいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7741
translate jp a2rc2o1_0c5f72fe:

    # hi "Sure, there were some people like this in my old school, too, but not as many. And it feels more intense, somehow."
    hi "もちろん前の学校にもそういう人はいましたよ、やっぱり。でも多くはなかったですね。それにこの学校のほうが強烈ですね、なんだか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7743
translate jp a2rc2o1_262c25e8:

    # hi "I think, if I had to pin it down to one thing, that the students here really appreciate going to school."
    hi "その感覚を１つにまとめるとしたら、ここの生徒たちは学校に通うってことの良さを本当にわかってると思うんです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7748
translate jp a2rc2o2_7a293884:

    # hi "I feel like I need to start moving in some direction, too. That's how this school makes me feel."
    hi "前に進み始めないといけない気もしてます。この学校にいると、そんな気がしてくるんです"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7755
translate jp a2rc3o1_7f8edb40:

    # "Rin could probably do it. Even though she seems to doubt herself, I have no doubts about her strength."
    "琳ならきっとできるだろう。本人に自信がなくたって、俺は琳の力になんの疑いも持っていない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7757
translate jp a2rc3o1_10195aac:

    # "She could do it, even if she can't."
    "琳ならできる、たとえできなくても。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7764
translate jp a2rc3o2_54d9df7a:

    # "Emi probably has done it. She's so happy and energetic, a runner girl without legs."
    "笑美はきっとやり遂げたんだろう。幸せと気力に満ちた、足のないランナーだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7766
translate jp a2rc3o2_82df88f9:

    # "If anyone has 'beaten' a disability, it must be her."
    "障害を『打ち負かした』人がいるとすれば、それは笑美のことに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7771
translate jp a2rc4o1_c5ac0e1c:

    # hi "I think you'd be super popular. I mean, your paintings are really amazing."
    hi "きっと超有名人になれるぞ。というか、お前の絵はとんでもなくすごいんだからさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7773
translate jp a2rc4o1_dbe08e5e:

    # hi "And you paint with your feet; that's really cool, too. I bet people will be amazed."
    hi "しかも足で描いてるだろ。それだってすごいし。絶対みんな驚くぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7778
translate jp a2rc4o1_0b9ca2d2:

    # rin "It's not a big deal. I would paint with hands if I had any."
    rin "大したことじゃないよ。もし手があったら手で描いてるし"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7780
translate jp a2rc4o1_16483a53:

    # hi "Oh… sorry. I'm sorry, I didn't mean it like that."
    hi "ああ……ごめん。俺が悪かった。そういうつもりじゃなかったんだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7785
translate jp a2rc4o1_235f18b6:

    # "Rin turns away, looking at her painting wistfully. I want to take back what I said if it was what made her make that face."
    "琳をそっぽを向いてしまい、物憂げに絵を見る。俺の言葉のせいで琳があんな表情を浮かべたのだとしたら、今の発言を取り消したくなる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7787
translate jp a2rc4o1_96b9e277:

    # rin "I get it."
    rin "わかったよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7792
translate jp a2rc4o2_6e30260d:

    # hi "You'd be letting your talent go to waste if you don't."
    hi "やらなかったら、才能を無駄にすることになるぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7797
translate jp a2rc4o2_8568a7c4:

    # rin "Go where?"
    rin "なににするって？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7799
translate jp a2rc4o2_080fcd59:

    # hi "To waste. I think it'd be a waste for other people to not see these things."
    hi "無駄にだよ。他の人たちがお前の才能を目にすることができないのはもったいないと思う"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7801
translate jp a2rc4o2_8b20d2ad:

    # "I try to press her a little bit, to extract some sort of decisiveness out of her, but Nomiya decides to intervene."
    "琳から何らかの決心を引き出そうと思って、少し後押しをしてみるけど、先生が割って入ってくる。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7807
translate jp a2rc4o2_83ebaee4:

    # no "Oh, it's not that bad."
    no "いや、そう悪いことでもないぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7812
translate jp a2rc4o2_2c7ac4a4:

    # no "I agree that it's important to strike when the iron is hot, but Tezuka is still just eighteen. She'll have time and her abilities will mature."
    no "鉄は熱いうちに打つべしというのは確かにその通りだが、手塚はまだ１８歳だ。まだ時間はあるし、実力もこれから伸びていくだろう"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7817
translate jp a2rc4o2_46f67f2a:

    # no "That said, there are many advantages for trying to make a break at a young age, if at all possible."
    no "とはいえ、もし可能なら若いうちに突っ走ろうとすることにも利点はたくさんある"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7822
translate jp a2rc4o2_fa23624c:

    # hi "Yeah, but…"
    hi "ええ、でも……"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7827
translate jp a2rc4o3_2c14e733:

    # hi "I mean, the teacher is probably right. You're not going to get a chance like this again."
    hi "というか、たぶん先生の言うとおりだよ。こんなチャンス二度と来ないって"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7829
translate jp a2rc4o3_345b2e71:

    # hi "People don't get many chances in life, and you shouldn't waste any of them even if you have doubts."
    hi "生きてるうちに得られるチャンスは多くないんだから、心配事があるくらいでそれを無駄にしちゃだめだ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7834
translate jp a2rc4o3_b1057224:

    # "Rin stares at me unresponsively. It's like my words don't have any meaning to her at all."
    "琳は返事もしないで俺を見る。俺の言葉が琳にはなんの意味も成していないかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7839
translate jp a2rc4o4_14bd83c9:

    # hi "Don't you think it would be exciting? I'd be wild about something like this."
    hi "わくわくすると思わないか？　俺だったらきっとやりたくて仕方ないって思うぜ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7844
translate jp a2rc4o4_d9a674c1:

    # no "Hahaha, so would I. But this is about things like your career and future, rather than a youthful adventure. Although there's nothing wrong with enjoying oneself."
    no "はっはっは、私もだよ。だがこれはお前たちの若々しい冒険というよりは、職業や将来のことに関するような話だ。とはいえ、楽しんでやることには何の問題もないぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7846
translate jp a2rc4o4_102a2915:

    # "Nomiya gently reprimands my excitement, but I'm not going to let it go."
    "野宮先生は興奮する俺を穏やかにたしなめるけど、俺はあきらめるつもりはない。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7848
translate jp a2rc4o4_9562a02c:

    # hi "Seriously, everyday life is so dull, you always do the same things every day, in the same way. This would be something else."
    hi "マジな話、日常生活なんて退屈なだけじゃないか。毎日同じ事を同じようにやってて。これなら違うことができるんだぜ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7853
translate jp a2rc4o5_d352e86c:

    # hi "This isn't like you. You told me that people should do things they can't, just because they can."
    hi "お前らしくないな。俺に言ってたじゃないか、人はできないことをやるべきだ、本当はできるんだからって"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7855
translate jp a2rc4o5_3f19681d:

    # hi "And now you're being all wishy-washy yourself about something this important."
    hi "この大事なときに自分が優柔不断になってるぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7860
translate jp a2rc4o6_f7678bd2:

    # hi "I really think you should aim higher. You should take the chance."
