# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7871
translate jp a2rc4o6_4aeb0c4b:

    # hi "No. I think that you're selling yourself short if you think like that. It's cowardly."
    hi "ああ。そう思ってるならお前は自分を低く見すぎてる。びびってるぞ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7876
translate jp a2rc5o1_2d4cc061:

    # hi "Nah. I'm your friend, for one."
    hi "いや、俺は友達だよ、俺としてはさ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7878
translate jp a2rc5o1_5ac68653:

    # hi "I mean, think about it. We already talk a lot to each other, and we've even gotten upset at each other and then forgiven the other for it."
    hi "つまりさ、考えてみろよ。お互いたくさん話もしたし、けんかもしたし、仲直りもしたじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7880
translate jp a2rc5o1_0efc587a:

    # hi "That's what they call friendship."
    hi "そういうのを友達っていうんだよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7885
translate jp a2rc5o2_f34b0b5f:

    # hi "What about Emi?"
    hi "笑美はどうなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7890
translate jp a2rc5o2_2d4ff1bb:

    # "She pauses for a while, as if having to consider the possibility came unexpected to her."
    "思いがけずその可能性を考える必要に迫られたかのように、琳はしばらく言葉を失う。"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7895
translate jp a2rc5o2_da6c54a4:

    # rin "Emi… takes care of me. I don't really know why."
    rin "笑美は……私の世話をしてくれるよ。なんでかは知らないけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7900
translate jp a2rc5o2_bcdc96a2:

    # rin "But I can't really talk to her, not in that way. It's like her head is made of soap foam and marshmallows. Or maybe it's just me. I like her though."
    rin "でも、ちゃんとは話せないんだ、さっき言った意味じゃ無理。笑美って頭が石鹸かマシュマロかでできてるみたい。さもなきゃ私がおかしいだけなのかも。笑美のことは好きだけど"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7902
translate jp a2rc5o2_24eec4a3:

    # hi "She's really nice, isn't she?"
    hi "いいやつじゃないか、だろ？"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7907
translate jp a2rc5o2_be16d51f:

    # rin "Yeah."
    rin "うん"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7909
translate jp a2rc5o2_2035904e:

    # hi "I want to be your friend too."
    hi "俺もお前の友達になりたいよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7911
translate jp a2rc5o2_c077c7cc:

    # hi "I'll listen to you if you want to talk. If you don't, then I can just sit quietly next to you."
    hi "話がしたいなら聞くよ。そうじゃなかったら、ただ何も言わずにお前の隣にいたっていい"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7913
translate jp a2rc5o2_2cbf921b:

    # hi "And I want to tell you about what I think too. It goes both ways."
    hi "それに俺の考えてることも話したいしな。両方だよ"

# game/script-a2-rin.rpy:7915
translate jp a2rc5o2_f109e65a:

    # hi "We should definitely be friends."
    hi "俺たち、絶対友達になるべきだよ"

